question: Tell me the total number of patients who were discharged from the hospital in 2100.

question: Tell me what was patient 10018423's daily maximum weight since 28 months ago?

question: What diagnosis did patient 10010471 receive in the first hospital encounter for the last time?

question: Show me the top three most frequent drugs that patients were prescribed within the same hospital visit after being diagnosed with hypertrophy (benign) of prostate without urinary obstruction and other lower urinary tract symptom (luts) this year.
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'hypertrophy (benign) of prostate without urinary obstruction and other lower urinary tract symptom (luts)' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3
generated_sql: SELECT d.drug_name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM patient_profiles p JOIN drug_prescriptions dp ON p.patient_id = dp.patient_id JOIN conditions c ON p.patient_id = c.patient_id JOIN drugs d ON dp.drug_id = d.drug_id WHERE c.condition_name = 'hypertrophy (benign) of prostate' AND dp.date_prescribed >= date_trunc('year', CURRENT_DATE) AND dp.date_prescribed < date_trunc('year', CURRENT_DATE) + interval '1 year' AND c.patient_id IN (SELECT patient_id FROM patient_profiles WHERE patient_id IN (SELECT patient_id FROM conditions WHERE condition_name IN ('urinary obstruction', 'other lower urinary tract symptoms'))) GROUP BY d.drug_name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 3;

question: Give me the top three most frequently prescribed drugs within 2 months for patients in their 20s who were diagnosed with long-term (current) use of anticoagulants.

question: What are the top four most common specimens tested after receiving excision of left main bronchus, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic in the same hospital encounter since 2100?
true_query: SELECT T3.spec_type_desc FROM ( SELECT T2.spec_type_desc, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'excision of left main bronchus, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc, microbiologyevents.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',microbiologyevents.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.spec_type_desc ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4
generated_sql: SELECT s.name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM specimen s JOIN procedure p ON s.id = p.specimen_id WHERE p.procedure_code = '757071' AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM p.procedure_date) >= 2021 GROUP BY s.name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 4;

question: Provide a list of the four most common diagnoses that patients were diagnosed with within 2 months after undergoing the extirpation of matter from right lower lung lobe, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic procedure.
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'extirpation of matter from right lower lung lobe, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.disease_name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM patient_diagnoses p JOIN diagnoses d ON p.diagnosis_id = d.diagnosis_id WHERE p.procedure_name = 'extirpation of matter from right lower lung lobe' AND p.procedure_date >= CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '2 months' GROUP BY d.disease_name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 4;

question: When was the last time that patient 10011398 was prescribed a medication since 10/2100 via im?
true_query: SELECT prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10011398 ) AND prescriptions.route = 'im' AND strftime('%Y-%m',prescriptions.starttime) >= '2100-10' ORDER BY prescriptions.starttime DESC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT MAX(p.date_prescribed) AS last_prescription_date FROM patient p JOIN prescription pr ON p.patient_id = pr.patient_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10011398 AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM p.date_prescribed) >= 2010;

question: Tell me the length in days of the first stay for patient 10020740 in the ICU.
true_query: SELECT strftime('%J', icustays.outtime) - strftime('%J', icustays.intime) FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10020740 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime ASC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT (o.discharge_date - o.admission_date) AS length_of_stay FROM patient_stay o WHERE o.patient_id = 10020740 AND o.stay_type_id = 2 ORDER BY o.admission_date ASC NULLS LAST LIMIT 1;

question: What was patient 10009049's last tested culture since 24 months ago?
true_query: SELECT microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc FROM microbiologyevents WHERE microbiologyevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10009049 ) AND datetime(microbiologyevents.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-24 month') ORDER BY microbiologyevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1

question: Tell me the reimbursement standard for a drug?

question: When since 07/2100 did patient 10016810 receive the sodium test for the last time?
true_query: SELECT labevents.charttime FROM labevents WHERE labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'sodium' ) AND labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10016810 ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',labevents.charttime) >= '2100-07' ORDER BY labevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1

question: Since 1 year ago, how many insertion of endotracheal airway into trachea, via natural or artificial opening procedures were there?
true_query: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'insertion of endotracheal airway into trachea, via natural or artificial opening' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year')
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM procedures p JOIN procedures_types pt ON p.procedure_type_id = pt.procedure_type_id WHERE p.date_performed >= (CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '1 year') AND (pt.name = 'Endotracheal airway' OR pt.name = 'Endotracheal intubation');

question: How many hours has it been since the first diagnosis of candidiasis of mouth in patient 10018081 during the current hospital visit?
true_query: SELECT 24 * ( strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J', diagnoses_icd.charttime) ) FROM diagnoses_icd WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'candidiasis of mouth' ) AND diagnoses_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10018081 AND admissions.dischtime IS NULL ) ORDER BY diagnoses_icd.charttime ASC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT EXTRACT(epoch FROM CURRENT_TIMESTAMP - (SELECT diagnosis_date FROM patient_diagnosis WHERE patient_id = 10018081 AND visit_id = (SELECT visit_id FROM patient_visit WHERE patient_id = 10018081 ORDER BY visit_id DESC LIMIT 1)))/3600 AS hours_since_diagnosis;

question: What is the treatment that patient 10007795 was given two or more times since 23 months ago?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T1.icd_code FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.icd_code, COUNT( procedures_icd.charttime ) AS C1 FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10007795 ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-23 month') GROUP BY procedures_icd.icd_code ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 >= 2 )
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM treatment t WHERE t.patient_id = 10007795 AND t.treatment_date >= CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '23 months' GROUP BY t.patient_id HAVING COUNT(t.treatment_id) >= 2;

question: How often did patient 10039997 go to the ICU on the first hospital encounter?

question: Show the mean blood pressure changes of patient 10031757 last measured on the first ICU visit compared to the value second to last measured on the first ICU visit?
true_query: SELECT ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10031757 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime ASC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'arterial blood pressure mean' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1 ) - ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10031757 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime ASC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'arterial blood pressure mean' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1 OFFSET 1 )
result: [{"( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10031757 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime ASC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'arterial blood pressure mean' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1 ) - ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10031757 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime ASC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'arterial blood pressure mean' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1 OFFSET 1 )": None}]
generated_sql: SELECT (SELECT AVG(bp_systolic) FROM patient_vitals WHERE patient_id = 10031757 AND icu_stay_id = 1000757075) - (SELECT AVG(bp_systolic) FROM patient_vitals WHERE patient_id = 10031757 AND icu_stay_id = 1000757075 LIMIT 1) AS change_in_avg_systolic_bp;

question: What are the three most common diagnoses of patients in their 30s this year?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T1.icd_code FROM ( SELECT diagnoses_icd.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM diagnoses_icd WHERE diagnoses_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age BETWEEN 30 AND 39 ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') GROUP BY diagnoses_icd.icd_code ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 3 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.diagnosis, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM patient p JOIN diagnosis d ON p.id = d.patient_id WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM p.date_of_birth) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) - 30 GROUP BY d.diagnosis ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 3;

question: What's the average daily number of admissions for other specified coagulation defects in 2100?
true_query: SELECT AVG(T1.C1) FROM ( SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT diagnoses_icd.hadm_id ) AS C1 FROM diagnoses_icd WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'other specified coagulation defects' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' GROUP BY strftime('%Y-%m-%d',diagnoses_icd.charttime) ) AS T1
generated_sql: SELECT AVG(count) AS average_admissions FROM (SELECT EXTRACT(DAY FROM age(CURRENT_DATE, date_admitted)) AS day_of_admission, COUNT(*) AS count FROM patient_info WHERE date_part('year', date_admitted) = 2010 AND coagulation_defect = 'other' GROUP BY day_of_admission) AS subquery;

question: So, the last glucose test result for the patient 10018423 on the last hospital visit was?

question: What was the first time that patient 10004422 was prescribed aspirin ec and milk of magnesia in 01/this year, at the same time?
true_query: SELECT T1.starttime FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'aspirin ec' AND admissions.subject_id = 10004422 AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '01' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'milk of magnesia' AND admissions.subject_id = 10004422 AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '01' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE datetime(T1.starttime) = datetime(T2.starttime) ORDER BY T1.starttime ASC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT MIN(t.date_ordered) AS min_date FROM test t WHERE t.patient_id = 10004422 AND t.date_ordered >= date_trunc('YEAR', CURRENT_DATE) AND t.date_ordered < date_trunc('YEAR', CURRENT_DATE) + interval '1 year';

question: What was the name of the organism found in the first microbiology test conducted on patient 10021487's fluid,other since 03/2100?

question: When did patient 10038933 since 07/17/2100 for the first time have an input?

question: How much does a procedure known as drainage of left upper lobe bronchus, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic, diagnostic cost?

question: When did patient 10021487 receive the last prescription of sodium bicarbonate and famotidine at the same time in 12/2100?
true_query: SELECT T1.starttime FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'sodium bicarbonate' AND admissions.subject_id = 10021487 AND strftime('%Y-%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '2100-12' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'famotidine' AND admissions.subject_id = 10021487 AND strftime('%Y-%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '2100-12' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE datetime(T1.starttime) = datetime(T2.starttime) ORDER BY T1.starttime DESC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT p.patient_id, p.last_date_treatment, row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY p.patient_id ORDER BY p.last_date_treatment DESC) AS row_num FROM patient p JOIN treatment t ON p.patient_id = t.patient_id AND p.last_date_treatment = t.date_of_treatment WHERE t.prescription_id IN ('10021487', '2100') LIMIT 1;

question: What was diagnosed for patient 10002930 the last time?

question: When did patient 10003046 last have their maximum SaO2 in the last ICU stay?

question: How much did patient 10021487 weigh during their first measurement in 12/2100?

question: What are the five commonly ordered medications that patients aged 60 or above were prescribed in the same month after diagnosed with retention of urine, unspecified in 2100?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'retention of urine, unspecified' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE admissions.age >= 60 AND strftime('%Y',prescriptions.starttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.starttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5
generated_sql: SELECT d.medication, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM dementia_medications d JOIN dementia_patients p ON d.patient_id = p.id WHERE p.age >= 60 AND EXTRACT(MONTH FROM d.date_prescribed) = EXTRACT(MONTH FROM p.date_diagnosed) AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM d.date_prescribed) = 2021 AND d.condition_code = '45423' GROUP BY d.medication ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 5;

question: What are the three most commonly prescribed medications for patients who were previously diagnosed with grand mal status within the same month, this year?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'grand mal status' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.starttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3
generated_sql: SELECT p.medication, COUNT(*) AS times_prescribed FROM patients p JOIN diagnoses d ON p.id = d.patient_id WHERE d.status = 'grand mal' AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM d.diagnosis_date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) GROUP BY p.medication ORDER BY times_prescribed DESC LIMIT 3;

question: When was patient 10005817's last microbiological examination since 03/2100?
true_query: SELECT microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents WHERE microbiologyevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10005817 ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',microbiologyevents.charttime) >= '2100-03' ORDER BY microbiologyevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT MAX(e.examination_date) AS last_examination_date FROM patient_examinations e WHERE e.patient_id = 10005817 AND e.examination_date >= '2010-03-21';

question: List the top four most frequent microbiology tests that were given to patients after they were diagnosed with sepsis during the same hospital visit during this year.
true_query: SELECT T3.test_name FROM ( SELECT T2.test_name, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'sepsis' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.test_name, microbiologyevents.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(microbiologyevents.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.test_name ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4
generated_sql: SELECT t.name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM tests t JOIN patient_tests pt ON t.id = pt.test_id JOIN patients p ON pt.patient_id = p.id JOIN diagnoses d ON p.id = d.patient_id WHERE d.diagnosis_code = 'Sepsis' AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM p.admission_date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) GROUP BY t.name ORDER BY frequency DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 4;

question: For patients who received performance of cardiac output, continuous , what are the top five most frequent diagnoses that followed afterwards within 2 months?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'performance of cardiac output, continuous' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT p.patient_id, p.patient_name, d.diagnosis_name, COUNT(d.diagnosis_name) AS frequency FROM patient_diagnosis_mapping pdm JOIN patient p ON p.patient_id = pdm.patient_id JOIN diagnosis d ON d.diagnosis_id = pdm.diagnosis_id WHERE pdm.performance_type_code = 'C' -- Assuming C stands for continuous

question: What were the four most commonly given diagnoses for patients who had received anastomosis of hepatic duct to gastrointestinal tract before in the same month this year?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'anastomosis of hepatic duct to gastrointestinal tract' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.name FROM diagnosis d JOIN patient_treatments pt ON d.id = pt.diagnosis_id WHERE pt.date_started >= date_trunc('YEAR', CURRENT_DATE) AND pt.date_started < date_trunc('YEAR', CURRENT_DATE) + interval '1 month' GROUP BY d.name ORDER BY COUNT(d.id) DESC LIMIT 4;

question: Since 2100, what are the top five most common medications prescribed in the same hospital visit to the patients aged 60 or above after they were diagnosed with unspecified acquired hypothyroidism?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'unspecified acquired hypothyroidism' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE admissions.age >= 60 AND strftime('%Y',prescriptions.starttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5
generated_sql: SELECT p.patient_name, p.patient_id, d.disease_name, m.medication_name, COUNT(*) AS medication_count FROM patient p JOIN patient_disease pd ON p.patient_id = pd.patient_id JOIN disease d ON pd.disease_id = d.disease_id JOIN patient_medication pm ON p.patient_id = pm.patient_id JOIN medication m ON pm.medication_id = m.medication_id WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM age(CURRENT_DATE, p.patient_date_of_birth)) >= 60 AND d.disease_name ILIKE '%acquired%hypothyroidism%' AND pm.prescription_date >= to_date('2021-01-01', 'YYYY-MM-DD') AND pm.prescription_date < to_date('2021-12-31', 'YYYY-MM-DD') GROUP BY p.patient_name, p.patient_id, d.d

question: List the top five most frequent diagnoses that patients were diagnosed with within 2 months after receiving diagnostic ultrasound of digestive system since 2100.
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'diagnostic ultrasound of digestive system' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.name AS diagnosis, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM diagnoses d JOIN ultrasound_diagnoses u ON d.id = u.diagnosis JOIN patient_diagnoses p ON u.patient_id = p.patient_id WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM p.diagnosis_date) >= 2100 AND p.diagnosis_date BETWEEN u.procedure_date AND u.procedure_date + interval '2 months' GROUP BY d.name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 5;

question: Which are the top three most common lab tests in 2100?
true_query: SELECT d_labitems.label FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.itemid IN ( SELECT T1.itemid FROM ( SELECT labevents.itemid, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM labevents WHERE strftime('%Y',labevents.charttime) = '2100' GROUP BY labevents.itemid ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 3 )

question: What are the four most frequently given diagnoses for patients who had previously had bypass coronary artery, one artery from left internal mammary, open approach during the same month, throughout this year?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'bypass coronary artery, one artery from left internal mammary, open approach' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.diagnosis, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM patient_diagnosis p JOIN patient_bypass_artery_date b ON p.patient_id = b.patient_id JOIN patient_mammary_artery_date m ON p.patient_id = m.patient_id WHERE EXTRACT(MONTH FROM b.bypass_date) = EXTRACT(MONTH FROM m.mammary_date) AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM b.bypass_date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM m.mammary_date) GROUP BY d.diagnosis ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 4;

question: What is the percentile of the hemoglobin value of 10.4 among patients of the same age as patient 10020740 on their first hospital encounter?
true_query: SELECT DISTINCT T1.C1 FROM ( SELECT labevents.valuenum, PERCENT_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY labevents.valuenum ) AS C1 FROM labevents WHERE labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'hemoglobin' ) AND labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age = ( SELECT admissions.age FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10020740 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1 ) ) ) AS T1 WHERE T1.valuenum = 10.4

question: What are the five commonly taken specimens for patients that were diagnosed with other disorders of neurohypophysis previously during the same hospital encounter, since 2100?

question: List the top four diagnoses that have the highest 3-month mortality rate.
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T4.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM ( SELECT T1.icd_code, ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/4 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) as C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/4 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id ) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 ) AS T4 WHERE T4.C3 <= 4 )

question: What were the top five diagnoses with the highest 6-month mortality rate?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T4.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM ( SELECT T1.icd_code, ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/2 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) as C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/2 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id ) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 ) AS T4 WHERE T4.C3 <= 5 )

question: Could you retrieve the top four diagnoses that have the highest 3-month mortality rate?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T4.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM ( SELECT T1.icd_code, ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/4 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) as C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/4 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id ) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 ) AS T4 WHERE T4.C3 <= 4 )

question: In 2100, how many patients underwent a venous catheterization, not elsewhere classified in the same month after the diagnosis of hepatic encephalopathy?
true_query: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT T1.subject_id ) FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'hepatic encephalopathy' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'venous catheterization, not elsewhere classified' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month')
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p.patient_id) AS number_of_patients FROM patient p JOIN procedure pr ON p.patient_id = pr.patient_id AND date_trunc('month', to_date(pr.procedure_date, 'YYYY-MM-DD')) = date_trunc('month', to_date(p.diagnosis_date, 'YYYY-MM-DD')) WHERE pr.procedure_code ilike '%venous%catheterization%' AND pr.procedure_code not ilike '%elsewhere%classified%in%the%same%month%after%the%diagnosis%of%hepatic%encephalopathy%';

question: What are the four most regularly ordered treatments for patients previously diagnosed with noncompliance with renal dialysis in the same hospital visit in 2100?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'noncompliance with renal dialysis' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT t.treatment_name, COUNT(*) AS COUNT FROM patient p JOIN treatment t ON p.patient_id = t.patient_id JOIN (SELECT patient_id, COUNT(*) AS num_visits FROM patient GROUP BY patient_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 1) v ON p.patient_id = v.patient_id WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM p.admission_date) = 2100 GROUP BY t.treatment_name ORDER BY COUNT DESC LIMIT 4;

question: Show me the top four diagnoses with the highest 6-month mortality rate.
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T4.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM ( SELECT T1.icd_code, ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/2 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) as C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/2 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id ) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 ) AS T4 WHERE T4.C3 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.name, SUM(CASE WHEN e.date_died <= d.date_diagnosed + INTERVAL '6 months' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) * 100.0 / NULLIF(COUNT(*), 0) AS mortality_rate FROM diagnoses d LEFT JOIN encounters e ON d.patient_id = e.patient_id GROUP BY d.name ORDER BY mortality_rate DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 4;

question: Which were the five most commonly ordered procedures for patients previously diagnosed with other motor vehicle traffic accident involving collision with motor vehicle injuring driver of motor vehicle other than motorcycle during the same hospital encounter, since 1 year ago?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'other motor vehicle traffic accident involving collision with motor vehicle injuring driver of motor vehicle other than motorcycle' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(procedures_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT p.procedure_code, COUNT(p.procedure_code) AS procedure_count FROM patient p JOIN diagnosis d ON p.patient_id = d.patient_id JOIN procedure_code pc ON d.diagnosis_code = pc.procedure_code JOIN admission a ON p.patient_id = a.patient_id WHERE pc.procedure_code ilike '%other%motor%vehicle%accident%' AND a.admission_date >= CURRENT_DATE - interval '1 year' GROUP BY p.procedure_code ORDER BY procedure_count DESC LIMIT 5;

question: What are the top five most frequently taken specimens for patients within the same hospital visit after receiving thoracentesis?
true_query: SELECT T3.spec_type_desc FROM ( SELECT T2.spec_type_desc, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'thoracentesis' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc, microbiologyevents.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.spec_type_desc ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5
generated_sql: SELECT p.patient_id, p.patient_name, s.specimen_type, COUNT(s.specimen_type) AS frequency FROM patient p JOIN specimen s ON p.patient_id = s.patient_id WHERE p.patient_id IN (SELECT t.patient_id FROM thoracentesis t) GROUP BY p.patient_id, p.patient_name, s.specimen_type ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 5;

question: What were the top five most common diagnoses that followed within 2 months for those who received insertion of endotracheal tube in this year?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'insertion of endotracheal tube' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.diagnosis, cume_dist() OVER (PARTITION BY d.diagnosis ORDER BY d.diagnosis) AS cumulative_distribution FROM Diagnosis d JOIN (SELECT patient_id, date_trunc('month', insertion_date) AS insertion_month FROM Endotracheal_tube_insertion) e ON d.patient_id = e.patient_id WHERE e.insertion_month = to_char(now() - interval '2 month', 'YYYY-MM') GROUP BY d.diagnosis ORDER BY cumulative_distribution DESC LIMIT 5;

question: Could you list the three most frequently prescribed medicines within the same hospital visit after a diagnosis of family history of ischemic heart disease was made during this year?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'family history of ischemic heart disease' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3

generated_sql: SELECT a.last_arterial_blood_pressure_systolic FROM patient p JOIN allergy_intolerance a ON p.id = a.patient_id WHERE p.id = 10003046;

question: During this hospital visit has iso-osmotic sodium chloride, lactated ringers, or metronidazole (flagyl) been prescribed for patient 10018081?
true_query: SELECT COUNT(*)>0 FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10018081 AND admissions.dischtime IS NULL ) AND prescriptions.drug IN ( 'iso-osmotic sodium chloride', 'lactated ringers', 'metronidazole (flagyl)' )
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(prescription_medicine_id) AS number_of_prescriptions FROM patient_prescriptions WHERE patient_id = 10018081;

question: Tell me all the prescriptions that patient 13054 received at the other department.
generated_sql: SELECT p.name, d.name, pr.date_prescribed FROM patient p JOIN prescription pr ON p.id = pr.patient_id JOIN department d ON p.department_id = d.id WHERE p.id = 13054 AND d.id != 757071;

question: Tell me what the total foley output of patient 10006580 is since 03/10/2100.
true_query: SELECT SUM(outputevents.value) FROM outputevents WHERE outputevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10006580 ) ) AND outputevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'foley' AND d_items.linksto = 'outputevents' ) AND strftime('%Y-%m-%d',outputevents.charttime) >= '2100-03-10'
generated_sql: SELECT SUM(f.f_output) AS total_f_output FROM foley f JOIN patient_visit pv ON f.f_visit_id = pv.pv_id WHERE pv.pv_patient_id = 10006580 AND pv.pv_visit_date >= '2021-03-10';

question: What was the count of patients who were prescribed glucagon during this year?
true_query: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT admissions.subject_id ) FROM admissions WHERE admissions.hadm_id IN ( SELECT prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'glucagon' AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') )
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Prescription p JOIN Medication m ON p.MedicationID = m.MedicationID WHERE m.Name = 'Glucagon' AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM p.DatePrescribed) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE);

question: Tell me the number of cases of extirpation of matter from left lower lung lobe, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic that occurred during this year.
true_query: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'extirpation of matter from left lower lung lobe, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year')
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM chest_x_rays WHERE date_taken >= date_trunc('YEAR', CURRENT_DATE) AND (lesion_type_code = 'ELL' OR lesion_type_code = 'ELA') AND (opening_endoscopy_code = 'N' OR opening_endoscopy_code = 'A');

question: What is the minimum total cost of the hospital visits which include medicines called ampicillin sodium since 2100?
true_query: SELECT MIN(T1.C1) FROM ( SELECT SUM(cost.cost) AS C1 FROM cost WHERE cost.hadm_id IN ( SELECT prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'ampicillin sodium' ) AND strftime('%Y',cost.chargetime) >= '2100' GROUP BY cost.hadm_id ) AS T1
generated_sql: SELECT MIN(total_cost) AS min_total_cost FROM visit_medicine_costs vmc JOIN medicines m ON vmc.medicine_id = m.id WHERE m.name ILIKE '%ampicillin%sodium%' AND vmc.visit_date >= to_date('2021', 'YYYY');

question: For the first time , how much lorazepam was prescribed to patient 10021487?
true_query: SELECT prescriptions.dose_val_rx FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10021487 ) AND prescriptions.drug = 'lorazepam' ORDER BY prescriptions.starttime ASC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT(l.prescription_id)) AS num_prescriptions FROM patient p JOIN patient_prescriptions pp ON p.patient_id = pp.patient_id JOIN lorazepam_prescriptions l ON pp.prescription_id = l.prescription_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10021487;

question: How much does the drug phenobarbital alcohol withdrawal dose taper (days 2-7) cost?
true_query: SELECT DISTINCT cost.cost FROM cost WHERE cost.event_type = 'prescriptions' AND cost.event_id IN ( SELECT prescriptions.row_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'phenobarbital alcohol withdrawal dose taper (days 2-7)' )
generated_sql: SELECT SUM(p.price) AS total_price FROM pharmacy p JOIN prescription pr ON p.id = pr.pharmacy_id WHERE pr.drug_name = 'Phenobarbital' AND pr.dose = 'alcohol withdrawal dose' AND pr.days_supply BETWEEN 2 AND 7;

question: Was any free water medication given to patient 10024043 on 12/24/last year?
true_query: SELECT COUNT(*)>0 FROM inputevents WHERE inputevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10024043 ) ) AND inputevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'free water' AND d_items.linksto = 'inputevents' ) AND datetime(inputevents.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-1 year') AND strftime('%m-%d',inputevents.starttime) = '12-24'
generated_sql: SELECT p.patient_name FROM patient p JOIN med_admin m ON p.patient_id = m.patient_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10024043 AND m.medication = 'water' AND m.dose_given = 'free' AND m.given_date::DATE = '2022-12-24';

question: Tell me the average total hospital cost that involves atenolol in 2100?
true_query: SELECT AVG(T1.C1) FROM ( SELECT SUM(cost.cost) AS C1 FROM cost WHERE cost.hadm_id IN ( SELECT prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'atenolol' ) AND strftime('%Y',cost.chargetime) = '2100' GROUP BY cost.hadm_id ) AS T1
generated_sql: SELECT AVG(total_cost) FROM drugs_data WHERE drug_name ILIKE '%atenolol%' AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM date_of_purchase) = 2100;

question: What is the maximum total hospital cost including a rbc, pleural lab test since 2100?
true_query: SELECT MAX(T1.C1) FROM ( SELECT SUM(cost.cost) AS C1 FROM cost WHERE cost.hadm_id IN ( SELECT labevents.hadm_id FROM labevents WHERE labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'rbc, pleural' ) ) AND strftime('%Y',cost.chargetime) >= '2100' GROUP BY cost.hadm_id ) AS T1
generated_sql: SELECT MAX(h.total_cost) AS max_total_cost FROM hospital h JOIN patient p ON h.patient_id = p.id JOIN test t ON p.test_id = t.id WHERE t.name = 'rbc' AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM p.date_of_birth) >= 2100;

question: Currently, how many patients are in the hospital?
true_query: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT admissions.subject_id ) FROM admissions WHERE admissions.dischtime is null
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_patients FROM patient_info pi JOIN patient_visit pv ON pi.patient_id = pv.patient_id WHERE pv.hospital_id = 757071 AND pi.patient_status = 'active';

question: Give a count of the number of ICU visits of patient 10025612 in the first hospital visit.
true_query: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT icustays.stay_id ) FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10025612 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1 )
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT v.hospital_stay_id) AS num_hospital_stays FROM patient_visits v WHERE v.patient_id = 10025612;

question: What are the charges for a procedure called replacement of stent (tube) in biliary or pancreatic duct?
true_query: SELECT DISTINCT cost.cost FROM cost WHERE cost.event_type = 'procedures_icd' AND cost.event_id IN ( SELECT procedures_icd.row_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'replacement of stent (tube) in biliary or pancreatic duct' ) )
generated_sql: SELECT procedure_costs.cost FROM procedure_costs JOIN procedure_details ON procedure_costs.procedure_id = procedure_details.procedure_id WHERE procedure_details.procedure_name ilike '%stent%replacement%' OR procedure_details.procedure_name ilike '%tube%replacement%' AND (procedure_details.procedure_location ilike '%biliary%duct%' OR procedure_details.procedure_location ilike '%pancreatic%duct%');

question: What is the code that corresponds to icd-11 for ac dvt/emb distl low ext in icd-10?
generated_sql: SELECT "icd-11" FROM "icd-10-to-icd-11-mapping" WHERE "icd-10" = 'ac dvt/emb distl low ext'

question: What is the percentile of 96.0 for a po2 test given the same age as patient 10003400 on their last hospital encounter?
true_query: SELECT DISTINCT T1.C1 FROM ( SELECT labevents.valuenum, PERCENT_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY labevents.valuenum ) AS C1 FROM labevents WHERE labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'po2' ) AND labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age = ( SELECT admissions.age FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10003400 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime DESC LIMIT 1 ) ) ) AS T1 WHERE T1.valuenum = 96.0
generated_sql: SELECT percentile_cont(0.96) within GROUP (ORDER BY age) AS percentile_96 FROM patient WHERE patient_id = 10003400;

question: What was the count of patients who were tested for base excess?
true_query: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT admissions.subject_id ) FROM admissions WHERE admissions.hadm_id IN ( SELECT labevents.hadm_id FROM labevents WHERE labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'base excess' ) )
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p.id) FROM patient p JOIN test t ON p.id = t.patient_id WHERE t.test_type_code = 'BE';

question: When was the first time patient 10008287 had an maximum po2 in their first hospital visit?
true_query: SELECT labevents.charttime FROM labevents WHERE labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10008287 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1 ) AND labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'po2' ) ORDER BY labevents.valuenum DESC, labevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT MIN(p.po2) AS min_po2, MAX(p.po2) AS max_po2, p.patient_id, h.hospital_id, v.visit_id FROM patient p JOIN hospital h ON p.hospital_id = h.hospital_id JOIN visit v ON p.patient_id = v.patient_id AND p.hospital_id = v.hospital_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10008287 GROUP BY p.patient_id, h.hospital_id, v.visit_id;

question: When did patient 10029291 last get blood culture's microbiology test since 03/2100?
true_query: SELECT microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents WHERE microbiologyevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10029291 ) AND microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc = 'blood culture' AND strftime('%Y-%m',microbiologyevents.charttime) >= '2100-03' ORDER BY microbiologyevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT MAX(l.date_of_test) AS last_test_date FROM lab_test l WHERE l.patient_id = 10029291 AND l.date_of_test > '2020-03-21';

question: What was the last time that patient 10022041 was prescribed acetaminophen iv and phosphorus in 06/2100, at the same time?
true_query: SELECT T1.starttime FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'acetaminophen iv' AND admissions.subject_id = 10022041 AND strftime('%Y-%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '2100-06' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'phosphorus' AND admissions.subject_id = 10022041 AND strftime('%Y-%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '2100-06' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE datetime(T1.starttime) = datetime(T2.starttime) ORDER BY T1.starttime DESC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT 10022041 AS patient_id, '2021-06-21' AS date_prescribed, 'acetaminophen iv' AS medication_name, 'phosphorus' AS additional_medication FROM dual;

question: Calculate the total volume of patient 10010471's input since 12/19/2100.
true_query: SELECT SUM(inputevents.totalamount) FROM inputevents WHERE inputevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10010471 ) ) AND strftime('%Y-%m-%d',inputevents.starttime) >= '2100-12-19'
generated_sql: SELECT SUM(p.volume) AS total_volume FROM patient p WHERE p.patient_id = 10010471 AND p.timestamp >= '2012-12-19';

question: Could you list the five most common specimen tests carried out since 2100?
true_query: SELECT T1.spec_type_desc FROM ( SELECT microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM microbiologyevents WHERE strftime('%Y',microbiologyevents.charttime) >= '2100' GROUP BY microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 5
generated_sql: SELECT s.name, COUNT(s.name) AS frequency FROM Specimen s WHERE s.name LIKE 's%' AND s.name > 's1000' GROUP BY s.name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 5;

question: How many patients stayed on emergency department observation since 2100?
true_query: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT admissions.subject_id ) FROM admissions WHERE admissions.hadm_id IN ( SELECT transfers.hadm_id FROM transfers WHERE transfers.careunit = 'emergency department observation' AND strftime('%Y',transfers.intime) >= '2100' )
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM patient WHERE patient_emergency_department_observation_period > 2100;

result: [{"( SELECT labevents.valuenum FROM labevents WHERE labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10006580 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1 ) AND labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'hematocrit' ) ORDER BY labevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 OFFSET 1 ) < ( SELECT labevents.valuenum FROM labevents WHERE labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10006580 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1 ) AND labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'hematocrit' ) ORDER BY labevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 )": None}]

question: Has there been any organism detected in the first microbiological examination of patient 10020944's sputum in 03/this year?
true_query: SELECT COUNT(*)>0 FROM microbiologyevents WHERE microbiologyevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10020944 ) AND microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc = 'sputum' AND microbiologyevents.org_name IS NOT NULL AND datetime(microbiologyevents.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',microbiologyevents.charttime) = '03' ORDER BY microbiologyevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM Sputum_Microbiology_Examination WHERE Patient_ID = 10020944 AND EXTRACT(MONTH FROM Examination_Date) = 3 AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM Examination_Date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE));

question: When did patient 10015272 last take the microbiology test in 06/2100?
true_query: SELECT microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents WHERE microbiologyevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10015272 ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',microbiologyevents.charttime) = '2100-06' ORDER BY microbiologyevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT MAX(t.test_date) AS last_test_date FROM patient_tests pt JOIN tests t ON pt.test_id = t.test_id WHERE pt.patient_id = 10015272 AND t.test_type_code = 'M';

question: What was the drug that was prescribed to patient 10018501 within the same hospital visit after the alcohol detoxification since 10 months ago?
true_query: SELECT T2.drug FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.charttime, procedures_icd.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'alcohol detoxification' ) AND procedures_icd.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10018501 ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-10 month') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10018501 ) AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-10 month') ) AS T2 ON T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime
generated_sql: SELECT d.drug_name FROM drug d JOIN patient_prescription p ON d.drug_id = p.drug_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10018501 AND p.date_prescribed BETWEEN (CURRENT_DATE - interval '10 months') AND CURRENT_DATE AND d.drug_name ILIKE '%alcohol detox%';

question: Was patient 10022041 given a test on rdw in 06/2100?

question: What is the outpatient schedule today for dr. solis?

result: [{"( SELECT labevents.valuenum FROM labevents WHERE labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10027602 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1 ) AND labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'glucose, csf' ) ORDER BY labevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 OFFSET 1 ) - ( SELECT labevents.valuenum FROM labevents WHERE labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10027602 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1 ) AND labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'glucose, csf' ) ORDER BY labevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 )": None}]

question: What was the name of the drug that was last prescribed for patient 10027445 since 06/2100?
true_query: SELECT prescriptions.drug FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10027445 ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',prescriptions.starttime) >= '2100-06' ORDER BY prescriptions.starttime DESC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT d.name FROM drug d JOIN patient_drug pd ON d.id = pd.drug_id WHERE pd.patient_id = 10027445 AND pd.start_date >= '2010-06-01' AND (pd.end_date IS NULL OR pd.end_date <= '2010-06-30') ORDER BY d.name DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 1;

question: What's the maximum yearly number of patients who had edema of male genital organs?
true_query: SELECT MAX(T1.C1) FROM ( SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT diagnoses_icd.hadm_id ) AS C1 FROM diagnoses_icd WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'edema of male genital organs' ) GROUP BY strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) ) AS T1
generated_sql: SELECT date_trunc('year', age(now(), p.date_of_birth)) AS year_of_birth, COUNT(*) AS total_patients FROM patient p WHERE p.gender = 'M' AND p.edema_of_male_genital_organs = TRUE GROUP BY year_of_birth ORDER BY year_of_birth DESC;

question: Reveal the drug name that was first prescribed to patient 10004235 via the po route in 07/2100?
true_query: SELECT prescriptions.drug FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10004235 ) AND prescriptions.route = 'po' AND strftime('%Y-%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '2100-07' ORDER BY prescriptions.starttime ASC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT d.drug_name FROM patient p JOIN prescription pr ON p.patient_id = pr.patient_id JOIN drug dg ON pr.drug_id = dg.drug_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10004235 AND EXTRACT(MONTH FROM pr.date_prescribed) = 7 AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM pr.date_prescribed) = 2000 AND dg.route = 'po' LIMIT 1;

question: What was the procedure conducted on patient 10020740 two or more times in 04/this year?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T1.icd_code FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.icd_code, COUNT( procedures_icd.charttime ) AS C1 FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10020740 ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',procedures_icd.charttime) = '04' GROUP BY procedures_icd.icd_code ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 >= 2 )
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM procedures p WHERE p.patient_id = 10020740 AND EXTRACT(MONTH FROM p.procedure_date) = 4 AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM p.procedure_date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) GROUP BY p.patient_id HAVING COUNT(*) >= 2;

question: What is the maximum total hospital cost that involved a procedure called fluoroscopy of multiple coronary arteries using other contrast since 2100?
true_query: SELECT MAX(T1.C1) FROM ( SELECT SUM(cost.cost) AS C1 FROM cost WHERE cost.hadm_id IN ( SELECT procedures_icd.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'fluoroscopy of multiple coronary arteries using other contrast' ) ) AND strftime('%Y',cost.chargetime) >= '2100' GROUP BY cost.hadm_id ) AS T1
generated_sql: SELECT MAX(p.cost) AS max_total_cost FROM procedures p JOIN patient_procedures pp ON p.id = pp.procedure_id WHERE p.name ilike '%fluoroscopy%' AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM pp.date_performed) >= 2100;

question: What is the body weight change of patient 10038933 second measured on the last hospital visit compared to the first value measured on the last hospital visit?
true_query: SELECT ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10038933 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime DESC LIMIT 1 ) ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'daily weight' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 OFFSET 1 ) - ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10038933 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime DESC LIMIT 1 ) ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'daily weight' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 )
result: [{"( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10038933 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime DESC LIMIT 1 ) ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'daily weight' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 OFFSET 1 ) - ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10038933 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime DESC LIMIT 1 ) ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'daily weight' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 )": None}]
generated_sql: SELECT (MAX(w.weight) - MIN(w.weight)) AS weight_change FROM patient_weight w WHERE w.patient_id = 10038933 AND w.visit_id IN (SELECT v.id FROM visit v WHERE v.patient_id = 10038933 ORDER BY v.date DESC LIMIT 2);

question: Has patient 10026406 been to the er since 2100?

question: Is it patient 10003046's o2 saturation pulseoxymetry last measured on the last ICU visit greater than second to last measured on the last ICU visit?

result: [{"( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10003046 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'o2 saturation pulseoxymetry' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1 ) > ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10003046 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'o2 saturation pulseoxymetry' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1 OFFSET 1 )": None}]
generated_sql: SELECT CAST(MAX(CASE WHEN p.patient_id = 10003046 THEN o.pulse_oxymetry_saturation END) AS FLOAT) / NULLIF(MAX(CASE WHEN p.patient_id = 10003046 THEN o.pulse_oxymetry_saturation END) - LAG(o.pulse_oxymetry_saturation, 1) OVER (PARTITION BY p.patient_id ORDER BY o.pulse_oxymetry_timestamp DESC), 0) AS ratio FROM patient p JOIN pulse_oxymetry o ON p.patient_id = o.patient_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10003046;

question: What was the organism detected in patient 10016742's first swab microbiology test since 07/2100?
true_query: SELECT microbiologyevents.org_name FROM microbiologyevents WHERE microbiologyevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10016742 ) AND microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc = 'swab' AND microbiologyevents.org_name IS NOT NULL AND strftime('%Y-%m',microbiologyevents.charttime) >= '2100-07' ORDER BY microbiologyevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1

question: How many days have passed since patient 10018081's first hematocrit laboratory test on this hospital stay?
true_query: SELECT 1 * ( strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J', labevents.charttime) ) FROM labevents WHERE labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'hematocrit' ) AND labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10018081 AND admissions.dischtime IS NULL ) ORDER BY labevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT CURRENT_DATE - MIN(t.laboratory_test_date) AS days_since_first_test FROM patient_lab_tests t WHERE t.patient_id = 10018081 AND t.laboratory_test_type_code = 'hct';

question: What was the count of patients who were prescribed phosphorus during the previous year?
true_query: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT admissions.subject_id ) FROM admissions WHERE admissions.hadm_id IN ( SELECT prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'phosphorus' AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-1 year') )
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p.id) AS number_of_patients FROM patient p JOIN prescription pr ON p.id = pr.patient_id WHERE pr.drug_name ilike '%phosphorus%' AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM pr.date_prescribed) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) - 1;

question: What was the name of that first specimen test patient 10016742 got in 08/this year?
true_query: SELECT microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc FROM microbiologyevents WHERE microbiologyevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10016742 ) AND datetime(microbiologyevents.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',microbiologyevents.charttime) = '08' ORDER BY microbiologyevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT d.name AS patient_name, t.name AS test_name, to_char(o.order_date, 'YYYY-MM-DD') AS order_date FROM patient p JOIN order_detail od ON p.patient_id = od.patient_id JOIN test t ON od.test_id = t.test_id JOIN doctor d ON p.patient_id = d.patient_id JOIN order o ON od.order_id = o.order_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10016742 AND to_char(o.order_date, 'YYYY-MM-DD') >= to_char((to_date('08/01/2020', 'MM/DD/YYYY')), 'YYYY-MM-DD') AND to_char(o.order_date, 'YYYY-MM-DD') <= to_char((to_date('08/31/2020', 'MM/DD/YYYY')), 'YYYY-MM-DD');

question: What percentile is the value of 13.0 in anion gap among patients of the same age as patient 10024043 on the first hospital encounter?
true_query: SELECT DISTINCT T1.C1 FROM ( SELECT labevents.valuenum, PERCENT_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY labevents.valuenum ) AS C1 FROM labevents WHERE labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'anion gap' ) AND labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age = ( SELECT admissions.age FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10024043 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1 ) ) ) AS T1 WHERE T1.valuenum = 13.0
generated_sql: SELECT percentile_cont(0.75) within GROUP (ORDER BY a.aniongap) AS seventy_fifth_percentile FROM patient p JOIN hospital_encounter e ON p.patientid = e.patientid JOIN aniongap a ON a.patientid = p.patientid WHERE p.patientid = 10024043;

question: Please retrieve the daily maximum amount of patient 10022880's po intake input.

question: Has there been any organism detected during the first mrsa screen microbiology test of patient 10021118 since 05/2100?

question: What number of patients were in the emergency department since 1 year ago?

question: Can you show me the three most frequently taken lab test?
true_query: SELECT d_labitems.label FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.itemid IN ( SELECT T1.itemid FROM ( SELECT labevents.itemid, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM labevents GROUP BY labevents.itemid ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 3 )
generated_sql: SELECT t.name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM tests t GROUP BY t.name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 3;

question: What are the four most commonly taken specimens for patients that received central venous catheter placement with guidance previously in the same hospital visit this year?
true_query: SELECT T3.spec_type_desc FROM ( SELECT T2.spec_type_desc, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'central venous catheter placement with guidance' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc, microbiologyevents.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(microbiologyevents.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.spec_type_desc ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4
generated_sql: SELECT p.name, s.name AS specimen_name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM patient p JOIN specimen s ON p.id = s.patient_id JOIN catheter_placement cp ON p.id = cp.patient_id WHERE cp.placement_method = 'central venous' AND cp.guidance_used = TRUE AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM cp.placement_date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) GROUP BY p.name, s.name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 4;

question: What was prescribed to patient 10015931 during the same hospital visit following their replacement of aortic valve with zooplastic tissue, percutaneous approach during this month?
true_query: SELECT T2.drug FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.charttime, procedures_icd.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'replacement of aortic valve with zooplastic tissue, percutaneous approach' ) AND procedures_icd.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10015931 ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(current_time,'start of month','-0 month') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10015931 ) AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of month') = datetime(current_time,'start of month','-0 month') ) AS T2 ON T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime
generated_sql: SELECT a.anamnesis FROM patient p JOIN admission a ON p.id = a.patient_id WHERE p.id = 10015931 AND a.date_in <= '2022-01-31' AND a.date_out >= '2022-01-01' AND a.procedure_code = 'ZOO';

question: On their first hospital visit, was patient 10015272 given any diagnosis?

question: What is the minimum total cost for the hospital when a rheumatoid factor lab test is involved since 1 year ago?
true_query: SELECT MIN(T1.C1) FROM ( SELECT SUM(cost.cost) AS C1 FROM cost WHERE cost.hadm_id IN ( SELECT labevents.hadm_id FROM labevents WHERE labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'rheumatoid factor' ) ) AND datetime(cost.chargetime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') GROUP BY cost.hadm_id ) AS T1
generated_sql: SELECT MIN(total_cost) AS min_total_cost FROM (SELECT total_cost FROM lab_tests WHERE date_of_test >= (CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '1 year') AND test_type = 'rheumatoid factor') AS subquery;

question: How much does it cost to purchase diltiazem extended-release?
true_query: SELECT DISTINCT cost.cost FROM cost WHERE cost.event_type = 'prescriptions' AND cost.event_id IN ( SELECT prescriptions.row_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'diltiazem extended-release' )

question: For the last time, what was the medication that patient 10016150 was prescribed in 05/2100 via the im route?
