question: What were the three most frequently given diagnoses for patients who received anastomosis of hepatic duct to gastrointestinal tract previously within 2 months in 2100?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'anastomosis of hepatic duct to gastrointestinal tract' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.name, COUNT(*) AS number_of_times FROM patient p JOIN anastomosis a ON p.id = a.patient_id JOIN procedure_diagnosis pd ON a.procedure_id = pd.procedure_id JOIN diagnosis d ON pd.diagnosis_id = d.id WHERE a.procedure_id = 757071 AND p.survey_time >= 20200101 AND p.survey_time <= 20201231 GROUP BY d.name ORDER BY number_of_times DESC LIMIT 3;

question: What was the last time on their current hospital visit patient 10021487 had the maximum plasma cells.
true_query: SELECT labevents.charttime FROM labevents WHERE labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10021487 AND admissions.dischtime IS NULL ) AND labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'plasma cells' ) ORDER BY labevents.valuenum DESC, labevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT MAX(p.last_plasma_cell_count) AS max_last_plasma_cell_count FROM patient p JOIN patient_hospital_visit phv ON p.id = phv.patient_id WHERE p.id = 10021487;

question: List the top five most frequent diagnoses that patients were diagnosed with within 2 months after receiving bypass coronary artery, one artery from left internal mammary, open approach throughout this year.
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'bypass coronary artery, one artery from left internal mammary, open approach' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM diagnosis d JOIN procedure p ON d.id = p.diagnosis_id WHERE p.procedure_date >= date_trunc('year', CURRENT_DATE) AND p.type = 'bypass' AND p.location = 'left internal mammary' AND p.method = 'open' GROUP BY d.name ORDER BY frequency DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 5;

question: On this month/10, when was the first input time for patient 10021487?

question: What was the total amount of output from patient 10018081 since 12/19/2100?

question: How many days has it been since patient 10021487 first received the po2 lab test during their current hospital encounter?

question: When was the first time that patient 10007818 has been prescribed medication via the subcut route since 05/2100?
true_query: SELECT prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10007818 ) AND prescriptions.route = 'subcut' AND strftime('%Y-%m',prescriptions.starttime) >= '2100-05' ORDER BY prescriptions.starttime ASC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT MIN(d.dosage_date) AS first_dosage_date FROM dosages d JOIN patient_medications p ON d.patient_id = p.patient_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10007818 AND p.route = 'subcut' AND d.dosage_date >= '2010-05-01' AND d.dosage_date < '2021-06-01';

question: What was the total amount of chlorhexidine gluconate 0.12% oral rinse prescribed to patient 10011398 in the first hospital visit?
true_query: SELECT SUM(prescriptions.dose_val_rx) FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10011398 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1 ) AND prescriptions.drug = 'chlorhexidine gluconate 0.12% oral rinse'
generated_sql: SELECT SUM(dose.dose_value_numerical) AS total_dose FROM medication_prescription_dose dose JOIN medication_prescription prescription ON dose.medication_prescription_id = prescription.medication_prescription_id WHERE prescription.patient_id = 10011398 AND prescription.hospital_visit = 1;

question: What are the five most frequently tested specimens for patients that received other incision of brain previously within 2 months in 2100?
true_query: SELECT T3.spec_type_desc FROM ( SELECT T2.spec_type_desc, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'other incision of brain' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc, microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',microbiologyevents.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.spec_type_desc ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5
generated_sql: SELECT s.specimen_name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM Specimens s JOIN Patient_Incision pi ON s.specimen_id = pi.specimen_id JOIN Patients p ON pi.patient_id = p.patient_id WHERE p.patient_id IN (SELECT patient_id FROM Patient_Incision WHERE date_of_incision > CURRENT_DATE - interval '2 months') GROUP BY s.specimen_name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 5;

question: What treatment were provided to patient 10007795 two or more times in 08/this year?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T1.icd_code FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.icd_code, COUNT( procedures_icd.charttime ) AS C1 FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10007795 ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',procedures_icd.charttime) = '08' GROUP BY procedures_icd.icd_code ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 >= 2 )
generated_sql: SELECT p.patient_name FROM patient p JOIN treatment t ON p.patient_id = t.patient_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10007795 AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM t.treatment_date) = 2008 GROUP BY p.patient_name HAVING COUNT(t.treatment_id) >= 2;

question: What output did patient 10018081 have for the first time since 04/07/2100?

generated_sql: SELECT p.last_value_date FROM patient p WHERE p.patient_id = 10018081 AND p.last_value_date > '2010-04-07';

question: When was the last time patient 10004720 was measured respiratory rate greater than 9.0 on this month/06?

generated_sql: SELECT MAX(timestamp) AS last_measurement FROM measurement m WHERE m.patient_id = 10004720 AND m.value > 9.0 AND EXTRACT(MONTH FROM m.timestamp) = 6 AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM m.timestamp) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) ;

question: What would the average yearly number of patients diagnosed with coronary atherosclerosis of autologous vein bypass graft be since 2100?
true_query: SELECT AVG(T1.C1) FROM ( SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT diagnoses_icd.hadm_id ) AS C1 FROM diagnoses_icd WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'coronary atherosclerosis of autologous vein bypass graft' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' GROUP BY strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) ) AS T1
generated_sql: SELECT AVG(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM coronary_artery_by_pass_grafts c WHERE c.year >= 2100 AND c.year <= 2105 AND c.surgeon_id = 757071) AS average_patients_per_year;

question: How many patients in 2100 were diagnosed with body mass index 35.0-35.9, adult within 2 months after the first diagnosis with anemia, unspecified?
true_query: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT T1.subject_id ) FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'anemia, unspecified' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'body mass index 35.0-35.9, adult' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month')
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM patients WHERE bmi BETWEEN 35.0 AND 35.9 AND age BETWEEN 18 AND 30 AND diagnosis_date >= '2021-01-01' AND (date_trunc('month', CURRENT_DATE) - interval '2 months') <= date_trunc('month', diagnosis_date) AND (SELECT name FROM diseases WHERE name ilike '%anemia%') IS NOT NULL AND (SELECT name FROM diseases WHERE name ilike '%unspecified%') IS NOT NULL;

question: What's the cost to get other endovascular procedures on other vessels?
true_query: SELECT DISTINCT cost.cost FROM cost WHERE cost.event_type = 'procedures_icd' AND cost.event_id IN ( SELECT procedures_icd.row_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'other endovascular procedures on other vessels' ) )
generated_sql: SELECT c.cost FROM procedure p JOIN vessel_procedure vp ON p.procedure_id = vp.procedure_id JOIN vessel v ON vp.vessel_id = v.vessel_id JOIN cost c ON p.cost_id = c.cost_id WHERE p.procedure_id != 123 AND v.vessel_id != 123;

question: In 2100, what are the top four most frequent medications prescribed during the same month to the patients in their 60 or above after they were diagnosed with atrial fibrillation?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'atrial fibrillation' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE admissions.age >= 60 AND strftime('%Y',prescriptions.starttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.starttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4
generated_sql: SELECT date_trunc('month', a.discharge_date) AS MONTH, COUNT(*) AS total_prescriptions, a.age, b.medication FROM af_patients a JOIN af_prescriptions b ON a.patient_id = b.patient_id WHERE a.age >= 60 GROUP BY MONTH, a.age, b.medication ORDER BY total_prescriptions DESC, MONTH ASC LIMIT 4;

question: When heparin and aspirin were prescribed to patient 10016150 for the last time in 05/this year at the same time?
true_query: SELECT T1.starttime FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'heparin' AND admissions.subject_id = 10016150 AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '05' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'aspirin' AND admissions.subject_id = 10016150 AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '05' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE datetime(T1.starttime) = datetime(T2.starttime) ORDER BY T1.starttime DESC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT date_trunc('month', p.date_start_treatment) AS MONTH, COUNT(*) AS total_treatments FROM patient p WHERE p.id = 10016150 AND date_part('year', p.date_start_treatment) = date_part('year', CURRENT_DATE - interval '1 year') GROUP BY MONTH;

question: What are the four most common diagnoses for patients who previously had the dilation of right main bronchus with intraluminal device, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic procedure within 2 months since 1 year ago?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'dilation of right main bronchus with intraluminal device, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.icd_code, d.icd_description, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM patient p JOIN procedure pr ON p.id = pr.patient_id JOIN dilation dl ON pr.id = dl.procedure_id JOIN icd d ON dl.icd_code = d.icd_code WHERE p.date_of_birth >= (CURRENT_DATE - interval '1 year') AND (pr.procedure_date BETWEEN (p.date_of_birth + interval '1 month') AND (p.date_of_birth + interval '2 months')) AND dl.method_of_procedure IN ('natural', 'artificial') GROUP BY d.icd_code, d.icd_description ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 4;

question: Calculate patient 10029484's total input amount of magnesium sulfate (bolus) on last month/23.

generated_sql: SELECT SUM(c.quantity) AS total_amount_magnesium_sulfate_bolus FROM cda_component c JOIN cda_section_observation_bolus s ON c.item_id = s.item_id WHERE c.item_name = 'Magnesium sulfate' AND s.patient_id = '10029484' AND s.date_time >= (CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '1 month') AND s.date_time < CURRENT_DATE;

question: What are the top four commonly ordered treatments for patients in their 40s in this year?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T1.icd_code FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age BETWEEN 40 AND 49 ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') GROUP BY procedures_icd.icd_code ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 4 )

question: What are the five most typically ordered procedures for patients previously diagnosed with other symbolic dysfunction, which took place within 2 months in 2100?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'other symbolic dysfunction' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )

question: Give me the top three most frequent procedures that patients were given in the same hospital visit after receiving extirpation of matter from left common iliac vein, percutaneous approach since 2100.

question: In 2100, what are the three frequently ordered treatments for patients who were diagnosed with personal history of other venous thrombosis and embolism within the same month?

question: How many patients were diagnosed with paroxysmal atrial fibrillation in 2100 after previously being diagnosed with pain in left shoulder within 2 months?
true_query: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT T1.subject_id ) FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'pain in left shoulder' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'paroxysmal atrial fibrillation' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month')

question: List the top four most frequent microbiology tests given to patients after being diagnosed with accidental puncture or laceration during a procedure, not elsewhere classified in the same hospital visit throughout this year.

generated_sql: SELECT v.patient_id, v.visit_date, v.test_name, COUNT(*) AS test_count FROM visits v JOIN (SELECT patient_id, visit_date FROM visits WHERE visit_date BETWEEN '2018-01-01' AND '2018-12-31' AND test_name IN ('blood culture', 'urinalysis', 'urine culture', 'hepatitis B test', 'histological examination')) AS subquery ON v.patient_id = subquery.patient_id AND v.visit_date = subquery.visit_date WHERE v.visit_date IN (SELECT visit_date FROM visits WHERE patient_id = subquery.patient_id GROUP BY patient_id HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT test_name) > 1) GROUP BY v.patient_id, v.visit_date, v.test_name ORDER BY test_count DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 4;

question: What are the three most regularly ordered treatments for patients previously diagnosed with anemia in other chronic diseases classified elsewhere during the same month in 2100?

question: What are the three most frequently prescribed drugs in the same hospital encounter to the patients aged 40s after they were diagnosed with acute embolism and thrombosis of left iliac vein in 2100?

question: What are the top five most frequent microbiology tests that patients were diagnosed with operating room of hospital as the place of occurrence of the external cause in the same month?
true_query: SELECT T3.test_name FROM ( SELECT T2.test_name, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'operating room of hospital as the place of occurrence of the external cause' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.test_name, microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.test_name ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5

question: What are the three most commonly ordered procedures for patients who were previously diagnosed with abdominal pain, unspecified site, which occurred within 2 months since 2100?

question: Throughout this year, what are the top five most common microbiology tests that patients were diagnosed with within 2 months after being diagnosed with saddle embolus of pulmonary artery with acute cor pulmonale?
true_query: SELECT T3.test_name FROM ( SELECT T2.test_name, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'saddle embolus of pulmonary artery with acute cor pulmonale' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.test_name, microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(microbiologyevents.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.test_name ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5
generated_sql: SELECT t.test_name, COUNT(*) AS test_count FROM (SELECT d.patient_id, t.test_name, t.test_date FROM diagnoses d JOIN tests t ON d.diagnosis_id = t.diagnosis_id WHERE d.diagnosis_id = 757071 AND d.patient_id IN (SELECT patient_id FROM diagnoses WHERE diagnosis_id = 757071 AND date_part('year', age(now(), test_date)) < 1) GROUP BY d.patient_id, t.test_name, t.test_date) AS subquery GROUP BY subquery.test_name ORDER BY test_count DESC LIMIT 5;

question: How many patients were diagnosed with asymptomatic human immunodeficiency virus [hiv] infection status within 2 months after first being diagnosed with mononeuritis of unspecified site in 2100?

question: What are the five most frequently prescribed drugs within 2 months to the patients aged 40s after they were diagnosed with constipation, unspecified?

question: What are the three commonly taken specimens for patients that received insertion of non-drug-eluting peripheral (non-coronary) vessel stent(s) previously within the same month in this year?
true_query: SELECT T3.spec_type_desc FROM ( SELECT T2.spec_type_desc, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'insertion of non-drug-eluting peripheral (non-coronary) vessel stent(s)' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc, microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(microbiologyevents.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.spec_type_desc ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3

question: What were the top four most common microbiology tests for patients who were previously diagnosed with spinal stenosis, lumbar region, without neurogenic claudication within 2 months?
true_query: SELECT T3.test_name FROM ( SELECT T2.test_name, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'spinal stenosis, lumbar region, without neurogenic claudication' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.test_name, microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.test_name ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4

question: What were the top four most common procedures that occurred within the same hospital visit for patients who had extirpation of matter from left lower lung lobe, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic before since 1 year ago?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'extirpation of matter from left lower lung lobe, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(procedures_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT p.procedure, COUNT(*) AS procedure_count FROM patient_procedures p JOIN patient_condition c ON p.patient_id = c.patient_id WHERE c.patient_condition_short_name = 'extirpation left lower lung lobe' AND p.procedure_date >= (CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '1 year') GROUP BY p.procedure ORDER BY procedure_count DESC LIMIT 4;

question: What are the three most frequently taken specimens for patients diagnosed with spinal stenosis, lumbar region, without neurogenic claudication previously within 2 months, in 2100?

question: During this year, what are the top three most common medications prescribed during the same month to the patients aged 60 or above after they were diagnosed with leukocytosis, unspecified?

generated_sql: SELECT MIN(m.date_of_examination) FROM microbiology m WHERE m.patient_id = 10027445 AND m.date_of_examination >= (CURRENT_DATE - interval '16 months') ORDER BY m.date_of_examination NULLS LAST LIMIT 1;

question: What are the four most frequently administered procedures for patients aged 20s in this year?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T1.icd_code FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age BETWEEN 20 AND 29 ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') GROUP BY procedures_icd.icd_code ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT p.procedure_name, COUNT(*) AS procedure_count FROM patient_procedures p JOIN patients pt ON p.patient_id = pt.patient_id WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM age(CURRENT_DATE, pt.date_of_birth)) BETWEEN 20 AND 29 GROUP BY p.procedure_name ORDER BY procedure_count DESC LIMIT 4;

question: What's the minimum total cost of a hospital that involves other and unspecified alcohol dependence, in remission in 2100?

question: What was the drug that patient 10004235 was prescribed for in the same hospital encounter after the procedure of laparoscopic cholecystectomy in 07/2100?
true_query: SELECT T2.drug FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.charttime, procedures_icd.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'laparoscopic cholecystectomy' ) AND procedures_icd.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10004235 ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100-07' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10004235 ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '2100-07' ) AS T2 ON T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime
generated_sql: SELECT d.drug_name FROM patient_prescriptions pp JOIN drugs d ON pp.drug_id = d.drug_id WHERE pp.patient_id = 10004235 AND pp.stay_id IN (SELECT s.stay_id FROM procedures p JOIN stays s ON p.stay_id = s.stay_id WHERE p.procedure_name = 'Laparoscopic cholecystectomy' AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM p.procedure_date) = 2007);

question: Show me the top three most common diagnoses of patients with age 40s this year.

generated_sql: SELECT d.diagnosis, COUNT(*) AS COUNT FROM patient_diagnoses pd JOIN patients p ON pd.patient_id = p.patient_id JOIN age_groups a ON p.age_group_id = a.age_group_id JOIN diagnoses d ON pd.diagnosis_id = d.diagnosis_id WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) - CAST(a.lower_bound AS INT) BETWEEN 40 AND 49 GROUP BY d.diagnosis ORDER BY COUNT DESC LIMIT 3;

question: Give me patient 10023239's total d5lr input since 230 days ago.

generated_sql: SELECT SUM(d.d5lr) AS total_d5lr FROM d5lr d WHERE d.patient_id = 10023239 AND d.systolic_time >= (CURRENT_TIME - INTERVAL '230 days');

question: How much is the average total cost of a hospital that involves a drug named amitriptyline in 2100?

question: How many patients with candidal stomatitis were diagnosed in the same month after previously being diagnosed with anxiety disorder, unspecified in 2100?
true_query: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT T1.subject_id ) FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'anxiety disorder, unspecified' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'candidal stomatitis' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month')
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p.id) FROM patient p JOIN diagnosis d ON p.id = d.patient_id WHERE d.diagnosis_date >= '2021-01-01' AND d.diagnosis_date < '2021-02-01' AND d.diagnosis_code = 'A01' AND EXTRACT(MONTH FROM d.diagnosis_date) = EXTRACT(MONTH FROM p.created_at);

question: What are the four most frequently taken specimens for patients diagnosed with iatrogenic pneumothorax previously in the same month, in 2100?
true_query: SELECT T3.spec_type_desc FROM ( SELECT T2.spec_type_desc, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'iatrogenic pneumothorax' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc, microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',microbiologyevents.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.spec_type_desc ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4
generated_sql: SELECT s.name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM Specimens s JOIN PatientDiagnoses pd ON s.id = pd.specimen_id WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM pd.diagnosis_date) = 2010 AND pd.diagnosis_code = 'IAT' JOIN PatientProcedures pp ON pd.patient_id = pp.patient_id WHERE EXTRACT(MONTH FROM pp.procedure_date) = EXTRACT(MONTH FROM pd.diagnosis_date) - 1 GROUP BY s.name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 4;

question: How many patients since 2100 were diagnosed with bacteremia within the same month after the diagnosis of unspecified essential hypertension?
true_query: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT T1.subject_id ) FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'unspecified essential hypertension' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'bacteremia' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month')
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p.id) AS patient_count FROM patient p JOIN (SELECT d.patient_id FROM diagnosis d WHERE d.diagnosis_date >= '2021-01-01' AND d.diagnosis_date < '2021-02-01' AND d.diagnosis_code_10 = 'E10.9') AS subquery ON p.id = subquery.patient_id WHERE EXTRACT(MONTH FROM p.birth_date) = EXTRACT(MONTH FROM subquery.diagnosis_date) AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM p.birth_date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM subquery.diagnosis_date) + 1 AND p.id NOT IN (SELECT d.patient_id FROM diagnosis d WHERE d.diagnosis_code_10 = 'E10.9');

question: What was the top three most frequent diagnoses that patients were diagnosed with within 2 months after receiving inspection of tracheobronchial tree, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'inspection of tracheobronchial tree, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.diagnosis_code, d.diagnosis_text, COUNT(d.diagnosis_code) AS frequency FROM diagnosis d JOIN inspection i ON d.diagnosis_code = i.diagnosis_code WHERE i.inspection_type IN ('N', 'A') AND i.inspection_date >= i.diagnosis_date AND i.inspection_date <= (i.diagnosis_date + interval '60 days') GROUP BY d.diagnosis_code, d.diagnosis_text ORDER BY frequency DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 3;

question: What are the five most frequently ordered medications that patients in their 30s were prescribed during the same month after being diagnosed with unspecified essential hypertension in 2100?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'unspecified essential hypertension' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE admissions.age BETWEEN 30 AND 39 AND strftime('%Y',prescriptions.starttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.starttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5
generated_sql: SELECT m.name, COUNT(*) AS times_ordered FROM patient_medications pm JOIN medications m ON pm.medication_id = m.id JOIN patients p ON pm.patient_id = p.id WHERE p.date_of_birth BETWEEN 1970-01-01 AND 2000-12-31 AND p.patient_code IN (SELECT patient_code FROM patients WHERE date_of_diagnosis BETWEEN 2000-01-01 AND 2000-12-31 AND code_of_diagnosis LIKE '%unspecified%essential%hypertension%' AND age(CURRENT_DATE, date_of_diagnosis) BETWEEN 0 AND 30) GROUP BY m.name ORDER BY times_ordered DESC LIMIT 5;

question: What are the top five most common microbiology tests for people who were diagnosed with respiratory failure, unspecified, unspecified whether with hypoxia or hypercapnia earlier within 2 months, since 2100?
true_query: SELECT T3.test_name FROM ( SELECT T2.test_name, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'respiratory failure, unspecified, unspecified whether with hypoxia or hypercapnia' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.test_name, microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',microbiologyevents.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.test_name ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5
generated_sql: SELECT c.given_name, c.sur_name, COUNT(*) AS test_count FROM patient p JOIN respiratory_failure rf ON p.patient_id = rf.patient_id JOIN diagnosis d ON rf.diagnosis_id = d.diagnosis_id JOIN microbiology m ON d.diagnosis_id = m.diagnosis_id JOIN bracket_join b ON p.patient_id = b.patient_id WHERE b.surgery_date >= 2021 AND b.surgery_date <= 2022 AND (m.test_name = 'hypoxia' OR m.test_name = 'hypercapnia') GROUP BY c.given_name, c.sur_name ORDER BY test_count DESC LIMIT 5;

question: Among patients who took other repair of vessel in 2100, what are the top five most frequent diagnoses that followed in the same month?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'other repair of vessel' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.name AS diagnosis, COUNT(*) AS frequency, date_trunc('month', d.diagnosis_date) AS MONTH, dense_rank() OVER (PARTITION BY date_trunc('month', d.diagnosis_date) ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC) AS rank FROM diagnosis d JOIN patient p ON d.patient_id = p.id JOIN procedure_code pc ON p.procedure_code = pc.code WHERE date_part('year', d.diagnosis_date) = 2010 AND pc.code like '07%' GROUP BY d.name, MONTH, rank LIMIT 5;

question: After receiving enteral infusion of concentrated nutritional substances during this year, what are the three most common diagnoses that patients received within 2 months?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'enteral infusion of concentrated nutritional substances' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3 )
generated_sql: SELECT s.diagnosis_code, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM patient_diagnoses p JOIN patient_treatments pt ON p.patient_id = pt.patient_id AND p.diagnosis_date BETWEEN pt.start_date AND pt.end_date JOIN treatments t ON pt.treatment_id = t.treatment_id AND t.treatment_date BETWEEN p.diagnosis_date AND (p.diagnosis_date + interval '2 months') JOIN substances s ON t.substance_id = s.substance_id GROUP BY s.diagnosis_code ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 3;

question: What are the three commonly ordered medications for patients who were diagnosed with atrial fibrillation previously in the same hospital visit, in this year?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'atrial fibrillation' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3
generated_sql: SELECT m.name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM medications m JOIN patient_medications pm ON m.id = pm.medication_id JOIN patients p ON pm.patient_id = p.id JOIN diagnoses d ON p.id = d.patient_id WHERE d.name = 'atrial fibrillation' AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM d.diagnosis_date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) GROUP BY m.name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 3;

question: What are the five most commonly prescribed medications for patients who were previously diagnosed with other motor vehicle traffic accident involving collision with motor vehicle injuring driver of motor vehicle other than motorcycle within 2 months?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'other motor vehicle traffic accident involving collision with motor vehicle injuring driver of motor vehicle other than motorcycle' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T2.starttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5
generated_sql: SELECT medication_name, COUNT(*) AS count_of_medications FROM patient_medications pm JOIN patient_visits pv ON pm.patient_id = pv.patient_id WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM patient_info pi JOIN past_patient_treatments ppt ON pi.patient_id = ppt.patient_id WHERE ppt.patient_id = pm.patient_id AND ppt.treatment_type_code = 'ACC' AND pi.date_of_birth >= (CURRENT_DATE - interval '2 months') AND (pi.date_of_birth <= (CURRENT_DATE - interval '6 months') AND (pm.start_date <= (CURRENT_DATE - interval '2 months')) ) GROUP BY pi.date_of_birth, ppt.patient_id HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN pi.patient_type_code = 'D' AND pm.medication_name != 'Medication Name' THEN pm.medication_name ELSE NULL END) >= 5 ) ORDER BY count_of_medications

question: What are the three frequently prescribed medications within 2 months to the patients aged 60 or above after diagnosed with chronic kidney disease, unspecified since 1 year ago?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'chronic kidney disease, unspecified' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE admissions.age >= 60 AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T2.starttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3
generated_sql: SELECT p.first_name, p.last_name, m.drug_name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM patient p JOIN prescription pr ON p.patient_id = pr.patient_id JOIN drug_prescription dp ON pr.prescription_id = dp.prescription_id JOIN medication m ON dp.drug_id = m.drug_id WHERE p.date_of_birth >= CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '1 year' AND p.date_of_birth <= CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '2 months' AND p.patient_category_code = 'C' GROUP BY p.first_name, p.last_name, m.drug_name ORDER BY frequency DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 3;

question: Show me the top three most commonly prescribed drugs within 2 months to the patients aged 60 or above after diagnosed with do not resuscitate since 2100.
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'do not resuscitate' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE admissions.age >= 60 AND strftime('%Y',prescriptions.starttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T2.starttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3

question: What are the four diagnoses with the highest 3-month mortality rate?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T4.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM ( SELECT T1.icd_code, ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/4 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) as C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/4 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id ) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 ) AS T4 WHERE T4.C3 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.diagnosis_code, d.diagnosis_name, 100 * COUNT(CASE WHEN date_part('year', age(CURRENT_DATE, c.creation_date)) < 3 THEN 1 END)::FLOAT / NULLIF(COUNT(c.creation_date), 0) AS mortality_rate FROM patient_clinical_data c JOIN diagnosis d ON c.diagnosis_code = d.diagnosis_code GROUP BY d.diagnosis_code, d.diagnosis_name ORDER BY mortality_rate DESC LIMIT 4;

question: What percentile is 0.9 creatinine in a patient of the same age as patient 10020740 during the first hospital encounter?
true_query: SELECT DISTINCT T1.C1 FROM ( SELECT labevents.valuenum, PERCENT_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY labevents.valuenum ) AS C1 FROM labevents WHERE labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'creatinine' ) AND labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age = ( SELECT admissions.age FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10020740 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1 ) ) ) AS T1 WHERE T1.valuenum = 0.9
generated_sql: SELECT percentile_cont(0.9) within GROUP (ORDER BY c.creatinine) AS p FROM patient p JOIN encounter e ON p.id = e.patient_id JOIN creatinine c ON e.id = c.encounter_id WHERE p.id = 10020740;

question: What was the last hospital admission type for patient 10018845?
true_query: SELECT admissions.admission_type FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10018845 AND datetime(admissions.admittime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ORDER BY admissions.admittime DESC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT v.admission_type_code, to_char(v.admit_date, 'YYYY-MM-DD') AS admit_date FROM patient_visit v WHERE v.patient_id = 10018845 ORDER BY to_date(to_char(v.admit_date,'YYYY-MM-DD'),'YYYY-MM-DD') DESC LIMIT 1;

question: Since 2100, what are the top five most frequently ordered lab tests for patients in the same hospital visit after being diagnosed with flatulence, eructation, and gas pain?
true_query: SELECT d_labitems.label FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.itemid IN ( SELECT T3.itemid FROM ( SELECT T2.itemid, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'flatulence, eructation, and gas pain' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, labevents.itemid, labevents.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM labevents JOIN admissions ON labevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',labevents.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.itemid ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(*) AS frequency_count, l.lab_test_name FROM patient_lab_tests p JOIN lab_tests l ON p.lab_test_id = l.lab_test_id WHERE p.patient_id IN (SELECT patient_id FROM patient_visits v WHERE v.hospital_id = 757071 AND (v.diagnosis_code LIKE '%flatulence%' OR v.diagnosis_code LIKE '%eructation%' OR v.diagnosis_code LIKE '%gas%pain%') GROUP BY patient_id HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT diagnosis_code) >= 3) GROUP BY l.lab_test_name ORDER BY frequency_count DESC LIMIT 5;

question: What was the total dosage of polyethylene glycol prescribed to patient 10021312 since 05/2100?

generated_sql: SELECT SUM(d.dosage) AS total_dosage FROM prescription p JOIN drug d ON p.drug_id = d.drug_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10021312 AND p.date_prescribed >= '2005-05-01';

question: What was the total number of input patient 10021487 has received since 09/07/2100?

question: What is the difference in patient 10019777's weights last measured on the first hospital visit compared to the second to last value measured on the first hospital visit?
true_query: SELECT ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10019777 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1 ) ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'daily weight' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1 ) - ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10019777 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1 ) ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'daily weight' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1 OFFSET 1 )
result: [{"( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10019777 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1 ) ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'daily weight' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1 ) - ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10019777 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1 ) ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'daily weight' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1 OFFSET 1 )": None}]
generated_sql: SELECT (MAX(p.weight) - MIN(p.weight)) AS weight_difference FROM patient p JOIN patient_data pd ON p.id = pd.patient_id WHERE p.id = 10019777 AND pd.hospital_no = 757071;

question: Tell me the number of cases of dilation of lower esophagus with intraluminal device, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic that occurred in 2100.

question: What was the name of the drug that patient 10001217 was prescribed with during the same hospital visit after undergoing spinal tap since 30 months ago?
true_query: SELECT T2.drug FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.charttime, procedures_icd.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'spinal tap' ) AND procedures_icd.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10001217 ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-30 month') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10001217 ) AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-30 month') ) AS T2 ON T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime
generated_sql: SELECT name FROM drug d JOIN patient_drug pd ON d.id = pd.drug_id WHERE pd.patient_id = 10001217 AND pd.hospital_id = 757071 AND pd.start_date > (CURRENT_DATE - interval '30 months');

question: For patients who undertook dilation of lower esophagus with intraluminal device, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic within the same hospital visit, what are the top three most frequent specimens tested afterward this year?
true_query: SELECT T3.spec_type_desc FROM ( SELECT T2.spec_type_desc, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'dilation of lower esophagus with intraluminal device, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc, microbiologyevents.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(microbiologyevents.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.spec_type_desc ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3
generated_sql: SELECT p.patient_id, p.first_name, p.last_name, s.specimen_type, COUNT(*) AS specimen_count FROM patient p JOIN (SELECT patient_id, specimen_type FROM specimen WHERE date_part('year', date_collected) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE)::INTEGER) AS s ON p.patient_id = s.patient_id GROUP BY p.patient_id, p.first_name, p.last_name, s.specimen_type ORDER BY specimen_count DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 3;

question: Can you tell me how many days patient 10005909 stayed in the ICU during their last stay?

question: Since 30 months ago, what was patient 10004720's first weight measurement?

generated_sql: SELECT p.first_name, p.last_name, to_char(o.order_date, 'YYYY-MM-DD') AS order_date, s.symptom, w.weight, l.lab_name, w.weight_unit FROM patients p JOIN orders o ON p.patient_id = o.patient_id JOIN order_details od ON o.order_id = od.order_id JOIN symptoms s ON od.symptom_id = s.symptom_id JOIN weight_measures w ON p.patient_id = w.patient_id JOIN labs l ON w.lab_id = l.lab_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10004720 AND to_date(to_char(o.order_date, 'YYYYMMDD'), 'YYYYMMDD') >= (CURRENT_DATE - interval '30 months') ORDER BY to_date(to_char(o.order_date, 'YYYYMMDD'), 'YYYYMMDD') ASC NULLS LAST;

question: Throughout this year, what are the top four most frequently ordered lab tests for patients in the same month after being diagnosed with unspecified essential hypertension?
true_query: SELECT d_labitems.label FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.itemid IN ( SELECT T3.itemid FROM ( SELECT T2.itemid, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'unspecified essential hypertension' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, labevents.itemid, labevents.charttime FROM labevents JOIN admissions ON labevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(labevents.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.itemid ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT date_trunc('month', c.creation_date) AS MONTH, COUNT(*) AS test_count, rank() OVER (PARTITION BY date_trunc('month', c.creation_date) ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC NULLS LAST) AS rank FROM cardiovascular_clinicals c JOIN patient_diagnoses p ON c.patient_id = p.patient_id WHERE p.diagnosis_code = '551.2' AND date_part('year', c.creation_date) = date_part('year', CURRENT_DATE) GROUP BY MONTH HAVING COUNT(*) > 3 ORDER BY MONTH NULLS LAST, rank NULLS LAST LIMIT 4;

question: What are the four commonly taken specimens for patients that were diagnosed with other late effects of cerebrovascular disease previously during the same month?
true_query: SELECT T3.spec_type_desc FROM ( SELECT T2.spec_type_desc, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'other late effects of cerebrovascular disease' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc, microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.spec_type_desc ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4
generated_sql: SELECT p.patient_id, p.patient_first_name, p.patient_last_name, o.order_date, COUNT(*) AS num_orders FROM patient p JOIN order o ON p.patient_id = o.patient_id JOIN order_detail od ON o.order_id = od.order_id GROUP BY p.patient_id, p.patient_first_name, p.patient_last_name, o.order_date HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT od.product_id) = 4 AND COUNT(DISTINCT od.product_id) > 0 ORDER BY p.patient_id NULLS LAST;

question: Can you get me the top four diagnoses that have the highest 6-month mortality rate?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T4.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM ( SELECT T1.icd_code, ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/2 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) as C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/2 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id ) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 ) AS T4 WHERE T4.C3 <= 4 )

question: Which are the top four most frequent procedures patients had within 2 months after being diagnosed with personal history of other malignant neoplasm of skin since 2100?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'personal history of other malignant neoplasm of skin' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )

question: How many patients stayed on cardiac vascular intensive care unit (cvicu) during the previous year?

generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p.patient_id) FROM patient p JOIN admission a ON p.patient_id = a.patient_id WHERE a.intensive_care_unit = 'cvicu' AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM a.admission_date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) - 1;

question: What was the number of times cepacol (menthol) was prescribed in 2100?

question: Show me the top four most frequent lab tests in 2100.
true_query: SELECT d_labitems.label FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.itemid IN ( SELECT T1.itemid FROM ( SELECT labevents.itemid, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM labevents WHERE strftime('%Y',labevents.charttime) = '2100' GROUP BY labevents.itemid ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT test, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM lab_tests WHERE year = 2100 GROUP BY test ORDER BY frequency DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 4;

question: Among patients who were administered dilation of left main bronchus with intraluminal device, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic this year, what were the top three most common treatments that they received in the same hospital encounter?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'dilation of left main bronchus with intraluminal device, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3 )
generated_sql: SELECT p.treatment, COUNT(p.treatment) AS treatment_count FROM patients p JOIN procedure_treatments pt ON p.id = pt.patient_id WHERE p.treatment_year = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) GROUP BY p.treatment ORDER BY treatment_count DESC LIMIT 3;

question: What were the most frequent diagnoses among the top five in 2100?

question: What was the name of the drug prescribed for patient 10004235 within the same day after having received a anastomosis of hepatic duct to gastrointestinal tract procedure in 07/2100?

question: What does a procedure under the name procedure on single vessel cost?

question: What were the four most commonly performed lab tests for patients who were previously diagnosed with other primary cardiomyopathies within 2 months, since 2100?
true_query: SELECT d_labitems.label FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.itemid IN ( SELECT T3.itemid FROM ( SELECT T2.itemid, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'other primary cardiomyopathies' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, labevents.itemid, labevents.charttime FROM labevents JOIN admissions ON labevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',labevents.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.itemid ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT t.lab_test, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM tb_patient_test t JOIN tb_patient p ON t.patient_id = p.patient_id WHERE p.previous_cardiomyopathy_date > 2100 AND p.previous_cardiomyopathy_date <= 2102 GROUP BY t.lab_test ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 4;

question: Tell me the name of an output that patient 10007058 has last had on last month/25?

question: What are the four most commonly ordered medications since 2100?

question: Give me the top three most frequent lab tests that patients were given after being diagnosed with knee joint replacement in the same month in 2100.
true_query: SELECT d_labitems.label FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.itemid IN ( SELECT T3.itemid FROM ( SELECT T2.itemid, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'knee joint replacement' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, labevents.itemid, labevents.charttime FROM labevents JOIN admissions ON labevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',labevents.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.itemid ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3 )

question: What were the five most frequently ordered procedures for patients who had also received drainage of left pleural cavity, percutaneous approach within the same month this year?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'drainage of left pleural cavity, percutaneous approach' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )

question: Among patients diagnosed with other pulmonary embolism without acute cor pulmonale, what were the top five most common microbiology tests conducted within 2 months?

question: Can you tell me the top three diagnoses with the highest 3-month mortality rate?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T4.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM ( SELECT T1.icd_code, ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/4 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) as C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/4 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id ) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 ) AS T4 WHERE T4.C3 <= 3 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.diagnosis, cume_dist() OVER (ORDER BY d.diagnosis) AS cumulative_distribution FROM diagnosis d ORDER BY cumulative_distribution DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 3;

generated_sql: SELECT procedure_name, COUNT(*) AS procedure_count FROM patient_procedures pp JOIN patients p ON pp.patient_id = p.id WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM age(CURRENT_DATE, p.date_of_birth)) >= 40 AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM pp.procedure_date) >= 2100 GROUP BY procedure_name ORDER BY procedure_count DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 3;

question: What was the maximum monthly number of patients who had hemothorax in 2100?
true_query: SELECT MAX(T1.C1) FROM ( SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT diagnoses_icd.hadm_id ) AS C1 FROM diagnoses_icd WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'hemothorax' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' GROUP BY strftime('%Y-%m',diagnoses_icd.charttime) ) AS T1
generated_sql: SELECT date_trunc('month', p.surgery_date) AS MONTH, COUNT(*) AS total_patients FROM patient p JOIN procedure pr ON p.patient_id = pr.patient_id WHERE date_part('year', p.surgery_date) = 2100 AND pr.procedure_id = (SELECT procedure_id FROM procedure WHERE name = 'hemothorax') GROUP BY MONTH ORDER BY MONTH;

question: Tell me the count of phlebography of the portal venous system using contrast material procedures that took place since 2100.
true_query: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'phlebography of the portal venous system using contrast material' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100'
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM procedure p JOIN procedure_type pt ON p.procedure_type_id = pt.procedure_type_id WHERE pt.procedure_type_name = 'phlebography' AND p.date_of_procedure > 20200101 AND p.date_of_procedure < 20210101 AND p.anesthesia_type_id IN (SELECT anesthesia_type_id FROM anesthesia_type WHERE anesthesia_type_name = 'contrast material');

question: Let me know the total quantity of input patient 10012552 received on 04/06/this year.

question: What was the name of the organism found in the first bronchoalveolar lavage microbiology test of patient 10007818 in 07/this year?

question: In this year, has patient 10018423 visited an emergency room?

question: What were the top five most common specimen tests conducted?

question: Tell me the four most frequent treatments for patients aged 30s in 2100.

question: What is the daily average input of d5 1/2ns that patient 10022281 is getting during their last ICU stay?
true_query: SELECT AVG(inputevents.totalamount) FROM inputevents WHERE inputevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10022281 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND inputevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'd5 1/2ns' AND d_items.linksto = 'inputevents' ) GROUP BY strftime('%Y-%m-%d',inputevents.starttime)
generated_sql: SELECT AVG(v.voltage) AS average_voltage FROM patient p JOIN (SELECT patient_id, date_trunc('day', admission_date) AS day, voltage FROM admission_voltage) AS v ON p.patient_id = v.patient_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10022281 AND p.patient_id = v.patient_id AND (p.death_date - v.day::TIMESTAMP) <= (p.admission_date - v.day::TIMESTAMP) ORDER BY day NULLS LAST LIMIT 1;

question: What was the name of the drug that patient 10004235 was prescribed in the same day after having received a laparoscopic cholecystectomy procedure?
true_query: SELECT T2.drug FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.charttime, procedures_icd.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'laparoscopic cholecystectomy' ) AND procedures_icd.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10004235 ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10004235 ) ) AS T2 ON T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of day') = datetime(T2.starttime,'start of day')
generated_sql: SELECT d.drug_name FROM drug_prescriptions d JOIN patient_surgeries ps ON d.drug_id = ps.surgery_id WHERE ps.patient_id = 10004235 AND ps.surgery_date = '2015-12-21' AND ps.surgery_procedure_code = 'L1215';
