question: What are the top four most common diagnoses that patients were diagnosed with within the same month after receiving hemodialysis's in 2100?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'hemodialysis' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.disease_name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM dialysis d JOIN patient_dialysis pd ON d.disease_id = pd.disease_id JOIN patient_info p ON pd.patient_id = p.patient_id WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM p.date_of_birth) = 2100 GROUP BY d.disease_name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 4;

question: What is the monthly maximum value of patient 10027445's weight since 14 months ago?
true_query: SELECT MAX(chartevents.valuenum) FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10027445 ) ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'daily weight' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) AND datetime(chartevents.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-14 month') GROUP BY strftime('%Y-%m',chartevents.charttime)
generated_sql: SELECT date_trunc('month', o.start_date) AS MONTH, MAX(o.value) AS max_value FROM observations o JOIN patient_observations po ON o.id = po.observation_id WHERE po.patient_id = 10027445 AND date_part('year', o.start_date) >= date_part('year', CURRENT_DATE - interval '14 months') GROUP BY MONTH;

question: What percentile of the lactate value is 2.7 among patients of the same age as patient 10005866 in their first hospital encounter?
true_query: SELECT DISTINCT T1.C1 FROM ( SELECT labevents.valuenum, PERCENT_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY labevents.valuenum ) AS C1 FROM labevents WHERE labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'lactate' ) AND labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age = ( SELECT admissions.age FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10005866 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1 ) ) ) AS T1 WHERE T1.valuenum = 2.7
generated_sql: SELECT percentile_cont(0.75) within GROUP (ORDER BY l.lactate) AS percentile_value FROM lactates l JOIN patient_states ps ON l.patient = ps.patient WHERE ps.patient = 10005866 AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM ps.stay_start_date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM l.measurement_date) AND EXTRACT(MONTH FROM ps.stay_start_date) = EXTRACT(MONTH FROM l.measurement_date) AND EXTRACT(DAY FROM ps.stay_start_date) = EXTRACT(DAY FROM l.measurement_date);

question: Among patients diagnosed with unspecified essential hypertension since 2100, what are the top four medications prescribed within 2 months to patients in their 50s?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'unspecified essential hypertension' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE admissions.age BETWEEN 50 AND 59 AND strftime('%Y',prescriptions.starttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T2.starttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4
generated_sql: SELECT p.drug FROM patient p JOIN prescription pr ON p.id = pr.patient_id WHERE p.age > 50 AND p.diagnosis = 'essential hypertension' AND date_part('year', age(now(), p.date_of_birth)) >= 2100 AND date_trunc('month', pr.date_prescribed) <= date_trunc('month', now()) + interval '2 months' GROUP BY p.drug ORDER BY COUNT(pr.id) DESC LIMIT 4;

question: What are the top three most common microbiology tests that patients had after the diagnosis of malignant neoplasm of lower third of esophagus within the same hospital visit?

generated_sql: SELECT p.patient_id, p.first_name, p.last_name, e.emergency_room_name FROM patient p JOIN patient_emergency_room_visit pev ON p.patient_id = pev.patient_id JOIN emergency_room e ON pev.emergency_room_id = e.emergency_room_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10001217;

question: Can you tell me the five most frequent diagnoses throughout this year?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T1.icd_code FROM ( SELECT diagnoses_icd.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM diagnoses_icd WHERE datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') GROUP BY diagnoses_icd.icd_code ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM Diagnosis d JOIN Visit v ON d.id = v.diagnosis_id WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM v.date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) GROUP BY d.name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 5;

question: How many hours has it been since patient 10018081's last phosphate lab test on their current hospital visit?
true_query: SELECT 24 * ( strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J', labevents.charttime) ) FROM labevents WHERE labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'phosphate' ) AND labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10018081 AND admissions.dischtime IS NULL ) ORDER BY labevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT (CURRENT_DATE - (SELECT to_date(MAX(h.startdate), 'YYYY-MM-DD') FROM histories h WHERE h.patient = 10018081 AND h.type = 'Phosphate Lab Test')) * interval '24 hours';

question: Has patient 10037861 been given a diagnosis in 2100?

generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(d.id) > 0 AS has_diagnosis FROM diagnosis d JOIN patient_diagnosis pd ON d.id = pd.diagnosis WHERE pd.patient_id = 10037861 AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM d.date) = 2021;

question: What kind of medicine does patient 50480 take when they get a prescription from another hospital?

question: What were the four most frequently diagnosed microbiology tests for patients who were diagnosed with encounter for palliative care before within the same hospital visit, since 1 year ago?
true_query: SELECT T3.test_name FROM ( SELECT T2.test_name, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'encounter for palliative care' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.test_name, microbiologyevents.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(microbiologyevents.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.test_name ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4
generated_sql: SELECT microbiology_test, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM encounters e JOIN patient_diagnoses pd ON e.patient_id = pd.patient_id WHERE (e.service = 'Microbiology' OR e.service = 'Microbiology (Dermatology)') AND (e.service_date >= (CURRENT_DATE - interval '1 year')) AND (e.service_date <= CURRENT_DATE) GROUP BY microbiology_test ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 4;

question: What's the rank of the top four most common output events?

question: How much does patient 10020944 weigh based on the last measurement since 03/2100?

question: What is the average total hospital cost for a patient diagnosed with hemiplegia, unspecified affecting left nondominant side since 1 year ago?

question: What was the name of the drug that patient 10018081 was prescribed with in the same hospital encounter after undergoing ileostomy, not otherwise specified during this month?
true_query: SELECT T2.drug FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.charttime, procedures_icd.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'ileostomy, not otherwise specified' ) AND procedures_icd.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10018081 ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(current_time,'start of month','-0 month') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10018081 ) AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of month') = datetime(current_time,'start of month','-0 month') ) AS T2 ON T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime
generated_sql: SELECT p.first_name, p.last_name, d.drug_name FROM patient p JOIN prescription pr ON p.patient_id = pr.patient_id JOIN drug d ON pr.drug_id = d.drug_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10018081 AND date_part('month', pr.prescription_date) = date_part('month', CURRENT_DATE) AND date_part('year', pr.prescription_date) = date_part('year', CURRENT_DATE) AND pr.drug_id NOT IN (SELECT drug_id FROM drug WHERE drug_name ilike '%not%otherwise%specified%') AND (pr.procedure_code = 'I10%') LIMIT 1;

generated_sql: SELECT t.name FROM patient_test p JOIN test t ON p.test_id = t.id WHERE p.patient_id = 10026406 AND to_char(p.start_date, 'YYYY') = to_char(CURRENT_DATE, 'YYYY') ORDER BY t.name NULLS LAST;

question: What is the minimum yearly number of patients who suffer from history of falling?
true_query: SELECT MIN(T1.C1) FROM ( SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT diagnoses_icd.hadm_id ) AS C1 FROM diagnoses_icd WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'history of falling' ) GROUP BY strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) ) AS T1
generated_sql: SELECT MIN(COUNT) AS MIN_PATIENTS FROM (SELECT date_trunc('year', visit_date) AS YEAR, COUNT(*) AS COUNT FROM patient_visits WHERE visit_type = 'F' GROUP BY YEAR) AS YEARLY_FALLS;

question: When are the dr. gutknecht's rounds and procedures?

question: What was the average value of lipase in patient 10021487's body in 12/this year?
true_query: SELECT AVG(labevents.valuenum) FROM labevents WHERE labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10021487 ) AND labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'lipase' ) AND datetime(labevents.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',labevents.charttime) = '12'

question: When was the last time the heart rate of patient 10018081 registered greater than 73.0 yesterday?
true_query: SELECT chartevents.charttime FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10018081 ) ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'heart rate' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) AND chartevents.valuenum > 73.0 AND datetime(chartevents.charttime,'start of day') = datetime(current_time,'start of day','-1 day') ORDER BY chartevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1

question: Has patient 10026255 been tested in the hemoglobin lab in 10/this year?

question: How many insertion of drug-eluting coronary artery stent(s) treatments were executed?

question: How many hours has it been since the first time that patient 10021487 was diagnosed with acute and subacute necrosis of liver in this hospital visit?
true_query: SELECT 24 * ( strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J', diagnoses_icd.charttime) ) FROM diagnoses_icd WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'acute and subacute necrosis of liver' ) AND diagnoses_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10021487 AND admissions.dischtime IS NULL ) ORDER BY diagnoses_icd.charttime ASC LIMIT 1

question: Is patient 10018423's respiratory rate second measured on the last ICU visit greater than the first value measured on the last ICU visit?
true_query: SELECT ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10018423 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'respiratory rate' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 OFFSET 1 ) > ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10018423 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'respiratory rate' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 )
result: [{"( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10018423 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'respiratory rate' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 OFFSET 1 ) > ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10018423 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'respiratory rate' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 )": None}]

question: What are the four most frequently tested specimens for patients that received arteriography of other intra-abdominal arteries previously within 2 months since 2100?
true_query: SELECT T3.spec_type_desc FROM ( SELECT T2.spec_type_desc, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'arteriography of other intra-abdominal arteries' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc, microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',microbiologyevents.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.spec_type_desc ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4
generated_sql: SELECT s.name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM patient p JOIN specimen s ON p.id = s.patient_id JOIN procedure_arteriography pa ON p.id = pa.patient_id WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM age(CURRENT_DATE, p.birth_date)) > 2100 AND p.id IN (SELECT patient_id FROM procedure_arteriography WHERE artery_of_interest IN (SELECT name FROM artery WHERE intra_abdominal = TRUE)) GROUP BY s.name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 4;

question: When was the last time that patient 10022281 had a maximum SaO2 in the first ICU visit?

question: What is the change in the medication of patient 10004733 today compared to yesterday?

question: When was patient 10019172 prescribed aspirin and aspirin ec at the same time for the first time since 04/2100?
true_query: SELECT T1.starttime FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'aspirin' AND admissions.subject_id = 10019172 AND strftime('%Y-%m',prescriptions.starttime) >= '2100-04' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'aspirin ec' AND admissions.subject_id = 10019172 AND strftime('%Y-%m',prescriptions.starttime) >= '2100-04' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE datetime(T1.starttime) = datetime(T2.starttime) ORDER BY T1.starttime ASC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT MIN(t.date_prescribed) AS earliest_date_prescribed FROM patient_medication p JOIN treatment t ON p.treatment_id = t.treatment_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10019172 AND t.name IN ('aspirin', 'aspirin ec') AND t.date_prescribed > '2004-04-01';

question: What is the percentile of 1.9 in a phosphate lab test conducted at the same age as patient 10007928 on their last hospital encounter?
true_query: SELECT DISTINCT T1.C1 FROM ( SELECT labevents.valuenum, PERCENT_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY labevents.valuenum ) AS C1 FROM labevents WHERE labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'phosphate' ) AND labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age = ( SELECT admissions.age FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10007928 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime DESC LIMIT 1 ) ) ) AS T1 WHERE T1.valuenum = 1.9
generated_sql: SELECT percentile_cont(0.9) within GROUP (ORDER BY p.value) AS percentile_09 FROM phosphate p JOIN patient_lab_test t ON p.patient_id = t.patient_id WHERE t.patient_id = 10007928;

question: Among patients aged 30s since 2100, what are the top three most common diagnoses?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T1.icd_code FROM ( SELECT diagnoses_icd.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM diagnoses_icd WHERE diagnoses_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age BETWEEN 30 AND 39 ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' GROUP BY diagnoses_icd.icd_code ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 3 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.name, COUNT(p.diagnosis_id) AS count FROM patient p JOIN age_range a ON p.age_range_id = a.id JOIN diagnosis d ON p.diagnosis_id = d.id WHERE a.range BETWEEN 30 AND 39 AND a.year BETWEEN 2021 AND 2100 GROUP BY d.name ORDER BY count DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 3;

question: What was the name of the organism found in patient 10021487's last bronchoalveolar lavage microbiology test since 08/2100?

question: For the patients with age 30s, what are the top four most frequent diagnoses since 2100?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T1.icd_code FROM ( SELECT diagnoses_icd.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM diagnoses_icd WHERE diagnoses_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age BETWEEN 30 AND 39 ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' GROUP BY diagnoses_icd.icd_code ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.diagnosis, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM (SELECT p.patient_id, p.date_of_birth, EXTRACT(YEAR FROM age(CURRENT_DATE, p.date_of_birth)) AS age, d.diagnosis FROM patient p JOIN diagnosis_patient dp ON p.patient_id = dp.patient_id JOIN diagnosis d ON dp.diagnosis_id = d.diagnosis_id WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM age(CURRENT_DATE, p.date_of_birth)) BETWEEN 20 AND 30) AS subquery GROUP BY d.diagnosis ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 4;

question: Tell me the top three most common diagnoses for patients aged 30s.
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T1.icd_code FROM ( SELECT diagnoses_icd.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM diagnoses_icd WHERE diagnoses_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age BETWEEN 30 AND 39 ) GROUP BY diagnoses_icd.icd_code ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 3 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.diagnosis, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM patient p JOIN patient_diagnosis pd ON p.id = pd.patient_id JOIN diagnosis d ON pd.diagnosis_id = d.id WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM AGE(p.date_of_birth)) BETWEEN 30 AND 39 GROUP BY d.diagnosis ORDER BY frequency DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 3;

question: When last did patient 10018081 have the minimum diastolic blood pressure since 10/04/2100?
true_query: SELECT chartevents.charttime FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10018081 ) ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'arterial blood pressure diastolic' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) AND strftime('%Y-%m-%d',chartevents.charttime) >= '2100-10-04' ORDER BY chartevents.valuenum ASC, chartevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT MAX(t.measure_date) FROM blood_pressure_measurements t WHERE t.patient_id = 10018081 AND t.measure_date >= '2021-10-04';

question: What were the three most frequent events?
true_query: SELECT d_items.label FROM d_items WHERE d_items.itemid IN ( SELECT T1.itemid FROM ( SELECT outputevents.itemid, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM outputevents GROUP BY outputevents.itemid ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 3 )
generated_sql: SELECT event_name, COUNT(event_name) AS event_count FROM event_log GROUP BY event_name ORDER BY event_count DESC LIMIT 3;

question: Could you tell me the top four most common procedures for patients aged 50s since 2100?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T1.icd_code FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age BETWEEN 50 AND 59 ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100' GROUP BY procedures_icd.icd_code ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT p.procedure, COUNT(*) AS procedure_count FROM patient p WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM age(p.date_of_birth)) BETWEEN 50 AND 54 AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) > 2100 GROUP BY p.procedure ORDER BY procedure_count DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 4;

question: During this year, has patient 10011398 received a diagnosis?
true_query: SELECT COUNT(*)>0 FROM diagnoses_icd WHERE diagnoses_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10011398 ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year')
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(d.id) > 0 AS has_diagnosis FROM diagnosis d JOIN patient_diagnosis pd ON d.id = pd.diagnosis_id WHERE pd.patient_id = 10011398 AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM d.diagnosis_date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE);

question: What is the daily maximum value of weight for patient 10019385 in 03/2100?
true_query: SELECT MAX(chartevents.valuenum) FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10019385 ) ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'daily weight' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',chartevents.charttime) = '2100-03' GROUP BY strftime('%Y-%m-%d',chartevents.charttime)
generated_sql: SELECT MAX(p.weight) FROM patient p WHERE p.id = 10019385 AND TO_CHAR(p.date_of_birth, 'YYYY-MM-DD') = '2000-03-21';

question: What are the five most commonly ordered procedures for patients who were previously diagnosed with noncompliance with renal dialysis, which occurred in the same hospital encounter since 2100?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'noncompliance with renal dialysis' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT p.procedure_code, p.procedure_name, COUNT(*) AS procedure_count FROM patient_procedure pp JOIN procedure p ON pp.procedure_code = p.procedure_code WHERE pp.discharge_date >= 2021 AND pp.discharge_date < 2022 AND pp.patient_id IN (SELECT patient_id FROM patient_problem WHERE problem_code = 'noncompliance with renal dialysis') GROUP BY p.procedure_code, p.procedure_name ORDER BY procedure_count DESC LIMIT 5;

question: What was the name of the drug that patient 10012552 was prescribed in the same hospital visit after having received a single internal mammary-coronary artery bypass procedure?
true_query: SELECT T2.drug FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.charttime, procedures_icd.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'single internal mammary-coronary artery bypass' ) AND procedures_icd.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10012552 ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10012552 ) ) AS T2 ON T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime
generated_sql: SELECT d.drug_name FROM patient p JOIN (SELECT v.patient_id, v.stay_id FROM visit v WHERE v.patient_id = 10012552 AND v.hospital_id = 757071 AND v.visit_date > CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '1 day') AS subquery ON p.patient_id = subquery.patient_id JOIN stay s ON s.stay_id = subquery.stay_id JOIN drug_prescription dp ON dp.stay_id = s.stay_id JOIN drug d ON d.drug_id = dp.drug_id WHERE d.drug_name NOT ILIKE '%coronary%artery%bypass%procedure%' GROUP BY d.drug_name;

question: When did patient 10015860 receive the last bisacodyl and ondansetron prescription at the same time in 10/this year?
true_query: SELECT T1.starttime FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'bisacodyl' AND admissions.subject_id = 10015860 AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '10' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'ondansetron' AND admissions.subject_id = 10015860 AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '10' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE datetime(T1.starttime) = datetime(T2.starttime) ORDER BY T1.starttime DESC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT MAX(p.date_end) AS last_prescription_date FROM patient p JOIN prescription_medicine pm ON p.patient_id = pm.patient_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10015860 AND EXTRACT(MONTH FROM p.date_end) = 10 AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM p.date_end) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE);

question: On this month/30, what was the first arterial blood pressure systolic reading for patient 10018081?

question: What was the first thing patient 10018328 had as output on 05/09/2100?

question: Give me the five most common treatments since 2100.

question: Please retrieve the daily minimum amount of patient 10005817's albumin 5% input on the last hospital visit.

question: What is the total number of days that have passed since patient 10021487's first asparate aminotransferase (ast) lab test in the current hospital visit?

generated_sql: SELECT (CURRENT_DATE - MIN(p.ast_date)) AS days_since_ast FROM patient p WHERE p.patient_id = 10021487;

question: Tell me the maximum total hospital cost that involves accidental poisoning from other specified plants in 2100.

question: What is the difference between respiratory rate on patient 10031404 last measured on the last ICU visit compared to the value first measured on the last ICU visit?
true_query: SELECT ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10031404 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'respiratory rate' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1 ) - ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10031404 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'respiratory rate' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 )
result: [{"( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10031404 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'respiratory rate' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1 ) - ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10031404 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'respiratory rate' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 )": None}]

question: Is the red blood cells level of patient 10021312 last measured on the first hospital visit greater than the second to last level measured on the first hospital visit?

question: What are the three frequently prescribed medications in the same month to the patients aged 60 or above after diagnosed with hypotension, unspecified in 2100?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'hypotension, unspecified' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE admissions.age >= 60 AND strftime('%Y',prescriptions.starttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.starttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3
generated_sql: SELECT m.drug_name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM medications m JOIN patient_problems p ON m.patient_id = p.patient_id JOIN patient_conditions pc ON p.patient_id = pc.patient_id WHERE pc.problem_type_code = 'HYPOTENSION' AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM pc.diagnosis_date) = 2021 AND pc.age >= 60 GROUP BY m.drug_name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 3;

question: Was nacl 0.9% administrated to patient 10015272 on their last ICU stay?

question: Retrieve the top four most frequent procedures that were delivered to patients within the same hospital visit after they received other endovascular procedures on other vessels.
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'other endovascular procedures on other vessels' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT p.name AS patient_name, o.name AS procedure_name, s.name AS site_name, v.name AS vessel_name, row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY p.id ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC) AS procedure_rank FROM procedures p INNER JOIN patient_procedures pp ON p.id = pp.procedure_id INNER JOIN sites s ON pp.site_id = s.id INNER JOIN vessels v ON pp.vessel_id = v.id INNER JOIN operations o ON p.id = o.patient_id WHERE o.name IN (SELECT name FROM procedures WHERE procedure_type_id = 1) AND v.id IN (SELECT vessel_id FROM vessels WHERE vessel_type_id = 1) GROUP BY p.name, o.name, s.name, v.name HAVING COUNT(o.name) >= 2 ORDER BY procedure_rank <= 4;

question: Tell me the difference in the respiratory rate value for patient 10007058 second measured on the last ICU visit compared to the first value measured on the last ICU visit?
true_query: SELECT ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10007058 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'respiratory rate' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 OFFSET 1 ) - ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10007058 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'respiratory rate' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 )
result: [{"( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10007058 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'respiratory rate' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 OFFSET 1 ) - ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10007058 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'respiratory rate' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 )": None}]
generated_sql: SELECT (SELECT RATE FROM RESPIRATORY_RATE WHERE PATIENT_ID = 10007058 ORDER BY ICU_VISIT DESC LIMIT 1) - (SELECT RATE FROM RESPIRATORY_RATE WHERE PATIENT_ID = 10007058 ORDER BY ICU_VISIT ASC LIMIT 1) AS RATE_DIFF;

question: Could you retrieve the top four diagnoses that have the highest 6-month mortality rate?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T4.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM ( SELECT T1.icd_code, ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/2 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) as C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/2 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id ) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 ) AS T4 WHERE T4.C3 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.name, SUM(CASE WHEN s.date_of_death BETWEEN (CURRENT_DATE - interval '6 months') AND CURRENT_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)::FLOAT / NULLIF(COUNT(s.id), 0) AS mortality_rate FROM diagnosis d JOIN patient_surgeries s ON d.id = s.diagnosis_id GROUP BY d.name ORDER BY mortality_rate DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 4;

question: What are the top five most common diagnoses that patients were diagnosed with during the same month after receiving bypass coronary artery, one artery from left internal mammary, open approach's this year?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'bypass coronary artery, one artery from left internal mammary, open approach' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT c.patient_id, c.date_of_procedure, d.name, COUNT(c.procedure_id) AS procedure_count FROM coronary_bypasses c JOIN procedures p ON c.procedure_id = p.procedure_id JOIN diagnoses d ON p.diagnosis_id = d.diagnosis_id WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM c.date_of_procedure) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) AND p.approach_id = 1 AND d.name NOT ILIKE '%bypass%coronary%' GROUP BY c.patient_id, c.date_of_procedure, d.name ORDER BY procedure_count DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 5;

question: Since 2100, how many patients received arteriography of femoral and other lower extremity arteries within 2 months after being diagnosed with other specified procedures as the cause of abnormal reaction of patient, or of later complication, without mention of misadventure at time of procedure?
true_query: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT T1.subject_id ) FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'other specified procedures as the cause of abnormal reaction of patient, or of later complication, without mention of misadventure at time of procedure' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'arteriography of femoral and other lower extremity arteries' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month')
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM patient p JOIN procedure pr ON p.patient_id = pr.patient_id JOIN arteriography a ON p.patient_id = a.patient_id WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM a.procedure_date) >= 2021 AND (p.patient_id IN (SELECT patient_id FROM procedure WHERE procedure_date BETWEEN a.procedure_date AND a.procedure_date + interval '60 days') OR p.patient_id IN (SELECT patient_id FROM procedure WHERE procedure_date BETWEEN a.procedure_date - interval '60 days' AND a.procedure_date)) AND pr.procedure_name NOT ILIKE '%misadventure%' AND pr.procedure_name NOT ILIKE '%complication%' AND pr.procedure_name NOT ILIKE '%reaction%';

question: What are the four most frequently performed treatments for patients in their 30s throughout this year?

question: Get me the top three most frequent medications that patients were prescribed with within the same month after being diagnosed with traumatic shock since 2100.
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'traumatic shock' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',prescriptions.starttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.starttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3
generated_sql: SELECT p.firstname, p.lastname, m.name, COUNT(m.name) AS medication_count FROM patient p JOIN prescription pr ON p.id = pr.patient_id JOIN medication m ON pr.medication_id = m.id WHERE p.diagnosis_date >= 2021 AND p.diagnosis_date < 2022 AND m.name IN ('Epinephrine', 'Aspirin', 'Acetylsalicylic Acid') GROUP BY p.firstname, p.lastname, m.name ORDER BY medication_count DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 3;

question: Which medication was patient 10009035 prescribed within 2 days following the extracorporeal circulation auxiliary to open heart surgery procedure in 05/this year?
true_query: SELECT T2.drug FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.charttime, procedures_icd.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'extracorporeal circulation auxiliary to open heart surgery' ) AND procedures_icd.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10009035 ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',procedures_icd.charttime) = '05' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10009035 ) AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '05' ) AS T2 ON T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T2.starttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 day')

question: How many patients received esophagogastroduodenoscopy [egd] with closed biopsy treatment within 2 months after being diagnosed with acute posthemorrhagic anemia in 2100?
true_query: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT T1.subject_id ) FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'acute posthemorrhagic anemia' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'esophagogastroduodenoscopy [egd] with closed biopsy' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month')

question: For patients diagnosed with hemorrhage of rectum and anus throughout this year, what are the top five most recurrent treatments within 2 months?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'hemorrhage of rectum and anus' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT p.patient_id, p.patient_name, t.treatment_name, COUNT(*) AS treatment_count, SUM(CASE WHEN p.last_treatment_date BETWEEN CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '2 months' AND CURRENT_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS recent_treatments FROM patients p JOIN treatments t ON p.last_treatment_id = t.treatment_id WHERE p.patient_status = 'Active' AND t.treatment_type = 'Surgical' AND t.treatment_name ILIKE '%hemorrhage%' GROUP BY p.patient_id, p.patient_name, t.treatment_name ORDER BY treatment_count DESC LIMIT 5;

question: What are the five most common diagnoses of patients in their 60 or above since 2100?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T1.icd_code FROM ( SELECT diagnoses_icd.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM diagnoses_icd WHERE diagnoses_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age >= 60 ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' GROUP BY diagnoses_icd.icd_code ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.diagnosis, COUNT(d.diagnosis) AS diagnosis_count FROM diagnoses d JOIN patients p ON d.patient_id = p.patient_id JOIN age a ON p.patient_id = a.patient_id WHERE a.age >= 60 AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) - a.year_of_birth >= 2100 GROUP BY d.diagnosis ORDER BY diagnosis_count DESC LIMIT 5;

question: Give me the top four most frequent procedures that patients were given in the same hospital encounter after receiving reposition left mandible with external fixation device, percutaneous approach.
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'reposition left mandible with external fixation device, percutaneous approach' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT p.patient_id, p.patient_first_name, p.patient_last_name, row_number() OVER(PARTITION BY p.patient_id ORDER BY COUNT(i.procedure_id) DESC) AS row_num FROM patient p JOIN procedure_patient pp ON p.patient_id = pp.patient_id JOIN procedure i ON pp.procedure_id = i.procedure_id WHERE i.procedure_name ilike '%reposition%left%mandible%with%external%fixation%device%,%percutaneous%approach%' GROUP BY p.patient_id, p.patient_first_name, p.patient_last_name HAVING COUNT(i.procedure_id) > 3 ORDER BY row_num <= 4;

question: What was the drug that patient 10022017 prescribed for within 2 days after the procedure of excision of left saphenous vein, percutaneous endoscopic approach on their last hospital encounter?
true_query: SELECT T2.drug FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.charttime, procedures_icd.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'excision of left saphenous vein, percutaneous endoscopic approach' ) AND procedures_icd.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10022017 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime DESC LIMIT 1 ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10022017 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime DESC LIMIT 1 ) ) AS T2 ON T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T2.starttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 day')
generated_sql: SELECT d.drug_name FROM patient_encounters e JOIN patient_treatments pt ON e.patient_id = pt.patient_id JOIN drugs d ON pt.drug_id = d.drug_id WHERE e.patient_id = 10022017 AND e.procedure_name = 'excision of left saphenous vein, percutaneous endoscopic approach' AND pt.treatment_start_date >= e.procedure_date - interval '2 days' LIMIT 1;

question: What is the average total hospital cost which involves exposure to other specified factors, initial encounter since 2100?

question: What were the five most frequently ordered procedures for patients who had also received extirpation of matter from left lower lobe bronchus, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic within the same hospital visit?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'extirpation of matter from left lower lobe bronchus, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT p.procedure_name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM patient p JOIN procedure_order po ON p.procedure_id = po.procedure_id WHERE p.patient_id IN (SELECT patient_id FROM procedure_order WHERE procedure_id IN (SELECT procedure_id FROM procedure_order WHERE procedure_name = 'Extirpation of matter from left lower lobe bronchus')) GROUP BY p.procedure_name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 5;

question: What are the four diagnoses with the highest 6-month mortality rate?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T4.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM ( SELECT T1.icd_code, ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/2 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) as C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/2 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id ) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 ) AS T4 WHERE T4.C3 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.disease_name, CAST(COUNT(*) filter (WHERE d.death_month BETWEEN EXTRACT(MONTH FROM CURRENT_DATE) - 6 AND EXTRACT(MONTH FROM CURRENT_DATE)) AS FLOAT) / NULLIF(COUNT(*), 0) AS mortality_rate FROM diseases d GROUP BY d.disease_name ORDER BY mortality_rate DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 4;

question: What are the five frequently prescribed medications for patients diagnosed with unspecified condition of brain previously within the same month?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'unspecified condition of brain' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.starttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5
generated_sql: SELECT p.drug_name, COUNT(p.drug_name) AS frequency FROM patient p JOIN prescription pr ON p.patient_id = pr.patient_id JOIN diagnosis d ON pr.diagnosis_id = d.diagnosis_id JOIN month m ON d.diagnosis_date >= m.month_start AND d.diagnosis_date < m.next_month_start WHERE m.month_start <= CURRENT_DATE AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM d.diagnosis_date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) AND d.diagnosis_condition ilike '%unspecified%' GROUP BY p.drug_name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 5;

question: Show me the top four most frequent diagnoses that patients were diagnosed with within 2 months after receiving extirpation of matter from left lower lobe bronchus, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic in 2100.
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'extirpation of matter from left lower lobe bronchus, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.diagnosis, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM diagnosis d JOIN procedures p ON d.procedure_id = p.procedure_id JOIN patient_procedures pp ON p.procedure_id = pp.procedure_id WHERE p.procedure_name = 'extirpation of matter from left lower lobe bronchus' AND pp.date_procedure >= '2021-01-01' AND pp.date_procedure <= '2021-12-31' GROUP BY d.diagnosis ORDER BY frequency DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 4;

question: What are the three most commonly ordered procedures for patients who were previously diagnosed with intestinal infection due to other organism, not elsewhere classified, which occurred during the same hospital visit since 2100?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'intestinal infection due to other organism, not elsewhere classified' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3 )
generated_sql: SELECT p.procedure_name, COUNT(p.procedure_name) AS procedure_count FROM patient_procedures pp JOIN procedures p ON pp.procedure_id = p.procedure_id WHERE pp.patient_id IN (SELECT patient_id FROM patient_diagnoses pd WHERE diagnosis_name ilike '%intestinal%infection%from%other%organism%not%elsewhere%classified%' AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM visit_date) >= 2021) GROUP BY p.procedure_name ORDER BY procedure_count DESC LIMIT 3;

question: List the five most frequent diagnoses a patient was diagnosed with within 2 months after receiving percutaneous abdominal drainage in this year.
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'percutaneous abdominal drainage' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.diagnosis, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM patient p JOIN drainage dg ON p.id = dg.patient_id JOIN diagnosis d ON dg.diagnosis_id = d.id WHERE dg.type = 'percutaneous abdominal' AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM dg.date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) AND dg.date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31' GROUP BY d.diagnosis ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 5;

question: What was the drug that patient 10018501 prescribed for within 2 days after the procedure of alcohol detoxification in 08/2100?
true_query: SELECT T2.drug FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.charttime, procedures_icd.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'alcohol detoxification' ) AND procedures_icd.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10018501 ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100-08' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10018501 ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '2100-08' ) AS T2 ON T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T2.starttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 day')
generated_sql: SELECT p.drug_name, p.dosage, p.start_date, p.end_date FROM patient p JOIN prescription pr ON p.patient_id = pr.patient_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10018501 AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM p.start_date) = 2008 AND EXTRACT(MONTH FROM p.start_date) = 8 AND EXTRACT(DAY FROM p.start_date) BETWEEN 2 AND 3 AND pr.drug_name = 'Alcohol detoxification';

question: What are the three frequently prescribed medications in the same month to the patients aged 40s after diagnosed with coronary atherosclerosis of native coronary artery throughout this year?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'coronary atherosclerosis of native coronary artery' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE admissions.age BETWEEN 40 AND 49 AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.starttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3
generated_sql: SELECT p.first_name, p.last_name, c.disease_name, date_trunc('month', c.diagnosis_date) AS MONTH, COUNT(*) AS number_of_prescriptions, rank() OVER (PARTITION BY p.first_name, p.last_name, MONTH ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC) AS rank FROM patient p JOIN coronary c ON p.id = c.patient_id WHERE date_part('year', c.diagnosis_date) = date_part('year', CURRENT_DATE) AND age(c.date_of_birth) BETWEEN 40 AND 49 AND c.disease_name = 'Coronary atherosclerosis of native coronary artery' GROUP BY p.first_name, p.last_name, MONTH ORDER BY rank;

question: Get me the top three most frequent medications that patients were prescribed with in the same month after being diagnosed with unspecified infectious and parasitic diseases.
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'unspecified infectious and parasitic diseases' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.starttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3
generated_sql: SELECT p.id, p.name, m.name AS medication_name, row_number() OVER(PARTITION BY p.id ORDER BY COUNT(m.id) DESC) AS rank FROM patient p JOIN prescription pr ON p.id = pr.patient_id JOIN medication m ON pr.medication_id = m.id WHERE p.diagnosis_id IN (SELECT diagnosis_id FROM diagnosis WHERE name IN ('infectious disease', 'parasitic disease')) GROUP BY p.id, p.name, m.name;

question: What was prescribed to patient 10027602 within 2 days following their percutaneous [endoscopic] gastrostomy [peg] in 12/2100?
true_query: SELECT T2.drug FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.charttime, procedures_icd.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'percutaneous [endoscopic] gastrostomy [peg]' ) AND procedures_icd.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10027602 ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100-12' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10027602 ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '2100-12' ) AS T2 ON T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T2.starttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 day')
generated_sql: SELECT t.name AS patient_name, p.name AS procedure_name, s.name AS surgeon_name, d.name AS department_name, to_char(t.date_of_birth, 'YYYY-MM-DD') AS patient_date_of_birth, to_char(p.date_last_performed, 'YYYY-MM-DD') AS procedure_date_last_performed, to_char(s.date_joined, 'YYYY-MM-DD') AS surgeon_date_joined, to_char(d.date_founded, 'YYYY-MM-DD') AS department_date_founded FROM patient t JOIN procedure p ON t.id = p.patient_id JOIN surgeon s ON p.surgeon_id = s.id JOIN department d ON s.department_id = d.id WHERE t.id = 10027602 AND to_date(to_char(p.date_last_performed,'YYYY'),'YYYY') <= (CURRENT_DATE - interval '2 days');

question: What are the top three most frequent microbiology tests that patients were diagnosed with malignant neoplasm of lower third of esophagus within 2 months since 2100?
true_query: SELECT T3.test_name FROM ( SELECT T2.test_name, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'malignant neoplasm of lower third of esophagus' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.test_name, microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',microbiologyevents.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.test_name ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3

question: Can you tell me the top five diagnoses with the highest 3-month mortality rate?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T4.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM ( SELECT T1.icd_code, ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/4 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) as C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/4 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id ) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 ) AS T4 WHERE T4.C3 <= 5 )

generated_sql: SELECT cost FROM drugs WHERE name ilike '%nicotine patch%';

question: For patients who were diagnosed with acute venous embolism and thrombosis of subclavian veins , what are the top four most common medications that followed afterward during the same hospital visit?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'acute venous embolism and thrombosis of subclavian veins' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4
generated_sql: SELECT p.patient_id, p.first_name, p.last_name, d.date_of_service, m.drug_name, COUNT(*) OVER(PARTITION BY p.patient_id, d.date_of_service, m.drug_name ORDER BY d.date_of_service ROWS BETWEEN UNBOUNDED preceding AND CURRENT ROW) AS drug_count FROM patient p JOIN patient_service ps ON p.patient_id = ps.patient_id JOIN service s ON ps.service_id = s.service_id JOIN drug_service ds ON s.service_id = ds.service_id JOIN drug d ON ds.drug_id = d.drug_id JOIN (SELECT patient_id, COUNT(*) AS num_drugs FROM patient_service WHERE service_id IN (SELECT service_id FROM service WHERE procedure_code ilike '%acute%venous%embolism%' OR procedure_code ilike '%thrombosis%of%subclavian%veins%') GROUP BY patient_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 3) subquery ON p.

question: When was the last time when patient 10021312 was prescribed vancomycin and 0.9% sodium chloride at the same time in 09/this year?
true_query: SELECT T1.starttime FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'vancomycin' AND admissions.subject_id = 10021312 AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '09' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = '0.9% sodium chloride' AND admissions.subject_id = 10021312 AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '09' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE datetime(T1.starttime) = datetime(T2.starttime) ORDER BY T1.starttime DESC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT MAX(r.date_prescribed) AS last_prescription_date FROM prescriptions p JOIN patient_medications pm ON p.id = pm.prescription_id JOIN medications m ON pm.medication_id = m.id JOIN refills r ON p.id = r.prescription_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10021312 AND EXTRACT(MONTH FROM p.date_prescribed) = 9 AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM p.date_prescribed) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) GROUP BY p.id ORDER BY last_prescription_date DESC LIMIT 1;

question: Is the value of patient 10009628's hemoglobin, second measured on the first hospital visit, less than the first value measured on the first hospital visit?

result: [{"( SELECT labevents.valuenum FROM labevents WHERE labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10009628 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1 ) AND labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'hemoglobin' ) ORDER BY labevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 OFFSET 1 ) < ( SELECT labevents.valuenum FROM labevents WHERE labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10009628 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1 ) AND labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'hemoglobin' ) ORDER BY labevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 )": None}]

question: What is the minimum monthly number of cases for unspecified atrial flutter?
true_query: SELECT MIN(T1.C1) FROM ( SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT diagnoses_icd.hadm_id ) AS C1 FROM diagnoses_icd WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'unspecified atrial flutter' ) GROUP BY strftime('%Y-%m',diagnoses_icd.charttime) ) AS T1
generated_sql: SELECT date_trunc('month', c.creation_date) AS MONTH, COUNT(*) AS number_of_cases FROM cases c WHERE c.disease_id = (SELECT d.disease_id FROM diseases d WHERE d.name ilike '%unspecified%atrial%flutter%') GROUP BY MONTH ORDER BY MONTH;

question: Last year, how many patients were diagnosed with hypertensive chronic kidney disease, unspecified, with chronic kidney disease stage i through stage iv, or unspecified?
true_query: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT admissions.subject_id ) FROM admissions WHERE admissions.hadm_id IN ( SELECT diagnoses_icd.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'hypertensive chronic kidney disease, unspecified, with chronic kidney disease stage i through stage iv, or unspecified' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-1 year') )
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p.patient_id) AS number_of_patients FROM patient p JOIN condition c ON p.patient_id = c.patient_id WHERE c.condition_category = 'Hypertensive Chronic Kidney Disease' AND c.condition_severity IN ('Unspecified', 'Stage I', 'Stage II', 'Stage III', 'Stage IV') AND c.condition_status = 'Active' AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM c.condition_start_date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) - 1;

question: Which are the five top specimens that were tested in 2100?

question: What specimen test was given in 12/2100 to patient 10008454 for the last time?
true_query: SELECT microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc FROM microbiologyevents WHERE microbiologyevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10008454 ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',microbiologyevents.charttime) = '2100-12' ORDER BY microbiologyevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT s.name, t.name AS test_name, o.name AS order_name, p.name AS patient_name, row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY p.id ORDER BY o.id DESC) AS recent_order_rank FROM specimen s JOIN test t ON s.id = t.specimen_id JOIN order_entry o ON o.specimen_id = s.id JOIN patient p ON p.id = o.patient_id WHERE o.date_ordered >= '2021-12-01' AND o.date_ordered < '2022-01-01' AND o.patient_id = 10008454;

question: What is the minimum total cost of hospitalization that includes the reticulocyte count, absolute laboratory test since 2100?

question: How many patients received unilateral simple mastectomy treatment in the same month after having been diagnosed with acquired absence of breast and nipple in 2100?
true_query: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT T1.subject_id ) FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'acquired absence of breast and nipple' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'unilateral simple mastectomy' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month')
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM breast_surgeries WHERE treatment_type = 'unilateral simple mastectomy' AND YEAR = 2021 AND MONTH = 10;

question: What is the minimum monthly number of patients diagnosed with personal history of traumatic brain injury since 2100?
