question: When did patient 10027602 last have a minimum value of diastolic blood pressure on last month/29?
true_query: SELECT chartevents.charttime FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10027602 ) ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'arterial blood pressure diastolic' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) AND datetime(chartevents.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(current_time,'start of month','-1 month') AND strftime('%d',chartevents.charttime) = '29' ORDER BY chartevents.valuenum ASC, chartevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT MAX(p.date_time) AS last_measurement_date FROM patient p JOIN measurement m ON p.id = m.patient_id WHERE p.id = 10027602 AND m.diastolic_pressure = MIN(m.diastolic_pressure) AND EXTRACT(MONTH FROM m.date_time) = EXTRACT(MONTH FROM CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '1 month') AND EXTRACT(DAY FROM m.date_time) = 29;

question: What are the five frequently ordered drugs for patients diagnosed with unspecified condition of brain previously in the same month?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'unspecified condition of brain' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.starttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5
generated_sql: SELECT o.drug, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM orders o JOIN (SELECT p.patient_id, p.first_name, p.last_name, o.drug, EXTRACT(MONTH FROM o.order_date) AS MONTH FROM patients p JOIN orders o ON p.patient_id = o.patient_id WHERE p.diagnosis_code = 'U071' GROUP BY p.patient_id, p.first_name, p.last_name, o.drug, MONTH HAVING COUNT(*) > 1) AS subquery ON o.patient_id = subquery.patient_id AND o.order_date >= subquery.order_date - interval '1 month' AND o.order_date < subquery.order_date GROUP BY o.drug ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 5;

question: Retrieve the top five most frequent medications that patients were prescribed within 2 months after being diagnosed with unspecified vascular insufficiency of intestine since 1 year ago.
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'unspecified vascular insufficiency of intestine' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(prescriptions.starttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T2.starttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5
generated_sql: SELECT m.name, COUNT(*) AS count FROM medications m JOIN patient_medications pm ON m.id = pm.medication_id JOIN patients p ON pm.patient_id = p.id JOIN (SELECT patient_id FROM patients WHERE date_diagnosed >= now() - interval '1 year' AND date_diagnosed < now() - interval '2 months') AS d ON p.id = d.patient_id GROUP BY m.name ORDER BY count DESC LIMIT 5;

question: What was the duration in days of patient 10014354's last stay in the ICU?

generated_sql: SELECT (MAX(s.stay_end_date) - MIN(s.stay_start_date)) AS duration FROM stays s WHERE s.patient_id = 10014354;

question: What are the five most frequently given diagnoses for patients who had previously had extirpation of matter from left lower lobe bronchus, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic in the same month, since 1 year ago?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'extirpation of matter from left lower lobe bronchus, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.diagnosis, COUNT(d.diagnosis) AS count FROM diagnoses d JOIN patient_procedures p ON d.patient_id = p.patient_id WHERE p.procedure_type_id = 4 AND p.procedure_subtype_id IN (757071) AND d.entry_date >= (CURRENT_DATE - interval '1 year') GROUP BY d.diagnosis ORDER BY count DESC LIMIT 5;

question: What are the five most commonly tested specimens for patients who were diagnosed with chronic osteomyelitis, site unspecified previously within the same month, throughout this year?
true_query: SELECT T3.spec_type_desc FROM ( SELECT T2.spec_type_desc, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'chronic osteomyelitis, site unspecified' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc, microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(microbiologyevents.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.spec_type_desc ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5
generated_sql: SELECT s.specimen_type, COUNT(*) AS count FROM specimens s JOIN patient_diagnoses pd ON s.patient_id = pd.patient_id WHERE pd.diagnosis_type_id = 1 AND pd.previous_diagnosis_site_id IS NULL AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM s.collection_date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) GROUP BY s.specimen_type ORDER BY count DESC LIMIT 5;

question: What are the four most frequent microbiology tests in this year?
true_query: SELECT T1.test_name FROM ( SELECT microbiologyevents.test_name, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM microbiologyevents WHERE datetime(microbiologyevents.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') GROUP BY microbiologyevents.test_name ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 4
generated_sql: SELECT t.name, COUNT(t.name) AS frequency FROM tests t WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM t.date_performed) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) GROUP BY t.name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 4;

question: Please list out the monthly average weight of patient 10004422 in 2100.
true_query: SELECT AVG(chartevents.valuenum) FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10004422 ) ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'daily weight' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) AND strftime('%Y',chartevents.charttime) = '2100' GROUP BY strftime('%Y-%m',chartevents.charttime)
generated_sql: SELECT date_trunc('month', o.order_date) AS MONTH, AVG(o.order_weight) AS Average_Weight FROM orders o WHERE o.patient_id = 10004422 AND date_part('year', o.order_date) = 2021 GROUP BY MONTH ORDER BY MONTH;

question: What are the five diagnoses with the lowest 3-month survival rate?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T4.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM ( SELECT T1.icd_code, ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/4 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) as C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/4 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id ) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 ) AS T4 WHERE T4.C3 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.diagnosis, d.survival_3_months FROM diagnoses d ORDER BY d.survival_3_months DESC LIMIT 5;

question: How much calcium carbonate was prescribed the last time on the first hospital stay to patient 10021938?
true_query: SELECT prescriptions.dose_val_rx FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10021938 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1 ) AND prescriptions.drug = 'calcium carbonate' ORDER BY prescriptions.starttime DESC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT h.hospital_name, p.patient_name, c.calcium_carbonate_dose FROM patient p JOIN hospitalization h ON p.patient_id = h.patient_id JOIN calcium_carbonate_dosages c ON h.hospital_id = c.hospital_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10021938 ORDER BY h.hospital_name, c.calcium_carbonate_dose DESC LIMIT 1;

question: What percentile does a urea nitrogen value of 15.0 for patient 10001725 place in today on the first hospital encounter?
true_query: SELECT DISTINCT T1.C1 FROM ( SELECT labevents.valuenum, PERCENT_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY labevents.valuenum ) AS C1 FROM labevents WHERE labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'urea nitrogen' ) AND labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age = ( SELECT admissions.age FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10001725 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1 ) ) ) AS T1 WHERE T1.valuenum = 15.0
generated_sql: SELECT percent_rank() OVER (ORDER BY u.urea_value) AS percentile_rank FROM urea_values u WHERE u.patient_id = 10001725 AND u.encounter_id = 1;

question: What was a drug that patient 10001217 was prescribed for within the same hospital visit after receiving central venous catheter placement with guidance in this month?
true_query: SELECT T2.drug FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.charttime, procedures_icd.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'central venous catheter placement with guidance' ) AND procedures_icd.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10001217 ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(current_time,'start of month','-0 month') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10001217 ) AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of month') = datetime(current_time,'start of month','-0 month') ) AS T2 ON T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime
generated_sql: SELECT d.drug_name, d.dose, d.route, d.frequency, d.duration, d.start_date, d.end_date, v.stay_id, v.stay_start_date, v.stay_end_date FROM drug_administrations d JOIN patient_visits v ON d.patient_id = v.patient_id WHERE d.patient_id = 10001217 AND d.start_date >= date_trunc('month', v.stay_start_date) AND d.end_date <= date_trunc('month', v.stay_end_date) AND d.start_date <= v.stay_start_date AND d.end_date >= v.stay_end_date AND v.stay_id IN (SELECT stay_id FROM patient_stays WHERE length_of_stay > 10) AND d.drug_indication_id IN (SELECT drug_indication_id FROM drug_indications WHERE drug_name = 'central venous catheter placement with guidance');

question: Has patient 10020306 been treated with a unilateral simple mastectomy procedure since 1 year ago?

question: What are the five frequently ordered medications for patients diagnosed with esophageal reflux previously during the same hospital visit?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'esophageal reflux' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5

question: What is the average yearly number of patients who suffer from unspecified sinusitis (chronic)?

question: Fetch the top five most frequent procedures that were administered to patients within 2 months after they had drainage of right lower lobe bronchus, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic, diagnostic.
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'drainage of right lower lobe bronchus, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic, diagnostic' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT p.procedure_name, COUNT(*) AS procedure_count FROM patient p JOIN procedure pr ON p.patient_id = pr.patient_id JOIN drainage d ON p.patient_id = d.patient_id WHERE d.drainage_type = 'Right lower lobe bronchus' AND pr.procedure_date BETWEEN d.drainage_date AND d.drainage_date + interval '60 days' GROUP BY p.procedure_name ORDER BY procedure_count DESC LIMIT 5;

question: What are the five most frequently administered procedures for patients aged 40s since 2100?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T1.icd_code FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age BETWEEN 40 AND 49 ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100' GROUP BY procedures_icd.icd_code ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT procedures.name, COUNT(*) AS procedure_count FROM procedures JOIN patient_procedures ON procedures.id = patient_procedures.procedure_id JOIN patients ON patient_procedures.patient_id = patients.id WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM age(CURRENT_DATE, patients.date_of_birth)) BETWEEN 40 AND 49 AND patient_procedures.procedure_date >= date '2021-01-01' GROUP BY procedures.name ORDER BY procedure_count DESC LIMIT 5;

question: What are the five most commonly diagnosed diagnoses for patients who had previously received extirpation of matter from left lower lobe bronchus, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic within the same month since 1 year ago?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'extirpation of matter from left lower lobe bronchus, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.diagnosis_code, d.diagnosis_description, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM diagnosis d JOIN patient_procedure p ON d.diagnosis_code = p.procedure_code WHERE d.procedure_code = '0102' AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM p.procedure_date) >= EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) - 1 AND EXTRACT(MONTH FROM p.procedure_date) = EXTRACT(MONTH FROM CURRENT_DATE) AND p.procedure_date <= CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '1 month' GROUP BY d.diagnosis_code, d.diagnosis_description ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 5;

question: When was patient 10020740's respiratory rate first measured less than 20.0 in their first ICU stay?
true_query: SELECT chartevents.charttime FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10020740 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime ASC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'respiratory rate' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) AND chartevents.valuenum < 20.0 ORDER BY chartevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT MIN(t.hr) AS min_hr FROM tb_vitals t JOIN (SELECT p.patient_id, p.first_name, p.last_name, s.stay_id FROM patients p JOIN stays s ON p.patient_id = s.patient_id) AS pstay ON t.patient_id = pstay.patient_id WHERE t.measurement_type_code = 'RR' AND t.hr < 20.0 AND pstay.stay_id IN (SELECT s.stay_id FROM stays s JOIN tb_vitals v ON s.patient_id = v.patient_id WHERE v.hr < 20.0) GROUP BY t.patient_id;

question: Show me patient 10004733's total volume of output since 05/19/2100.
true_query: SELECT SUM(outputevents.value) FROM outputevents WHERE outputevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10004733 ) ) AND strftime('%Y-%m-%d',outputevents.charttime) >= '2100-05-19'
generated_sql: SELECT SUM(p.output) AS total_output FROM patient p WHERE p.id = 10004733 AND p.last_update >= '2021-05-19';

question: How much is introduction of nutritional substance into upper gi, via natural or artificial opening?
true_query: SELECT DISTINCT cost.cost FROM cost WHERE cost.event_type = 'procedures_icd' AND cost.event_id IN ( SELECT procedures_icd.row_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'introduction of nutritional substance into upper gi, via natural or artificial opening' ) )
generated_sql: SELECT g.name, s.name, SUM(d.amount) AS total_amount FROM gastric_introductions g JOIN substances s ON g.id = s.gastric_introduction JOIN digestive_system d ON g.id = d.gastric_introduction WHERE g.location = 'upper' GROUP BY g.name, s.name;

question: Tell me the name of the diagnosis that patient 10039831 received the first time in 2100?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT diagnoses_icd.icd_code FROM diagnoses_icd WHERE diagnoses_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10039831 ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ORDER BY diagnoses_icd.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.name FROM diagnosis d JOIN patient_diagnosis pd ON d.id = pd.diagnosis_id WHERE pd.patient_id = 10039831 AND pd.entry_date >= 2100 ORDER BY pd.entry_date ASC NULLS LAST LIMIT 1;

question: What new drugs are prescribed for patient 10039831 today compared to yesterday?
true_query: SELECT prescriptions.drug FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10039831 ) AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of day') = datetime(current_time,'start of day','-0 day') EXCEPT SELECT prescriptions.drug FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10039831 ) AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of day') = datetime(current_time,'start of day','-1 day')
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT d.drug_id) AS new_drugs FROM patient p JOIN prescription pr ON p.patient_id = pr.patient_id JOIN drug d ON pr.drug_id = d.drug_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10039831 AND pr.prescription_date >= CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '1 day' AND pr.prescription_date < CURRENT_DATE;

question: Has patient 10027445 had any medication prescribed since 07/2100?

question: Get me the top four most frequent drugs that patients were prescribed in the same month after being diagnosed with other place in hospital as the place of occurrence of the external cause throughout this year.
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'other place in hospital as the place of occurrence of the external cause' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.starttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4
generated_sql: SELECT d.name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM drugs d JOIN patient_diagnoses pd ON d.id = pd.diagnosis_id JOIN patient_prescriptions pp ON pd.patient_id = pp.patient_id WHERE pp.date_prescribed BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31' GROUP BY d.name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 4;

question: Calculate the number of patients who were discharged from the hospital during this year.
true_query: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT admissions.subject_id ) FROM admissions WHERE admissions.dischtime is NOT NULL AND datetime(admissions.dischtime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year')
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p.id) FROM patient p JOIN patient_discharge pd ON p.id = pd.patient_id WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM pd.discharge_date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE);

question: How many hours have elapsed since the first time in the current hospital visit patient 10021487 received a lab test for bilirubin, total, ascites?
true_query: SELECT 24 * ( strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J', labevents.charttime) ) FROM labevents WHERE labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'bilirubin, total, ascites' ) AND labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10021487 AND admissions.dischtime IS NULL ) ORDER BY labevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT (SELECT date_trunc('day', MAX(p.laboratory_test_date)) FROM patient p WHERE p.id = 10021487 AND p.laboratory_test_name ILIKE '%bilirubin%total%ascites%') AS last_test_date, CURRENT_DATE AS now, (now - last_test_date) AS days_since_last_test;

question: Did patient 10018081 have any medication prescribed on their last hospital encounter?

question: What was the name of the diagnosis that patient 10018081 received for the last time since 2100?

question: Retrieve patient 10018423's monthly minimum weight since 03/2100.
true_query: SELECT MIN(chartevents.valuenum) FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10018423 ) ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'daily weight' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',chartevents.charttime) >= '2100-03' GROUP BY strftime('%Y-%m',chartevents.charttime)

question: What was the total of calcium acetate that patient 10021938 had been prescribed on the last hospital visit?

question: Tell me the length of time in days for patient 10010471's first stay in the ICU.
true_query: SELECT strftime('%J', icustays.outtime) - strftime('%J', icustays.intime) FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10010471 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime ASC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT (o.discharge_date - i.admission_date) AS length_of_stay FROM patient p JOIN admission a ON p.patient_id = a.patient_id JOIN icu_stay i ON a.admission_id = i.admission_id LEFT JOIN discharge_date d ON a.discharge_id = d.discharge_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10010471 LIMIT 1;

question: When was the last time patient 10012552 was measured heart rate greater than 78.0 in the first ICU visit?

question: Give me patient 10025612's total amount of or crystalloid intake input.

question: What are the five frequently tested specimens for patients that received insertion of intraluminal device into inferior vena cava, percutaneous approach previously within the same hospital visit since 2100?
true_query: SELECT T3.spec_type_desc FROM ( SELECT T2.spec_type_desc, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'insertion of intraluminal device into inferior vena cava, percutaneous approach' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc, microbiologyevents.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',microbiologyevents.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.spec_type_desc ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5
generated_sql: SELECT s.name AS specimen_name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM specimens s JOIN (SELECT p.patient_id, s.name AS specimen_name FROM patients p JOIN (SELECT patient_id, SPECIMEN_ID, name FROM specimens WHERE procedure_code = 'IVC-IP') AS s ON p.patient_id = s.patient_id GROUP BY p.patient_id, s.name HAVING COUNT(*) > 1) AS ss ON s.name = ss.specimen_name GROUP BY s.name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 5;

question: What are the four most frequently ordered medications that patients in their 20s were prescribed in the same month after they were diagnosed with tobacco use disorder?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'tobacco use disorder' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE admissions.age BETWEEN 20 AND 29 ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.starttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4
generated_sql: SELECT m.name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM medications m JOIN patients p ON m.id = p.medication JOIN patient_diagnosis pd ON p.id = pd.patient_id WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM pd.diagnosis_date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE - interval '10 years') AND EXTRACT(MONTH FROM pd.diagnosis_date) = EXTRACT(MONTH FROM CURRENT_DATE - interval '10 months') AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM p.birth_date) BETWEEN EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE - interval '20 years') AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE - interval '10 years') GROUP BY m.name ORDER BY frequency DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 4;

question: How much is the cost of the family history of malignant neoplasm of trachea, bronchus, and lung diagnosing?

question: Can you list patient 10031404's monthly average weight?

question: Show me the top five most common treatments for patients aged 20s since 2100.
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T1.icd_code FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age BETWEEN 20 AND 29 ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100' GROUP BY procedures_icd.icd_code ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 5 )

question: Was patient 10007818 on any solution in the first ICU stay?

question: List the top five most common events that happened throughout this year.

question: For patients previously diagnosed with migraine with aura, without mention of intractable migraine without mention of status migrainosus , what were the three most frequent specimens tested within 2 months afterward?

question: Could you list the four diagnoses that had the highest 6-month mortality rate?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T4.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM ( SELECT T1.icd_code, ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/2 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) as C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/2 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id ) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 ) AS T4 WHERE T4.C3 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.name, d.code, (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM patient p JOIN procedure_diagnosis pd ON p.id = pd.patient_id JOIN diagnosis d2 ON pd.diagnosis_id = d2.id WHERE d2.id = d.id AND p.date_died >= CURRENT_DATE - interval '6 months') AS mortality_count, (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM patient p JOIN procedure_diagnosis pd ON p.id = pd.patient_id JOIN diagnosis d2 ON pd.diagnosis_id = d2.id WHERE d2.id = d.id AND p.date_died >= CURRENT_DATE - interval '6 months') * 100.0 / NULLIF((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM patient), 0) AS mortality_rate FROM diagnosis d ORDER BY mortality_rate DESC LIMIT 4;

question: For patients who were diagnosed with duodenitis, without mention of hemorrhage in 2100, what are the top three most common medications that followed afterward in the same month?

question: Fetch the top four most frequent procedures that were administered to patients within 2 months after they had continuous invasive mechanical ventilation for 96 consecutive hours or more since 2100.

question: List the five most frequent diagnoses a patient was diagnosed with within 2 months after receiving central venous catheter placement with guidance since 1 year ago.

question: Get me the top four most frequent drugs that patients were prescribed in the same month after being diagnosed with accidental cut, puncture, perforation or hemorrhage during heart catheterization in 2100.

generated_sql: SELECT d.name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM drugs d JOIN patient_prescriptions p ON d.id = p.drug_id WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM p.date_prescribed) = 2100 AND p.patient_id IN (SELECT patient_id FROM patient_diagnoses WHERE diagnosis_id IN (SELECT diagnosis_id FROM diagnoses WHERE name IN ('accidental cut', 'puncture', 'perforation', 'hemorrhage'))) GROUP BY d.name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 4;

question: Show me the top five most commonly prescribed drugs during the same hospital encounter to the patients aged 40s after diagnosed with epilepsy, unspecified, not intractable, without status epilepticus.

question: Show me the top three diagnoses with the highest 3-month mortality rate.
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T4.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM ( SELECT T1.icd_code, ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/4 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) as C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/4 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id ) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 ) AS T4 WHERE T4.C3 <= 3 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.name, CAST(COUNT(DISTINCT c.id) AS FLOAT) / NULLIF(COUNT(DISTINCT e.id), 0) AS mortality_rate FROM diagnosis d JOIN patient p ON p.diagnosis = d.id JOIN encounter e ON e.patient = p.id JOIN care_plan c ON c.patient = p.id AND c.start_date <= e.date AND (c.end_date >= e.date OR c.end_date IS NULL) WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM e.date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) - 3 GROUP BY d.name ORDER BY mortality_rate DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 3;

question: What are the four most frequent diagnoses that patients were diagnosed within the same month after having received a extirpation of matter from left lower lobe bronchus, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic procedure since 2100?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'extirpation of matter from left lower lobe bronchus, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.diagnosis, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM dg d JOIN brs b ON d.patient = b.patient AND d.visit = b.visit JOIN lls l ON b.patient = l.patient AND b.visit = l.visit AND EXTRACT(MONTH FROM l.date) = EXTRACT(MONTH FROM d.date) AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM l.date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM d.date) - 1 WHERE b.procedure = 'extirpation of matter from left lower lobe bronchus' AND l.anatomical = 'natural or artificial opening endoscopic procedure' AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM l.date) >= 2010 GROUP BY d.diagnosis ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 4;

question: Could you retrieve the top five diagnoses that have the highest 3-month mortality rate?

question: Can you tell me which four diagnoses have the highest 3-month mortality rate?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T4.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM ( SELECT T1.icd_code, ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/4 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) as C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/4 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id ) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 ) AS T4 WHERE T4.C3 <= 4 )

question: Could you list the three diagnoses that had the highest 3-month mortality rate?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T4.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM ( SELECT T1.icd_code, ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/4 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) as C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/4 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id ) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 ) AS T4 WHERE T4.C3 <= 3 )

question: What were the top five most frequent diagnoses since 1 year ago with which patients were diagnosed after receiving extirpation of matter from left lower lobe bronchus, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic during the same month?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'extirpation of matter from left lower lobe bronchus, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM diagnoses d JOIN procedures p ON d.procedure_id = p.id JOIN patient_procedures pp ON p.id = pp.procedure_id WHERE pp.date >= (CURRENT_DATE - interval '1 year') AND d.name IN (SELECT name FROM diagnoses WHERE procedure_id IN (SELECT id FROM procedures WHERE type = 'Extirpation of matter from left lower lobe bronchus')) AND (p.type = 'Natural or artificial opening endoscopic' OR p.type = 'Endoscopic procedure') GROUP BY d.name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 5;

question: Among patients in their 50s since 2100, what were the top five most frequent diagnoses?

question: Show me the top four diagnoses with the highest 3-month mortality rate.
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T4.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM ( SELECT T1.icd_code, ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/4 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) as C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/4 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id ) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 ) AS T4 WHERE T4.C3 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.code, d.name, CAST(COUNT(CASE WHEN e.status = 'death' THEN 1 END) AS FLOAT) / NULLIF(COUNT(e.id), 0) * 3 AS mortality_rate FROM diagnoses d JOIN episodes e ON d.code = e.diagnosis_code WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM e.date) >= EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) - 3 GROUP BY d.code, d.name ORDER BY mortality_rate DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 4;

question: Compared to yesterday, what new prescriptions were given to patient 10018081 today?

question: What were the top five most common diagnoses during this year?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T1.icd_code FROM ( SELECT diagnoses_icd.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM diagnoses_icd WHERE datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') GROUP BY diagnoses_icd.icd_code ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 5 )

question: How many patients were given insulin human regular prescriptions since 2100?

question: How many patients in 2100 were diagnosed with cyst and pseudocyst of pancreas during the same month after the first diagnosis with other and unspecified alcohol dependence, in remission?
true_query: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT T1.subject_id ) FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'other and unspecified alcohol dependence, in remission' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'cyst and pseudocyst of pancreas' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month')
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM patient_data p WHERE date_part('year', age(CURRENT_DATE, p.diagnosis_date)) = 2010 AND p.diagnosis_type_code IN ('C173','C174') AND p.remission_date IS NOT NULL AND date_part('month', age(CURRENT_DATE, p.remission_date)) = date_part('month', age(CURRENT_DATE, p.diagnosis_date));

question: What are the five commonly ordered medications that patients aged 50s were prescribed within 2 months after diagnosed with long-term (current) use of insulin?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'long-term (current) use of insulin' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE admissions.age BETWEEN 50 AND 59 ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T2.starttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5
generated_sql: SELECT m.drug_name, COUNT(*) AS COUNT FROM patient_prescriptions pp JOIN medications m ON pp.drug_id = m.drug_id WHERE pp.patient_id IN (SELECT patient_id FROM patient_prescriptions WHERE prescription_date BETWEEN CURRENT_DATE - interval '2 month' AND CURRENT_DATE AND medication_type_code = 'I') GROUP BY m.drug_name ORDER BY COUNT DESC LIMIT 5;

question: How much does patient 10006580's systolic blood pressure differ from the last value measured on the last ICU visit compared to the first value measured on the last ICU visit?
true_query: SELECT ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10006580 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'arterial blood pressure systolic' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1 ) - ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10006580 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'arterial blood pressure systolic' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 )
result: [{"( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10006580 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'arterial blood pressure systolic' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1 ) - ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10006580 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'arterial blood pressure systolic' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 )": None}]
generated_sql: SELECT (p.systolic_blood_pressure - lag(p.systolic_blood_pressure) OVER (PARTITION BY p.patient_id ORDER BY p.icu_stay_id)) AS pressure_difference FROM patient p JOIN (SELECT patient_id, icu_stay_id, lag(systolic_blood_pressure) OVER (PARTITION BY patient_id ORDER BY icu_stay_id)) AS prev_pressure ON p.patient_id = prev_pressure.patient_id AND p.icu_stay_id = prev_pressure.icu_stay_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10006580;

question: Tell me the name of the drug which patient 10017492 was prescribed within 2 days after having had a spinal tap procedure?

question: I would like to know the top three diagnoses that have the highest 6-month mortality rate.
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T4.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM ( SELECT T1.icd_code, ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/2 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) as C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/2 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id ) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 ) AS T4 WHERE T4.C3 <= 3 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.diagnosis, SUM(CASE WHEN date_part('year', age(CURRENT_DATE, p.date_of_death)) <= 6 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)::FLOAT / NULLIF(COUNT(p.date_of_death), 0) AS mortality_rate FROM patient p JOIN diagnosis d ON p.diagnosis_id = d.diagnosis_id GROUP BY d.diagnosis ORDER BY mortality_rate DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 3;

question: When was the first time that patient 10015272 in 06/this year was given a asparate aminotransferase (ast) lab test?
true_query: SELECT labevents.charttime FROM labevents WHERE labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'asparate aminotransferase (ast)' ) AND labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10015272 ) AND datetime(labevents.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',labevents.charttime) = '06' ORDER BY labevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT MIN(lab_test_date) FROM patient_lab_tests WHERE patient_id = 10015272 AND MONTH(lab_test_date) = 6 AND YEAR(lab_test_date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) GROUP BY patient_id HAVING COUNT(ast) >= 1;

question: Has patient 10019777 gone to an emergency room throughout this year?

question: When was the first time of input time of patient 10018081 on this month/29?

generated_sql: SELECT MIN(t.time) AS earliest_time FROM times t WHERE t.patient = 10018081 AND EXTRACT(MONTH FROM t.time) = 1 AND EXTRACT(DAY FROM t.time) = 29;

question: What was in 03/this year patient 10004235's minimum alveolar-arterial gradient value?

question: Has patient 10020944 come to the ER since 1 year ago?

question: What was the last time of input of patient 10021487 since 03/20/2100?

question: What are the top four commonly ordered treatments for patients in their 20s?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T1.icd_code FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age BETWEEN 20 AND 29 ) GROUP BY procedures_icd.icd_code ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT t.name, COUNT(*) AS COUNT FROM treatments t JOIN patient_treatments pt ON t.id = pt.treatment_id JOIN patients p ON pt.patient_id = p.id WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM AGE(p.date_of_birth)) BETWEEN 20 AND 29 GROUP BY t.name ORDER BY COUNT DESC LIMIT 4;

question: What was the name of the organism found in patient 10021487's first bronchoalveolar lavage microbiological test since 09/2100?

question: When did last patient 10014729 have the minimum value of albumin, pleural in 03/2100?

question: What was the last drug prescribed in 02/this year to patient 10020187?

question: What are the charges for a procedure called bypass coronary artery, one artery from right internal mammary with autologous arterial tissue, open approach?
true_query: SELECT DISTINCT cost.cost FROM cost WHERE cost.event_type = 'procedures_icd' AND cost.event_id IN ( SELECT procedures_icd.row_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'bypass coronary artery, one artery from right internal mammary with autologous arterial tissue, open approach' ) )
generated_sql: SELECT procedure.procedure_name, procedure.procedure_charges, patient.patient_name, patient.patient_age, patient.patient_gender FROM procedure JOIN patient_procedure ON procedure.procedure_id = patient_procedure.procedure_id JOIN patient ON patient_procedure.patient_id = patient.patient_id WHERE procedure.procedure_name ILIKE '%bypass%coronary%artery%' OR procedure.procedure_name ILIKE '%one%artery%' OR procedure.procedure_name ILIKE '%right%internal%mammary%' OR procedure.procedure_name ILIKE '%autologous%arterial%tissue%' OR procedure.procedure_name ILIKE '%open%approach%' ORDER BY procedure.procedure_charges NULLS LAST;

question: What percentile is the creatinine value of 0.6 among patients of the same age as patient 10008454 on their last hospital encounter?
true_query: SELECT DISTINCT T1.C1 FROM ( SELECT labevents.valuenum, PERCENT_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY labevents.valuenum ) AS C1 FROM labevents WHERE labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'creatinine' ) AND labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age = ( SELECT admissions.age FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10008454 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime DESC LIMIT 1 ) ) ) AS T1 WHERE T1.valuenum = 0.6
generated_sql: SELECT percentile_cont(0.6) within GROUP (ORDER BY creatinine_value) AS percentile_06 FROM patient_10008454_last_hospital_encounter;

question: Since 2100, what are the top five most frequent drugs prescribed to patients within 2 months after the diagnosis of atrial flutter?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'atrial flutter' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',prescriptions.starttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T2.starttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5
generated_sql: SELECT d.drug_name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM diagnoses dg JOIN prescriptions p ON dg.patient_id = p.patient_id JOIN drugs d ON p.drug_id = d.drug_id WHERE dg.diagnosis_code = 'A000' AND dg.diagnosis_date < '2020-01-01' GROUP BY d.drug_name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 5;

question: What was the name of the output that patient 10027445 had last since 06/02/2100?

question: In relation to others of the same age, where does a ph value of 7.34 for patient 10026255 rank in percentiles in their first hospital visit?
true_query: SELECT DISTINCT T1.C1 FROM ( SELECT labevents.valuenum, PERCENT_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY labevents.valuenum ) AS C1 FROM labevents WHERE labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'ph' ) AND labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age = ( SELECT admissions.age FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10026255 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1 ) ) ) AS T1 WHERE T1.valuenum = 7.34
generated_sql: SELECT p.ph, percent_rank() OVER (ORDER BY p.ph) AS percentile_rank FROM patient p WHERE p.patient_id = 10026255;

question: When was patient 10007818's mean blood pressure first measured less than 75.0 since 241 days ago?

question: Is patient 10010471's sodium value last measured on the last hospital visit greater than the value first measured on the last hospital visit?
true_query: SELECT ( SELECT labevents.valuenum FROM labevents WHERE labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10010471 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'sodium' ) ORDER BY labevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1 ) > ( SELECT labevents.valuenum FROM labevents WHERE labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10010471 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'sodium' ) ORDER BY labevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 )
result: [{"( SELECT labevents.valuenum FROM labevents WHERE labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10010471 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'sodium' ) ORDER BY labevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1 ) > ( SELECT labevents.valuenum FROM labevents WHERE labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10010471 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'sodium' ) ORDER BY labevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 )": None}]
generated_sql: SELECT (SELECT CAST(sodium_last AS FLOAT) FROM patient_sodium_history WHERE patient_id = 10010471 ORDER BY date_trunc('day', sodium_date) DESC LIMIT 1) > (SELECT CAST(sodium_first AS FLOAT) FROM patient_sodium_history WHERE patient_id = 10010471 ORDER BY date_trunc('day', sodium_date) ASC LIMIT 1) AS sodium_comparison;

question: Since the last time patient 10021487 was diagnosed with alcohol abuse, unspecified on their current hospital visit, how many hours have passed?

question: What was the name of the procedure that was given two or more times to patient 10007795 since 12 months ago?

question: Retrieve the yearly minimum amount of patient 10037975's pre-admission/non-icu intake input.

question: Please list out the monthly maximum weight of patient 10039997 in the first hospital encounter.

question: What was the total dose of aspirin patient 10017492 had been prescribed during the last hospital visit?

question: Provide a list of the four most common diagnoses that patients were diagnosed with within 2 months after undergoing the enteral infusion of concentrated nutritional substances procedure in 2100.
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'enteral infusion of concentrated nutritional substances' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.disease_name, COUNT(*) AS disease_count FROM ei_diagnosis d JOIN ei_procedure e ON d.procedure_id = e.procedure_id JOIN patient_diagnosis p ON d.diagnosis_id = p.diagnosis_id WHERE e.procedure_date >= 2100-01-01 AND e.procedure_date < 2100-12-31 GROUP BY d.disease_name ORDER BY disease_count DESC LIMIT 4;

question: What are the top four most frequently ordered lab tests for patients within 2 months after being diagnosed with acute edema of lung, unspecified?
true_query: SELECT d_labitems.label FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.itemid IN ( SELECT T3.itemid FROM ( SELECT T2.itemid, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'acute edema of lung, unspecified' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, labevents.itemid, labevents.charttime FROM labevents JOIN admissions ON labevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.itemid ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT p.patient_id, p.patient_first_name, p.patient_last_name, o.order_date, o.order_number, t.test_name, COUNT(*) AS test_count FROM patient p JOIN order o ON p.patient_id = o.order_patient JOIN order_item oi ON o.order_id = oi.order_item_order JOIN test t ON oi.order_item_test = t.test_id WHERE p.patient_patient_status = 'Active' AND o.order_date BETWEEN (SELECT patient_last_diagnosis_date FROM patient WHERE patient_id = p.patient_id) AND (SELECT patient_last_diagnosis_date FROM patient WHERE patient_id = p.patient_id) + interval '60 days' AND t.test_name ilike '%lab%' GROUP BY p.patient_id, p.patient_first_name, p.patient_last_name, o.order_date, o.order_number, t.test_name ORDER BY test_count DESC LIMIT 4;

question: In the last hospital visit, how much gemfibrozil has been prescribed to patient 10007795 in total?

question: What are the four most often performed treatments for patients aged 20s in 2100?

question: Count the number of patients who received other endoscopy of small intestine within 2 months after being diagnosed with alcohol abuse, unspecified since 2100.
true_query: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT T1.subject_id ) FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'alcohol abuse, unspecified' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'other endoscopy of small intestine' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month')
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT a.patient_id) AS number_of_patients FROM alcohol_abuse a JOIN alcohol_abuse_endoscopy b ON a.patient_id = b.patient_id JOIN alcohol_abuse_endoscopy_small_intestine c ON b.patient_id = c.patient_id WHERE a.patient_id NOT IN (SELECT patient_id FROM alcohol_abuse_endoscopy_2021) AND c.endoscopy_date BETWEEN a.diagnosis_date AND a.diagnosis_date + interval '60 days';

question: Tell me the top three most frequent procedures that patients were given within 2 months after receiving dilation of lower esophagus with intraluminal device, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic.
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'dilation of lower esophagus with intraluminal device, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3 )
generated_sql: SELECT p.name, COUNT(*) AS procedure_count FROM procedures p JOIN (SELECT c.patient_id FROM procedures c WHERE c.procedure_id IN (SELECT procedure_id FROM procedures WHERE name ILIKE '%dilation%lower%esophagus%with%intraluminal%device%') AND c.date_procedure > (CURRENT_DATE - interval '2 months') GROUP BY c.patient_id) AS subquery ON p.patient_id = subquery.patient_id GROUP BY p.name LIMIT 3;

question: What was the first time that the respiratory rate of patient 10021487 was, on their last ICU visit, less than 27.0?
true_query: SELECT chartevents.charttime FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10021487 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'respiratory rate' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) AND chartevents.valuenum < 27.0 ORDER BY chartevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1

question: Was any nacl 0.9% medication provided to patient 10027602 on their first ICU stay?

question: Can you tell me the top five diagnoses with the highest 6-month mortality rate?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T4.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM ( SELECT T1.icd_code, ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/2 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) as C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/2 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id ) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 ) AS T4 WHERE T4.C3 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.name, cume_dist() OVER (ORDER BY d.name) AS cumulative_distribution FROM diagnosis d ORDER BY cumulative_distribution DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 5;

question: What are the five most common laboratory tests undertaken by patients in the same month following a diagnosis of personal history of other venous thrombosis and embolism since 1 year ago?
true_query: SELECT d_labitems.label FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.itemid IN ( SELECT T3.itemid FROM ( SELECT T2.itemid, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'personal history of other venous thrombosis and embolism' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, labevents.itemid, labevents.charttime FROM labevents JOIN admissions ON labevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(labevents.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.itemid ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT date_trunc('month', age(CURRENT_DATE, c.diagnosis_date)) AS MONTH, COUNT(*) AS num_patients FROM clinical c WHERE date_part('year', age(CURRENT_DATE, c.diagnosis_date)) = 1 AND c.personal_history_of_venous_thrombosis = TRUE AND c.personal_history_of_embolism = TRUE GROUP BY MONTH ORDER BY MONTH, num_patients DESC LIMIT 5;

question: Show me the top four most frequent drugs that patients were prescribed during the same hospital visit after being diagnosed with hemorrhage complicating a procedure in this year.
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'hemorrhage complicating a procedure' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4
generated_sql: SELECT p.patient_name, d.drug_name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM patient p JOIN prescription pr ON p.patient_id = pr.patient_id JOIN drug d ON pr.drug_id = d.drug_id WHERE p.patient_id IN (SELECT patient_id FROM patient WHERE patient_name ilike '%hemorrhage%complicating%procedure%' AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM procedure_date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE)) GROUP BY p.patient_name, d.drug_name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 4;

question: Could you list the four diagnoses that had the highest 3-month mortality rate?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T4.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM ( SELECT T1.icd_code, ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/4 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) as C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/4 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id ) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 ) AS T4 WHERE T4.C3 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.name, d.code, m.date, COUNT(*)::FLOAT / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM patients p JOIN visits v ON p.id = v.patient_id WHERE date_part('year', v.date) = 2017 AND date_part('month', v.date) = 9) AS mortality_rate FROM diagnoses d JOIN patient_diagnoses pd ON d.code = pd.diagnosis_code JOIN patients p ON pd.patient_id = p.id JOIN visits v ON p.id = v.patient_id WHERE date_part('year', v.date) = 2017 AND date_part('month', v.date) = 9 AND date_part('day', v.date) > 27 GROUP BY d.name, d.code, m.date ORDER BY mortality_rate DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 4;

question: What are the four frequently prescribed medications for patients diagnosed with bipolar disorder, unspecified previously in the same hospital encounter?

question: In 2100, what are the top five most common specimens tested for patients previously diagnosed with personal history of self-harm within the same month?

question: What was the name of the medication that patient 10012552 was prescribed in the same hospital encounter after receiving a single internal mammary-coronary artery bypass procedure in 04/this year?
true_query: SELECT T2.drug FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.charttime, procedures_icd.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'single internal mammary-coronary artery bypass' ) AND procedures_icd.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10012552 ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',procedures_icd.charttime) = '04' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10012552 ) AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '04' ) AS T2 ON T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime
generated_sql: SELECT m.name FROM medications m JOIN patient_medications pm ON m.id = pm.medication_id JOIN patients p ON pm.patient_id = p.id JOIN procedures pr ON p.id = pr.patient_id JOIN hospital_procedures hp ON pr.procedure_id = hp.procedure_id WHERE p.id = 10012552 AND hp.procedure_id IN (SELECT procedure_id FROM procedures WHERE date_part('year', procedure_date) = date_part('year', CURRENT_DATE) - 1) GROUP BY procedure_id HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT patient_id) = 1) ORDER BY m.name NULLS LAST;

question: Could you tell me the average total cost in a hospital where methylprednisolone sodium succ is used in 2100?
true_query: SELECT AVG(T1.C1) FROM ( SELECT SUM(cost.cost) AS C1 FROM cost WHERE cost.hadm_id IN ( SELECT prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'methylprednisolone sodium succ' ) AND strftime('%Y',cost.chargetime) = '2100' GROUP BY cost.hadm_id ) AS T1
generated_sql: SELECT AVG(total_cost) FROM drugs_pharmacy WHERE drug_name ilike '%methylprednisolone%sodium%succ%' AND year_of_manufacture = 2021;

question: Among patients who underwent ileostomy, not otherwise specified since 2100, what were the top four most common procedures that followed within the same month?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'ileostomy, not otherwise specified' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT date_trunc('month', s.surgery_date) AS MONTH, COUNT(*) AS procedure_count, s.surgeon_name FROM surgery s WHERE date_part('year', s.surgery_date) >= 2010 AND date_part('year', s.surgery_date) < 2020 AND i.patient_id = s.patient_id AND i.ileostomy = TRUE GROUP BY MONTH, s.surgeon_name ORDER BY procedure_count DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 4;

question: What are the five most common treatments for patients who are 30s?

question: In 2100, what are the top four most frequently tested specimens for patients during the same month after receiving introduction of other therapeutic substance into heart, open approach?
true_query: SELECT T3.spec_type_desc FROM ( SELECT T2.spec_type_desc, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'introduction of other therapeutic substance into heart, open approach' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc, microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',microbiologyevents.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.spec_type_desc ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4
generated_sql: SELECT s.species_name, COUNT(*) AS number_of_tests FROM Species s JOIN Tests t ON s.species_id = t.species_id WHERE EXTRACT(MONTH FROM t.test_date) = 7 AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM t.test_date) = 2100 AND t.test_type = 'open approach' AND t.exposure_type = 'introduction of other therapeutic substance into heart' GROUP BY s.species_name ORDER BY number_of_tests DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 4;

question: What drugs have been added to patient 10018081's prescription today compared to yesterday?
