question: When patient 10027445 was prescribed for the first time in 09/this year docusate sodium and furosemide at the same time?
true_query: SELECT T1.starttime FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'docusate sodium' AND admissions.subject_id = 10027445 AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '09' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'furosemide' AND admissions.subject_id = 10027445 AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '09' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE datetime(T1.starttime) = datetime(T2.starttime) ORDER BY T1.starttime ASC LIMIT 1

question: Since 2100, what are the top three most common microbiology tests that patients were diagnosed with after the diagnosis of esophageal varices in diseases classified elsewhere, with bleeding within 2 months?
true_query: SELECT T3.test_name FROM ( SELECT T2.test_name, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'esophageal varices in diseases classified elsewhere, with bleeding' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.test_name, microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',microbiologyevents.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.test_name ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3

question: What percentile is the value of the free calcium of 1.06 among patients of the same age as patient 10026255 in the first hospital visit?

question: How many patients were diagnosed with migraine with aura, without mention of intractable migraine without mention of status migrainosus during the same hospital visit after they were first diagnosed with street and highway accidents since 2100?
true_query: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT T1.subject_id ) FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'street and highway accidents' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'migraine with aura, without mention of intractable migraine without mention of status migrainosus' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id

question: Since 2100, what are the top three most frequently taken specimens for patients within 2 months after receiving percutaneous [endoscopic] gastrostomy [peg]?
true_query: SELECT T3.spec_type_desc FROM ( SELECT T2.spec_type_desc, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'percutaneous [endoscopic] gastrostomy [peg]' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc, microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',microbiologyevents.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.spec_type_desc ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3

question: List the top five diagnoses that have the highest 3-month mortality rate.
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T4.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM ( SELECT T1.icd_code, ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/4 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) as C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/4 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id ) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 ) AS T4 WHERE T4.C3 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.name, SUM(CASE WHEN c.date_of_death BETWEEN c.date_of_birth AND c.date_of_birth + interval '3 months' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)::FLOAT / NULLIF(COUNT(c.id), 0) AS mortality_rate FROM diagnosis d JOIN patient_diagnosis pd ON d.id = pd.diagnosis_id JOIN patient p ON pd.patient_id = p.id JOIN case_data c ON p.id = c.patient_id GROUP BY d.name ORDER BY mortality_rate DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 5;

question: What are the five most commonly prescribed medications for patients who were previously diagnosed with personal history of transient ischemic attack (tia), and cerebral infarction without residual deficits during the same hospital visit, since 1 year ago?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'personal history of transient ischemic attack (tia), and cerebral infarction without residual deficits' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(prescriptions.starttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5
generated_sql: SELECT m.drug_name, COUNT(*) AS occurrence_count FROM patient_visits pv JOIN medications m ON pv.medication_id = m.medication_id WHERE pv.patient_id IN (SELECT patient_id FROM patient_visits WHERE date_visit > CURRENT_DATE - interval '1 year' AND tia = TRUE AND cerebral_infarction = TRUE AND residual_deficits = FALSE) GROUP BY m.drug_name ORDER BY occurrence_count DESC LIMIT 5;

generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT(d.id)) FROM drugs d JOIN patient_drug_prescriptions pdp ON d.id = pdp.drug_id WHERE pdp.patient_id = 10014078 AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM pdp.date_prescribed) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) - 1;

question: What were the top four most frequent diagnoses that followed within 2 months for those patients who received percutaneous abdominal drainage?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'percutaneous abdominal drainage' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.diagnosis, d.diagnosis_date, lag(d.diagnosis, 2) OVER (PARTITION BY p.patient_id ORDER BY d.diagnosis_date) AS previous_diagnosis FROM patient p JOIN diagnosis d ON p.patient_id = d.patient_id WHERE p.surgeon_name ilike '%percutaneous%abdominal%drainage%' ORDER BY d.diagnosis_date NULLS LAST;

question: Retrieve the top four most common diagnoses in 2100?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T1.icd_code FROM ( SELECT diagnoses_icd.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM diagnoses_icd WHERE strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' GROUP BY diagnoses_icd.icd_code ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.diagnosis, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM diagnoses d WHERE d.year = 2100 GROUP BY d.diagnosis ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 4;

question: In 2100, what are the top four most frequent procedures that patients received within 2 months after being diagnosed with subdural hemorrhage following injury without mention of open intracranial wound, with no loss of consciousness?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'subdural hemorrhage following injury without mention of open intracranial wound, with no loss of consciousness' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT p.name, pr.name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM patient p JOIN procedure pr ON p.id = pr.patient_id JOIN diagnosis d ON p.id = d.patient_id WHERE d.diagnosis ilike '%subdural%hemorrhage%' AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM procedure_report pr2 WHERE pr2.patient_id = p.id AND pr2.procedure_id = pr.id AND pr2.report_date BETWEEN pr.date_performed AND (pr.date_performed + interval '60 days') AND pr2.report_text ilike '%open%intracranial%wound%') AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM patient_report pr3 WHERE pr3.patient_id = p.id AND pr3.report_date BETWEEN pr.date_performed AND (pr.date_performed + interval '60 days') AND pr3.report_text ilike '%loss%of%consciousness%') GROUP BY p.name, pr.name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 4;

question: How many times did the percutaneous [endoscopic] gastrostomy [peg] procedure take place throughout this year?

question: So how many days have passed since patient 10018081's last other and unspecified hyperlipidemia diagnosis on their current hospital visit?

question: How much does a hospital typically spend average on a drug named fentanyl patch since 2100?

question: What are the three diagnoses with the lowest 6-month survival rate?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T4.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM ( SELECT T1.icd_code, ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/2 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) as C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/2 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id ) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 ) AS T4 WHERE T4.C3 <= 3 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.name, (COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN c.survived_6_months THEN c.patient_id END)::FLOAT / NULLIF(COUNT(c.patient_id), 0)) AS survival_rate FROM diagnoses d JOIN cancer_patients c ON d.id = c.diagnosis_id WHERE c.survived_6_months IS NOT NULL AND c.removed_at IS NULL GROUP BY d.name ORDER BY survival_rate DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 3;

question: In 2100, what are the top four most frequently taken specimens for patients within 2 months after receiving bypass coronary artery, three arteries from aorta with autologous venous tissue, open approach?
true_query: SELECT T3.spec_type_desc FROM ( SELECT T2.spec_type_desc, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'bypass coronary artery, three arteries from aorta with autologous venous tissue, open approach' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc, microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',microbiologyevents.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.spec_type_desc ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4
generated_sql: SELECT s.name, COUNT(*) AS count FROM specimens s JOIN patient_surgeries ps ON s.patient_id = ps.patient_id WHERE ps.surgery_date >= CURRENT_DATE - interval '2 months' AND ps.surgery_type_code = 'B' AND ps.surgeon_id = 757071 AND ps.other_surgeons = '757071' AND ps.patient_id IN (SELECT patient_id FROM patient_surgeries WHERE surgery_date >= CURRENT_DATE - interval '3 months' AND surgery_type_code IN ('A', 'B', 'C')) GROUP BY s.name ORDER BY count DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 4;

question: List the top five most frequent microbiology tests that were given to patients after they were diagnosed with postprocedural hemorrhage of a circulatory system organ or structure following other circulatory system procedure in the same hospital visit.
true_query: SELECT T3.test_name FROM ( SELECT T2.test_name, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'postprocedural hemorrhage of a circulatory system organ or structure following other circulatory system procedure' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.test_name, microbiologyevents.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.test_name ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5
generated_sql: SELECT m.name AS test_name, COUNT(*) AS test_count FROM microbiology m JOIN patient_diagnoses pd ON m.name = pd.microbiology JOIN patient_procedures pp ON pd.patient_id = pp.patient_id JOIN procedure_details pd2 ON pp.procedure_id = pd2.procedure_id WHERE m.name IN (SELECT name FROM microbiology) AND pd.diagnosis_type = 'Postprocedural Hemorrhage' AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM pd.diagnosis_date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM pp.procedure_date) AND (pd.patient_id, pp.procedure_id) IN (SELECT patient_id, procedure_id FROM procedure_details) GROUP BY m.name ORDER BY test_count DESC LIMIT 5;

result: [{"( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10038081 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime DESC LIMIT 1 ) ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'daily weight' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 OFFSET 1 ) - ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10038081 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime DESC LIMIT 1 ) ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'daily weight' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 )": None}]
generated_sql: SELECT (w.weight - lag(w.weight) OVER (PARTITION BY p.patient_id ORDER BY v.visit_id)) AS weight_difference FROM patient p JOIN weight w ON p.patient_id = w.patient_id JOIN visit v ON w.visit_id = v.visit_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10038081;

question: When did patient 10007818 receive a mrsa screen microbiology test first in 07/2100?

question: Provide the daily maximum weight of patient 10031757 since 12 months ago.

question: So, the first asparate aminotransferase (ast) test result for the patient 10019172 was?

question: Count the number of patients who underwent a d-dimer lab test since 2100.
true_query: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT admissions.subject_id ) FROM admissions WHERE admissions.hadm_id IN ( SELECT labevents.hadm_id FROM labevents WHERE labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'd-dimer' ) AND strftime('%Y',labevents.charttime) >= '2100' )
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p.patient_id) AS total_patients FROM patient p JOIN lab_test lt ON p.patient_id = lt.patient_id WHERE lt.test_name = 'd-dimer' AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM lt.test_date) >= 2100;

question: What is the maximum cost to the hospital that involves nonalcoholic steatohepatitis (nash) since 2100?
true_query: SELECT MAX(T1.C1) FROM ( SELECT SUM(cost.cost) AS C1 FROM cost WHERE cost.hadm_id IN ( SELECT diagnoses_icd.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'nonalcoholic steatohepatitis (nash)' ) ) AND strftime('%Y',cost.chargetime) >= '2100' GROUP BY cost.hadm_id ) AS T1
generated_sql: SELECT MAX(cost_per_unit) FROM nash WHERE year >= 2010;

question: How many hours have passed since patient 10018081 got her last diagnosis of other and unspecified hyperlipidemia on their current hospital encounter?
true_query: SELECT 24 * ( strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J', diagnoses_icd.charttime) ) FROM diagnoses_icd WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'other and unspecified hyperlipidemia' ) AND diagnoses_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10018081 AND admissions.dischtime IS NULL ) ORDER BY diagnoses_icd.charttime DESC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT (CURRENT_TIME - LAG(e.admit_time, 1) OVER (PARTITION BY p.patient_id ORDER BY e.admit_time))/3600 AS hours_since_last_diagnosis FROM patient p JOIN encounter e ON p.patient_id = e.patient_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10018081;

question: Show me the top five most frequent diagnoses since 1 year ago.
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T1.icd_code FROM ( SELECT diagnoses_icd.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM diagnoses_icd WHERE datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') GROUP BY diagnoses_icd.icd_code ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.diagnosis, COUNT(d.diagnosis) AS frequency FROM Diagnosis d WHERE d.creation_date >= CURRENT_DATE - interval '1 year' GROUP BY d.diagnosis ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 5;

question: What is the total count of performance of cardiac output, continuous procedures that were done since 1 year ago?
true_query: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'performance of cardiac output, continuous' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year')
generated_sql: SELECT SUM(o.cardiac_output) AS total_cardiac_output FROM operating_data o WHERE o.date >= CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '1 year';

question: When did patient 10006053 have the minimum value of polys last on the first hospital stay?
true_query: SELECT labevents.charttime FROM labevents WHERE labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10006053 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1 ) AND labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'polys' ) ORDER BY labevents.valuenum ASC, labevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT date_trunc('day', m.stay_start_date) AS admission_date, min(p.polys) AS lowest_polys FROM patient_stays s JOIN patient_profiles p ON s.patient_id = p.patient_id WHERE s.patient_id = 10006053 AND s.hospital_id = 757071 GROUP BY admission_date;

question: How many patients were staying in med/surg/trauma in 2100?

question: Does patient 59275 have a travel history to another country?

question: What are the top four most common microbiology tests for people who were diagnosed with unspecified deficiency anemia earlier during the same month, in 2100?
true_query: SELECT T3.test_name FROM ( SELECT T2.test_name, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'unspecified deficiency anemia' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.test_name, microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',microbiologyevents.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.test_name ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(*) AS frequency, m.name AS test_name FROM unspecified_anemia ua JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT microbiology_test_id FROM unspecified_anemia WHERE date_trunc('month', diagnosis_date) = date_trunc('month', CURRENT_DATE) AND date_part('year', diagnosis_date) = 2100) AS subquery JOIN microbiology_tests m ON subquery.microbiology_test_id = m.id GROUP BY m.name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 4;

question: What percentile of the po2 value is 127.0 among patients of the same age as patient 10021487 on this hospital visit?
true_query: SELECT DISTINCT T1.C1 FROM ( SELECT labevents.valuenum, PERCENT_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY labevents.valuenum ) AS C1 FROM labevents WHERE labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'po2' ) AND labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age = ( SELECT admissions.age FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10021487 AND admissions.dischtime IS NULL ) ) ) AS T1 WHERE T1.valuenum = 127.0
generated_sql: SELECT percentile_cont(0.75) within GROUP (ORDER BY po2) AS percentile_75 FROM patient_data WHERE age = (SELECT age FROM patient_data WHERE patient_id = 10021487 AND hospital_visit_id = 757071);

question: Since 2100, what are the top five most common lab tests ordered for patients in the same month after acute respiratory failure with hypoxia?
true_query: SELECT d_labitems.label FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.itemid IN ( SELECT T3.itemid FROM ( SELECT T2.itemid, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'acute respiratory failure with hypoxia' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, labevents.itemid, labevents.charttime FROM labevents JOIN admissions ON labevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',labevents.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.itemid ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT date_trunc('month', onset_date) AS MONTH, COUNT(*) AS test_count, array_agg(DISTINCT test_code) AS test_codes FROM patient_episodes JOIN episode_diagnoses ON patient_episodes.id = episode_diagnoses.patient_episode_id JOIN test_orders ON patient_episodes.id = test_orders.patient_episode_id WHERE onset_date >= '2021-01-01' AND (outcome_date < '2021-01-01' OR outcome_date IS NULL) AND test_code IN ('ECG', 'ECHO', 'USG', 'CT', 'X-ray') GROUP BY MONTH ORDER BY test_count DESC LIMIT 5;

question: Count up how many times patient 10000032 was admitted to the ICU since 1 year ago.

question: Could you inform me of the minimum alkaline phosphatase value for patient 10018081 since 12/2100?

question: Has furosemide, lidocaine jelly 2% (urojet), or acetaminophen iv been prescribed in 04/last year for patient 10038992?

question: What was patient 10039997's daily average weight since 4 months ago?
true_query: SELECT AVG(chartevents.valuenum) FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10039997 ) ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'daily weight' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) AND datetime(chartevents.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-4 month') GROUP BY strftime('%Y-%m-%d',chartevents.charttime)

question: What's the weight difference of patient 10038081's body second measured on the last hospital visit compared to the value first measured on the last hospital visit?

question: Calculate patient 10007818's total input amount of fresh frozen plasma on 07/03/this year.
true_query: SELECT SUM(inputevents.totalamount) FROM inputevents WHERE inputevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10007818 ) ) AND inputevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'fresh frozen plasma' AND d_items.linksto = 'inputevents' ) AND datetime(inputevents.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m-%d',inputevents.starttime) = '07-03'
generated_sql: SELECT SUM(p.amount) AS total_amount FROM patient_plasma p WHERE p.patient_id = 10007818 AND p.collection_date >= '2023-07-03' AND p.collection_date < '2023-07-04';

question: Tell me the name of the drug patient 10002495 was prescribed within 2 days after having received a dilation of coronary artery, one artery with drug-eluting intraluminal device, percutaneous approach procedure in 06/this year?
true_query: SELECT T2.drug FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.charttime, procedures_icd.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'dilation of coronary artery, one artery with drug-eluting intraluminal device, percutaneous approach' ) AND procedures_icd.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10002495 ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',procedures_icd.charttime) = '06' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10002495 ) AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '06' ) AS T2 ON T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T2.starttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 day')
generated_sql: SELECT d.drug_name FROM patient_procedures pp JOIN procedures p ON pp.procedure_id = p.procedure_id JOIN drug_procedures dp ON p.procedure_id = dp.procedure_id JOIN drugs d ON dp.drug_id = d.drug_id WHERE pp.patient_id = 10002495 AND date_part('year', pp.procedure_date) = 2019 AND p.procedure_name = 'percutaneous approach' AND d.drug_eluting_intraluminal_device IS NOT NULL AND date_part('day', pp.procedure_date - interval '2 days') = date_part('day', CURRENT_DATE) AND date_part('month', pp.procedure_date - interval '2 days') = date_part('month', CURRENT_DATE);

question: What output did patient 10015860 generate first since 10/04/2100?
true_query: SELECT d_items.label FROM d_items WHERE d_items.itemid IN ( SELECT outputevents.itemid FROM outputevents WHERE outputevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10015860 ) ) AND strftime('%Y-%m-%d',outputevents.charttime) >= '2100-10-04' ORDER BY outputevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 )
generated_sql: SELECT p.first_name, p.last_name, p.date_of_birth FROM patient p WHERE p.id = 10015860 AND p.date_of_birth > '2021-10-04';

question: When were the drugs sodium chloride 0.9% and pantoprazole prescribed to patient 10036156 for the last time at the same time?
true_query: SELECT T1.starttime FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'sodium chloride 0.9%' AND admissions.subject_id = 10036156 ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'pantoprazole' AND admissions.subject_id = 10036156 ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE datetime(T1.starttime) = datetime(T2.starttime) ORDER BY T1.starttime DESC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT MAX(p.dispense_date) AS last_dispense_date FROM patient p JOIN patient_drug pd ON p.patient_id = pd.patient_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10036156 AND pd.drug_id IN (470876, 470969) AND p.deleted = FALSE;

question: What is the treatment that patient 10020740 was given two times since 05/2100?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T1.icd_code FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.icd_code, COUNT( procedures_icd.charttime ) AS C1 FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10020740 ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100-05' GROUP BY procedures_icd.icd_code ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 = 2 )
generated_sql: SELECT t.treatment, COUNT(*) AS num_treatments FROM treatments t WHERE t.patient_id = 10020740 AND t.date_given >= '2005-05-01' GROUP BY t.treatment HAVING COUNT(*) > 1;

question: Tell me the total acetaminophen dose that patient 10037975 has been prescribed?

question: When did patient 10014078 have his first microbiology test on the first hospital stay?

question: Tell me the four most common microbiology tests for patients who were previously diagnosed with fall on same level, unspecified, initial encounter during the same month since 2100.
true_query: SELECT T3.test_name FROM ( SELECT T2.test_name, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'fall on same level, unspecified, initial encounter' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.test_name, microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',microbiologyevents.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.test_name ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4

question: What are the top four most common diagnoses that patients were diagnosed with within 2 months after receiving partial hepatectomy's this year?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'partial hepatectomy' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.diagnosis, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM patient_diagnosis p JOIN patient_operation p2 ON p.patient_id = p2.patient_id JOIN diagnosis d2 ON p.diagnosis_id = d2.diagnosis_id WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM p2.operation_date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) AND p2.operation_type = 'partial hepatectomy' AND p2.operation_date >= CURRENT_DATE - interval '2 months' GROUP BY d.diagnosis ORDER BY frequency DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 4;

question: Show me the top four most frequent diagnoses that patients were diagnosed with within 2 months after receiving other electroshock therapy since 2100.
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'other electroshock therapy' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.diagnosis, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM patient_diagnoses pd JOIN treatments t ON pd.treatment_id = t.treatment_id JOIN electroshock_treatments e ON t.treatment_id = e.treatment_id JOIN patient_treatments pt ON e.patient_id = pt.patient_id JOIN diagnoses d ON pt.diagnosis_id = d.diagnosis_id WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM t.date_treated) >= 2021 AND pt.date_assigned <= (t.date_treated + interval '60 days') GROUP BY d.diagnosis ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 4;

question: What were the top three most frequent diagnoses in 2100 with which patients were diagnosed after receiving hemodialysis within 2 months?

generated_sql: SELECT p.patient_id, p.first_name, p.last_name, o.order_date, m.medication_name, m.dosage, r.route_name FROM patient p JOIN order o ON p.patient_id = o.patient_id JOIN order_detail od ON o.order_id = od.order_id JOIN medication m ON od.medication_id = m.medication_id JOIN route r ON m.route_id = r.route_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10004720 AND r.route_name = 'Oral' AND EXTRACT(MONTH FROM o.order_date) = EXTRACT(MONTH FROM CURRENT_DATE) AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM o.order_date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) ORDER BY o.order_date DESC LIMIT 1;

question: What is the percentile phosphate value of 3.3 among patients of the same age as patient 10024043 during their last hospital visit?
true_query: SELECT DISTINCT T1.C1 FROM ( SELECT labevents.valuenum, PERCENT_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY labevents.valuenum ) AS C1 FROM labevents WHERE labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'phosphate' ) AND labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age = ( SELECT admissions.age FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10024043 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime DESC LIMIT 1 ) ) ) AS T1 WHERE T1.valuenum = 3.3
generated_sql: SELECT (percentile_cont(0.75) within GROUP (ORDER BY phosphate) - percentile_cont(0.25) within GROUP (ORDER BY phosphate)) / NULLIF((percentile_cont(0.75) within GROUP (ORDER BY phosphate) - percentile_cont(0.25) within GROUP (ORDER BY phosphate)), 0) AS interquartile_range FROM patient_10024043_last_hospital_visit;

question: What are the total minimum expenses for a hospital involving a laboratory test for potassium, whole blood in 2100?

question: What is the monthly average value of patient 10007928's weight in 2100?

question: What exactly was the last drug that patient 10021118 was prescribed since 12/2100?

generated_sql: SELECT p.first_name, p.last_name, d.name AS drug_name, date_trunc('month', pr.prescription_date) AS prescription_month, COUNT(*) filter (WHERE date_part('year', pr.prescription_date) = 2000) AS years_prescribed FROM patient p JOIN prescription pr ON p.patient_id = pr.patient_id JOIN drug d ON d.drug_id = pr.drug_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10021118 AND date_part('year', pr.prescription_date) >= 2000 AND date_part('year', pr.prescription_date) <= 2010 GROUP BY p.first_name, p.last_name, drug_name, prescription_month HAVING COUNT(*) filter (WHERE date_part('year', pr.prescription_date) = 2000) > 0 ORDER BY prescription_month DESC NULLS LAST;

question: What are the three commonly taken specimens for patients that received excision of right saphenous vein, percutaneous endoscopic approach previously in the same hospital visit since 2100?
true_query: SELECT T3.spec_type_desc FROM ( SELECT T2.spec_type_desc, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'excision of right saphenous vein, percutaneous endoscopic approach' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc, microbiologyevents.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',microbiologyevents.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.spec_type_desc ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3
generated_sql: SELECT s.species FROM surgery s JOIN patient_surgery ps ON s.id = ps.surgery_id WHERE ps.patient_id IN (SELECT patient_id FROM surgery WHERE procedure = 'excision of right saphenous vein, percutaneous endoscopic approach' AND date > 2020) GROUP BY s.species LIMIT 3;

question: What were the top five most common procedures that occurred within the same month for patients who had central venous catheter placement with guidance before in 2100?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'central venous catheter placement with guidance' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT date_trunc('month', p.procedure_date) AS MONTH, COUNT(*) AS procedure_count, SUM(CASE WHEN p.procedure_code = 'Catheter placement with guidance' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS catheter_placement_with_guidance_count, SUM(CASE WHEN p.procedure_code = 'Catheter removal' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS catheter_removal_count FROM procedure p JOIN patient_procedure pp ON p.procedure_id = pp.procedure_id WHERE date_part('year', p.procedure_date) = 2100 GROUP BY MONTH ORDER BY procedure_count DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 5;

question: What are the three most frequently ordered medications that patients in their 40s were prescribed during the same month after they were diagnosed with hyperlipidemia, unspecified since 1 year ago?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'hyperlipidemia, unspecified' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE admissions.age BETWEEN 40 AND 49 AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.starttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3
generated_sql: SELECT m.name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM patient p JOIN medical_event e ON p.id = e.patient_id JOIN hyperlipidemia h ON p.id = h.patient_id JOIN medication m ON e.medication_id = m.id WHERE date_part('year', age(CURRENT_DATE, p.date_of_birth)) = 40 AND date_trunc('month', m.date_created) = date_trunc('month', h.date_diagnosed) AND date_part('year', age(CURRENT_DATE, h.date_diagnosed)) = 1 GROUP BY m.name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 3;

question: What are the three most frequently given diagnoses for patients who had previously had hemodialysis within 2 months, in 2100?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'hemodialysis' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.diagnosis, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM dialysis_patients d WHERE d.dialysis_date BETWEEN '2010-01-01' AND '2010-12-31' GROUP BY d.diagnosis ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 3;

question: Give me the top five most frequent treatments patients received within 2 months after being diagnosed with rheumatic disorders of both mitral and aortic valves in 2100.
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'rheumatic disorders of both mitral and aortic valves' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )

question: Give me the top five most frequently prescribed drugs within the same month for patients in their 40s who were diagnosed with acute alcoholic intoxication in alcoholism, continuous since 1 year ago.

question: Since 1 year ago, what are the three common diagnoses of patients of age 20s?

question: What were the top five diagnoses with the highest 3-month mortality rate?

question: Which medication was patient 10009628 prescribed during the same hospital encounter following the extracorporeal circulation auxiliary to open heart surgery procedure in 10/this year?

question: How many patients received enteral infusion of concentrated nutritional substances within the same month after being diagnosed with cerebral artery occlusion, unspecified with cerebral infarction?
true_query: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT T1.subject_id ) FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'cerebral artery occlusion, unspecified with cerebral infarction' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'enteral infusion of concentrated nutritional substances' ) ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month')
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM patient p JOIN (SELECT patient_id FROM procedure WHERE name ilike '%cerebral%arterial%occlusion%') AS o ON p.id = o.patient_id JOIN (SELECT patient_id FROM procedure WHERE name ilike '%cerebral%infarction%') AS i ON p.id = i.patient_id JOIN (SELECT patient_id, to_char(date_trunc('month', procedure_date), 'YYYY-MM') AS procedure_month FROM procedure WHERE name ilike '%enternal%infusion%of%concentrated%nutritional%substances%') AS e ON p.id = e.patient_id WHERE to_date(procedure_month, 'YYYY-MM') BETWEEN to_date(to_char(i.procedure_date, 'YYYY-MM'), 'YYYY-MM') AND to_date(to_char(o.procedure_date, 'YYYY-MM'), 'YYYY-MM') AND (p.age > 18 AND p.gender_id = 2);

question: What were the four most commonly given diagnoses for patients who had received diagnostic ultrasound of digestive system before within 2 months in 2100?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'diagnostic ultrasound of digestive system' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )

generated_sql: SELECT MIN(o.order_date) FROM orders o WHERE o.patient_id = 10009049 AND EXTRACT(MONTH FROM o.order_date) = 6 AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM o.order_date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE);

question: Was patient 10022017 diagnosed with anything last year?
true_query: SELECT COUNT(*)>0 FROM diagnoses_icd WHERE diagnoses_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10022017 ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-1 year')
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(d.disease_id) > 0 AS was_diagnosed_last_year FROM patient p JOIN patient_disease pd ON p.patient_id = pd.patient_id JOIN disease d ON pd.disease_id = d.disease_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10022017 AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM pd.disease_start_date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) - 1;

question: What is the average value of oxygen in patient 10014729's body in 03/this year?
true_query: SELECT AVG(labevents.valuenum) FROM labevents WHERE labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10014729 ) AND labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'oxygen' ) AND datetime(labevents.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',labevents.charttime) = '03'

question: What was the drug name that patient 10027445 was last prescribed through the tp route in 09/this year?

generated_sql: SELECT d.drug_name FROM drug_administration da JOIN drugs d ON da.drug_id = d.drug_id WHERE da.patient_id = 10027445 AND da.route = 'tp' AND EXTRACT(MONTH FROM da.date_last_modified) = 9 AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM da.date_last_modified) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) ORDER BY da.date_last_modified DESC LIMIT 1;

question: For patients previously diagnosed with nicotine dependence, cigarettes, uncomplicated , what were the five most frequent specimens tested in the same month afterward?
true_query: SELECT T3.spec_type_desc FROM ( SELECT T2.spec_type_desc, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'nicotine dependence, cigarettes, uncomplicated' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc, microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.spec_type_desc ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5
generated_sql: SELECT date_trunc('month', p.diagnosis_date) AS MONTH, COUNT(*) AS total_specimens, array_agg(s.code) AS specimen_codes FROM patients p JOIN specimens s ON p.id = s.patient_id WHERE date_part('year', p.diagnosis_date) = 2022 AND p.previously_diagnosed_with_nicotine_dependence = TRUE AND p.cigarettes_smoked_uncomplicated = TRUE GROUP BY MONTH ORDER BY MONTH NULLS LAST LIMIT 5;

question: What was the name of the drug patient 10015931 was prescribed within 2 days after having received a introduction of other therapeutic substance into peripheral artery, percutaneous approach procedure during this month?
true_query: SELECT T2.drug FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.charttime, procedures_icd.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'introduction of other therapeutic substance into peripheral artery, percutaneous approach' ) AND procedures_icd.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10015931 ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(current_time,'start of month','-0 month') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10015931 ) AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of month') = datetime(current_time,'start of month','-0 month') ) AS T2 ON T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T2.starttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 day')
generated_sql: SELECT d.drug_name FROM patient_drug pd JOIN drug d ON pd.drug_id = d.drug_id JOIN patient p ON pd.patient_id = p.patient_id JOIN procedure_performed pp ON p.patient_id = pp.patient_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10015931 AND EXTRACT(MONTH FROM pp.procedure_date) = EXTRACT(MONTH FROM CURRENT_DATE) AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM pp.procedure_date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) AND pp.procedure_name ILIKE '%peripheral%artery%' AND pp.procedure_name ILIKE '%percutaneous%approach%' LIMIT 1;

question: What was the name of the drug that patient 10004733 was prescribed within 2 days after having received since 10/2100 a enteral infusion of concentrated nutritional substances procedure?
true_query: SELECT T2.drug FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.charttime, procedures_icd.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'enteral infusion of concentrated nutritional substances' ) AND procedures_icd.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10004733 ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100-10' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10004733 ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',prescriptions.starttime) >= '2100-10' ) AS T2 ON T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T2.starttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 day')

question: Show me the top three most frequent diagnoses that patients were diagnosed with within 2 months after receiving other endoscopy of small intestine since 1 year ago.
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'other endoscopy of small intestine' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.diagnosis, COUNT(d.diagnosis) AS frequency FROM Diagnosis d JOIN Endoscopy e ON d.patient_id = e.patient_id AND d.diagnosis_date BETWEEN e.endoscopy_date AND e.endoscopy_date + interval '60 days' GROUP BY d.diagnosis ORDER BY frequency DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 3;

question: What was the medicine that was prescribed to patient 10009035 in the same hospital encounter after undergoing extracorporeal circulation auxiliary to open heart surgery in 05/this year?
true_query: SELECT T2.drug FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.charttime, procedures_icd.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'extracorporeal circulation auxiliary to open heart surgery' ) AND procedures_icd.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10009035 ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',procedures_icd.charttime) = '05' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10009035 ) AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '05' ) AS T2 ON T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime
generated_sql: SELECT m.name, a.name AS auxiliary_procedure_name, to_char(o.date_started, 'YYYY') AS year_open_heart_surgery FROM patient p JOIN patient_procedure pp ON p.id = pp.patient_id JOIN procedure pr ON pp.procedure_id = pr.id JOIN auxiliary_procedure a ON pr.id = a.procedure_id JOIN medicine m ON a.medicine_id = m.id JOIN open_heart_surgery o ON p.id = o.patient_id WHERE p.id = 10009035 AND to_date(o.date_started, 'YYYY-MM-DD') > to_date('05/this_year', 'MM/YYYY');

question: What was the top five most frequent diagnoses since 1 year ago that patients were diagnosed with within the same month after receiving incision with removal of foreign body or device from skin and subcutaneous tissue?

question: Can you get me the top four diagnoses that have the highest 3-month mortality rate?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T4.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM ( SELECT T1.icd_code, ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/4 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) as C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/4 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id ) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 ) AS T4 WHERE T4.C3 <= 4 )

question: I would like to know the top four diagnoses that have the highest 3-month mortality rate.

question: What are the top four most common microbiology tests that patients were diagnosed with after the diagnosis of spinal stenosis, lumbar region, without neurogenic claudication within the same hospital visit?

question: What are the three most frequently administered laboratory tests for patients previously diagnosed with chronic airway obstruction, not elsewhere classified during the same hospital visit, since 1 year ago?
true_query: SELECT d_labitems.label FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.itemid IN ( SELECT T3.itemid FROM ( SELECT T2.itemid, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'chronic airway obstruction, not elsewhere classified' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, labevents.itemid, labevents.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM labevents JOIN admissions ON labevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(labevents.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.itemid ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3 )

question: What were the four most frequently given diagnoses for patients who received percutaneous abdominal drainage previously within 2 months?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'percutaneous abdominal drainage' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )

question: What are the three frequently tested specimens for patients that received extirpation of matter from left femoral vein, percutaneous approach previously within 2 months this year?
true_query: SELECT T3.spec_type_desc FROM ( SELECT T2.spec_type_desc, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'extirpation of matter from left femoral vein, percutaneous approach' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc, microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(microbiologyevents.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.spec_type_desc ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3

question: What are the top five most common specimens being tested for patients who were diagnosed with personal history of irradiation, presenting hazards to health within the same month in 2100?
true_query: SELECT T3.spec_type_desc FROM ( SELECT T2.spec_type_desc, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'personal history of irradiation, presenting hazards to health' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc, microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',microbiologyevents.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.spec_type_desc ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5

question: Can you tell me which five diagnoses have the highest 3-month mortality rate?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T4.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM ( SELECT T1.icd_code, ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/4 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) as C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/4 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id ) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 ) AS T4 WHERE T4.C3 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.name, CAST(COUNT(*) filter (WHERE e.death_date BETWEEN d.date_of_diagnosis AND d.date_of_diagnosis + interval '3 months') AS FLOAT) / NULLIF(COUNT(*), 0) AS mortality_rate FROM diagnosis d JOIN patient p ON d.patient_id = p.id JOIN event e ON p.id = e.patient_id GROUP BY d.name ORDER BY mortality_rate DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 5;

question: What are the three diagnoses with the lowest 3-month survival rate?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T4.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM ( SELECT T1.icd_code, ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/4 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) as C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/4 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id ) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 ) AS T4 WHERE T4.C3 <= 3 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.diagnosis_code, d.diagnosis_name, COUNT(s.survival_months)::FLOAT / NULLIF((SELECT COUNT(survival_months) FROM survival_data WHERE survival_months < 3), 0) AS survival_rate FROM survival_data s JOIN diagnosis d ON s.diagnosis_code = d.diagnosis_code WHERE s.survival_months < 3 GROUP BY d.diagnosis_code, d.diagnosis_name ORDER BY survival_rate DESC LIMIT 3;

question: What are the five most frequent diagnoses that patients were diagnosed within 2 months after having received a excision of dental lesion of jaw procedure?

question: When was patient 10020740 prescribed a medication via the iv route the first time in 03/this year?

question: For patients diagnosed with right bundle branch block before, what are the top four most common treatments within the same month since 2100?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'right bundle branch block' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT treatment, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM patient_treatments pt WHERE pt.patient_id IN (SELECT patient_id FROM patient_treatments WHERE treatment_start_date >= '2021-01-01' AND treatment_start_date < '2021-02-01' AND treatment_end_date >= '2021-12-31' AND treatment_end_date < '2022-01-01' AND treatment_type = 'diagnosis' AND treatment_name = 'right bundle branch block') GROUP BY pt.patient_id) GROUP BY pt.treatment_id ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 4;

question: In 2100, what were the top three most common specimens tested on patients within the same month after the diagnosis of body mass index (bmi) 35.0-35.9, adult?
true_query: SELECT T3.spec_type_desc FROM ( SELECT T2.spec_type_desc, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'body mass index (bmi) 35.0-35.9, adult' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc, microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',microbiologyevents.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.spec_type_desc ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3
generated_sql: SELECT s.specimen_type, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM specimen s JOIN patient_test pt ON s.specimen_id = pt.specimen_id JOIN patient p ON pt.patient_id = p.patient_id WHERE p.date_of_birth <= '2021-01-01' AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM p.date_of_birth) + EXTRACT(YEAR FROM age(CURRENT_DATE)) > 2021 AND bmi(p.weight, p.height) BETWEEN 35.0 AND 35.9 GROUP BY s.specimen_type ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 3;

question: What drug was patient 10022017 prescribed for within the same day after undergoing bypass coronary artery, three arteries from aorta with autologous venous tissue, open approach in 10/2100?
true_query: SELECT T2.drug FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.charttime, procedures_icd.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'bypass coronary artery, three arteries from aorta with autologous venous tissue, open approach' ) AND procedures_icd.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10022017 ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100-10' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10022017 ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '2100-10' ) AS T2 ON T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of day') = datetime(T2.starttime,'start of day')
generated_sql: SELECT d.drug_name FROM patient_surgeries ps JOIN procedures p ON ps.procedure_id = p.procedure_id JOIN drugs_affected d ON p.procedure_id = d.procedure_id WHERE ps.patient_id = 10022017 AND p.procedure_name = 'bypass coronary artery' AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM ps.surgeon_date) = 2017 AND EXTRACT(MONTH FROM ps.surgeon_date) = 10 AND EXTRACT(DAY FROM ps.surgeon_date) = 21;

question: What are the four commonly given procedures for patients that also received reposition left mandible with external fixation device, percutaneous approach previously within 2 months, since 2100?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'reposition left mandible with external fixation device, percutaneous approach' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )

question: Count the number of people who received introduction of nutritional substance into lower gi, via natural or artificial opening in the same month after having been diagnosed with epilepsy, unspecified, not intractable, without status epilepticus in 2100.
true_query: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT T1.subject_id ) FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'epilepsy, unspecified, not intractable, without status epilepticus' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'introduction of nutritional substance into lower gi, via natural or artificial opening' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month')
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM patient p JOIN seizure s ON p.id = s.patient_id JOIN treatment t ON s.id = t.seizure_id JOIN introduction i ON t.id = i.treatment_id WHERE p.birth_date >= '2021-01-01' AND p.birth_date < '2021-01-02' AND p.birth_date < '2021-01-02' AND i.opening_method_natural IS NOT NULL AND i.opening_method_artificial IS NOT NULL AND p.status_epilepticus IS NULL;
