generated_sql: SELECT MIN(o.discharge_date) AS earliest_discharge_date FROM patient_stay ps JOIN patient p ON ps.patient_id = p.patient_id JOIN patient_visit pv ON ps.patient_id = pv.patient_id JOIN stay s ON ps.stay_id = s.stay_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10012853;

question: What percentile is the calcium, total value of 8.2 among patients of the same age as patient 10020740 on the last hospital stay?
true_query: SELECT DISTINCT T1.C1 FROM ( SELECT labevents.valuenum, PERCENT_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY labevents.valuenum ) AS C1 FROM labevents WHERE labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'calcium, total' ) AND labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age = ( SELECT admissions.age FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10020740 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime DESC LIMIT 1 ) ) ) AS T1 WHERE T1.valuenum = 8.2
generated_sql: SELECT percentile_cont(0.75) within GROUP (ORDER BY c.calcium) AS seventy_fifth_percentile FROM patient_calcium p JOIN patient_stay s ON p.patient_id = s.patient_id WHERE s.patient_id = 10020740 AND s.hospital_id = 757071;

question: What are the three frequently tested specimens for patients that received bypass coronary artery, one artery from aorta with autologous venous tissue, open approach previously in the same month in 2100?
true_query: SELECT T3.spec_type_desc FROM ( SELECT T2.spec_type_desc, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'bypass coronary artery, one artery from aorta with autologous venous tissue, open approach' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc, microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',microbiologyevents.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.spec_type_desc ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3
generated_sql: SELECT s.name, COUNT(*) AS freq FROM specimens s JOIN patient_surgeries ps ON s.id = ps.specimen_id JOIN patients p ON ps.patient_id = p.id WHERE ps.surgery_type = 'bypass' AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM ps.surgery_date) = 2100 AND p.birth_date BETWEEN '1920-01-01' AND '2020-12-31' GROUP BY s.name ORDER BY freq DESC LIMIT 3;

question: How was patient 10038933 admitted in terms of admission type for the last time?

question: When furosemide and albuterol inhaler were prescribed to patient 10037975 for the first time in 02/this year at the same time?
true_query: SELECT T1.starttime FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'furosemide' AND admissions.subject_id = 10037975 AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '02' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'albuterol inhaler' AND admissions.subject_id = 10037975 AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '02' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE datetime(T1.starttime) = datetime(T2.starttime) ORDER BY T1.starttime ASC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM prescriptions p WHERE p.patient_id = 10037975 AND p.date_prescribed >= date_trunc('year', CURRENT_DATE) AND p.date_prescribed <= date_trunc('year', CURRENT_DATE) AND p.drug_id IN (777072, 757071);

question: Could you tell me the average total cost in a hospital where tramadol (ultram) is used since 1 year ago?

question: What's the maximum yearly number of admissions for respiratory failure, unspecified, unspecified whether with hypoxia or hypercapnia since 2100?

generated_sql: SELECT MAX(COUNT) AS max_admissions_year FROM (SELECT EXTRACT(YEAR FROM age(CURRENT_DATE, to_date(patient_id, 'YYYYMMDD'))) AS YEAR, COUNT(*) AS COUNT FROM patients WHERE patient_id IN (SELECT patient_id FROM patients WHERE to_number(patient_id, '99999999') >= 2100 AND to_number(patient_id, '99999999') <= 2101 AND patient_condition_code IN ('RF', 'U', 'UH', 'UC')) GROUP BY YEAR ORDER BY YEAR) AS subquery;

question: What are the three most often performed treatments for patients aged 60 or above in 2100?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T1.icd_code FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age >= 60 ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100' GROUP BY procedures_icd.icd_code ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 3 )

question: Among patients who were diagnosed with hip joint replacement, what were the top five most common microbiology tests conducted within 2 months in 2100?
true_query: SELECT T3.test_name FROM ( SELECT T2.test_name, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'hip joint replacement' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.test_name, microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',microbiologyevents.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.test_name ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5
generated_sql: SELECT m.microbiology_test, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM patient_procedures pp JOIN microbiology_test m ON pp.microbiology_test_id = m.id JOIN hip_joint_replacement h ON pp.procedure_id = h.procedure_id WHERE pp.date_of_procedure BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31' GROUP BY m.microbiology_test ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 5;

question: Count the number of patients in neuro stepdown in the previous year.

question: Tell me the name of the drug patient 10007818 was prescribed during the same day after having received a fluoroscopy of superior vena cava using other contrast, guidance procedure in 07/this year?
true_query: SELECT T2.drug FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.charttime, procedures_icd.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'fluoroscopy of superior vena cava using other contrast, guidance' ) AND procedures_icd.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10007818 ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',procedures_icd.charttime) = '07' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10007818 ) AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '07' ) AS T2 ON T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of day') = datetime(T2.starttime,'start of day')
generated_sql: SELECT d.drug_name, to_char(p.procedure_date, 'YYYY-MM-DD') AS procedure_date FROM patient p JOIN procedure_details pd ON p.patient_id = pd.patient_id JOIN drugs_administered da ON pd.procedure_id = da.procedure_id JOIN drugs d ON da.drug_id = d.drug_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10007818 AND to_char(p.procedure_date, 'YYYY-MM-DD') > to_char(now() - interval '1 day', 'YYYY-MM-DD') AND pd.procedure_id NOT IN (SELECT procedure_id FROM procedure_details WHERE procedure_date = (to_char(now() - interval '1 day', 'YYYY-MM-DD')));

question: What is the average total hospital cost that involved implantation or replacement of carotid sinus stimulation device, total system since 1 year ago?

question: What are the three frequently ordered drugs for patients diagnosed with tobacco use disorder previously in the same month, this year?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'tobacco use disorder' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.starttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3

question: Can you provide the name of the drug that was prescribed to patient 10027602 within 2 days post arteriography of cerebral arteries procedure since 12/2100?
true_query: SELECT T2.drug FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.charttime, procedures_icd.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'arteriography of cerebral arteries' ) AND procedures_icd.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10027602 ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100-12' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10027602 ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',prescriptions.starttime) >= '2100-12' ) AS T2 ON T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T2.starttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 day')
generated_sql: SELECT d.name FROM drugs d JOIN patient_prescriptions pp ON d.id = pp.drug_id WHERE pp.patient_id = 10027602 AND pp.date_prescribed BETWEEN '2012-12-21' AND '2012-12-23';

question: Could you tell me the sex of patient 10002930?

question: Give me the top four most commonly prescribed medications during the same month to patients aged 60 or above after they were diagnosed with unspecified essential hypertension since 1 year ago.
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'unspecified essential hypertension' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE admissions.age >= 60 AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.starttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4
generated_sql: SELECT d.drug_name, COUNT(d.drug_name) AS drug_count FROM patient p JOIN patient_diagnosis pd ON p.patient_id = pd.patient_id JOIN drug_prescription dp ON p.patient_id = dp.patient_id JOIN drug d ON dp.drug_id = d.drug_id WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM pd.diagnosis_date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE - interval '1 year') AND p.age >= 60 AND pd.diagnosis_type_code = 'EH' GROUP BY d.drug_name ORDER BY drug_count DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 4;

question: What was the monthly minimum input of nacl 0.9% for patient 10015931 since 09/2100?
true_query: SELECT MIN(inputevents.totalamount) FROM inputevents WHERE inputevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10015931 ) ) AND inputevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'nacl 0.9%' AND d_items.linksto = 'inputevents' ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',inputevents.starttime) >= '2100-09' GROUP BY strftime('%Y-%m',inputevents.starttime)
generated_sql: SELECT date_trunc('month', t.time) AS MONTH, MIN(v.value) AS min_value FROM nacl_0.9% t JOIN patient_10015931 v ON t.time = v.time WHERE date_part('year', t.time) >= 2000 AND date_part('year', t.time) < 2010 GROUP BY MONTH ORDER BY MONTH;

question: When was the first time since 06/05/2100 that patient 10007818's mean blood pressure was measured greater than 72.0?
true_query: SELECT chartevents.charttime FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10007818 ) ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'arterial blood pressure mean' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) AND chartevents.valuenum > 72.0 AND strftime('%Y-%m-%d',chartevents.charttime) >= '2100-06-05' ORDER BY chartevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT MIN(o.timestamp) AS first_time_high_bp FROM Observation o WHERE o.patient = 10007818 AND o.mean_bp > 72.0 AND o.timestamp >= '2021-06-05';

question: Can you give me the five most common output events since 1 year ago?
true_query: SELECT d_items.label FROM d_items WHERE d_items.itemid IN ( SELECT T1.itemid FROM ( SELECT outputevents.itemid, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM outputevents WHERE datetime(outputevents.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') GROUP BY outputevents.itemid ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT o.output_event, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM outputs o WHERE o.time >= now() - interval '1 year' GROUP BY o.output_event ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 5;

question: What is the price of a drug named tobramycin sulfate?

generated_sql: SELECT price FROM drug d WHERE d.name ILIKE '%tobramycin%sulfate%' LIMIT 1;

question: What were the top five most frequent diagnoses that followed within 2 months for those patients who received laparoscopic partial cholecystectomy since 1 year ago?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'laparoscopic partial cholecystectomy' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.name, cume_dist() OVER (ORDER BY d.name) AS cumulative_distribution FROM diagnosis d JOIN patient_procedure pp ON d.name = pp.procedure_name JOIN procedure_occurrence po ON pp.procedure_name = po.procedure_name WHERE po.procedure_name = 'Laparoscopic partial cholecystectomy' AND po.date > CURRENT_DATE - interval '1 year' GROUP BY d.name ORDER BY cumulative_distribution DESC LIMIT 5;

question: How much octreotide acetate has patient 10007818 been prescribed on the last hospital visit?

question: Can you calculate how many patients were prescribed glucagon this year?

question: What is the title of the medication that was given to patient 10012853 last via the po means in 04/this year?
true_query: SELECT prescriptions.drug FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10012853 ) AND prescriptions.route = 'po' AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '04' ORDER BY prescriptions.starttime DESC LIMIT 1

question: What is the name of the treatment given to patient 10038081 two or more times since 07/2100?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T1.icd_code FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.icd_code, COUNT( procedures_icd.charttime ) AS C1 FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10038081 ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100-07' GROUP BY procedures_icd.icd_code ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 >= 2 )
generated_sql: SELECT t.treatment_name, COUNT(*) AS number_of_treatments FROM patient_treatments pt JOIN treatments t ON pt.treatment_id = t.treatment_id WHERE pt.patient_id = 10038081 AND pt.treatment_given_date >= '2010-07-01' GROUP BY t.treatment_name HAVING COUNT(t.treatment_name) >= 2;

question: What is the total number of excision of dental lesion of jaw procedures that took place in 2100?

question: In 2100, what are the five frequently ordered treatments for patients who were diagnosed with cachexia during the same month?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'cachexia' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT t.treatment_name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM patient_treatments pt JOIN treatments t ON pt.treatment_id = t.treatment_id JOIN patient_diagnoses pd ON pt.patient_id = pd.patient_id WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM pd.diagnosis_date) = 2021 AND EXTRACT(MONTH FROM pd.diagnosis_date) = 1 AND pt.discharge_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-01-31' GROUP BY t.treatment_name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 5;

question: Tell me the four most common diagnoses since 1 year ago.

generated_sql: SELECT d.diagnosis, COUNT(d.diagnosis) AS COUNT FROM Diagnoses d WHERE d.date >= CURRENT_DATE - interval '1 year' GROUP BY d.diagnosis ORDER BY COUNT DESC LIMIT 4;

question: When did patient 10004720 receive the last prescription of soln and bag at the same time since 12/2100?
true_query: SELECT T1.starttime FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'soln' AND admissions.subject_id = 10004720 AND strftime('%Y-%m',prescriptions.starttime) >= '2100-12' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'bag' AND admissions.subject_id = 10004720 AND strftime('%Y-%m',prescriptions.starttime) >= '2100-12' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE datetime(T1.starttime) = datetime(T2.starttime) ORDER BY T1.starttime DESC LIMIT 1

question: What is patient 10016150's heart rate change last measured on the first ICU visit compared to the value first measured on the first ICU visit?
true_query: SELECT ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10016150 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime ASC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'heart rate' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1 ) - ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10016150 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime ASC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'heart rate' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 )
result: [{"( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10016150 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime ASC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'heart rate' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1 ) - ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10016150 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime ASC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'heart rate' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 )": None}]
generated_sql: SELECT (MAX(hr.heart_rate) - MIN(hr.heart_rate)) AS change_in_heart_rate FROM patient p JOIN patient_icu_visit piv ON p.patient_id = piv.patient_id JOIN heart_rate hr ON piv.patient_icu_visit_id = hr.patient_icu_visit_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10016150;

question: How many days have passed since patient 10004733 got his last diagnosis of proteus (mirabilis) (morganii) infection in conditions classified elsewhere and of unspecified site on their current hospital encounter?

question: How many hours have elapsed since patient 10018081 first received a hematocrit lab test during this hospital visit?

question: What are the top five most frequently performed procedures for patients who are 20s since 1 year ago?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T1.icd_code FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age BETWEEN 20 AND 29 ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') GROUP BY procedures_icd.icd_code ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(*), SUBSTRING(p.procedure_date, 1, 4) AS procedure_year, p.procedure_code, p.patient_id FROM patient_procedures p WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) - CAST(p.procedure_date AS INT) < 1 AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CAST(p.procedure_date AS DATE)) BETWEEN 20 AND 29 GROUP BY procedure_year, procedure_code, patient_id ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC LIMIT 5;

question: Among patients who underwent other electroshock therapy this year, what were the top five diagnoses they received within 2 months?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'other electroshock therapy' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT p.first_name, p.last_name, d.diagnosis_name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM patient p JOIN procedure pr ON p.patient_id = pr.patient_id JOIN diagnosis d ON pr.diagnosis_id = d.diagnosis_id WHERE pr.procedure_name = 'electroshock' AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM pr.procedure_date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) AND pr.procedure_date >= CURRENT_DATE - interval '2 months' GROUP BY p.first_name, p.last_name, d.diagnosis_name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 5;

question: Calculate the number of patients who were in the pacu careunit this year.
true_query: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT admissions.subject_id ) FROM admissions WHERE admissions.hadm_id IN ( SELECT transfers.hadm_id FROM transfers WHERE transfers.careunit = 'pacu' AND datetime(transfers.intime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') )
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p.patient_id) FROM pacucareunit p WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM p.entry_date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE);

question: When, on 01/28/2100, was patient 10019917's heart rate measured less than 73.0 for the last time?
true_query: SELECT chartevents.charttime FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10019917 ) ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'heart rate' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) AND chartevents.valuenum < 73.0 AND strftime('%Y-%m-%d',chartevents.charttime) = '2100-01-28' ORDER BY chartevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT MAX(v.value_date) AS last_value_date FROM vital_signs v WHERE v.patient_id = 10019917 AND v.value_number < 73.0;

question: Count the number of patients who were discharged.

generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM patients p WHERE p.discharged = TRUE;

question: Show me the length of stay in days of patient 10019385 from the last stay in the ICU.
true_query: SELECT strftime('%J', icustays.outtime) - strftime('%J', icustays.intime) FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10019385 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime DESC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT (CURRENT_DATE - lag(discharge_date) OVER (PARTITION BY patient_id ORDER BY admission_date)) AS length_of_stay FROM patient_stays WHERE patient_id = 10019385 ORDER BY admission_date DESC LIMIT 1;

question: Can you report the last respiratory rate for patient 10007058 since 09/08/2100?
true_query: SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10007058 ) ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'respiratory rate' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) AND strftime('%Y-%m-%d',chartevents.charttime) >= '2100-09-08' ORDER BY chartevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT v.value_date, v.value AS respiratory_rate FROM vital_signs v WHERE v.patient_id = 10007058 AND v.value_date > '2009-08-31' ORDER BY v.value_date ASC LIMIT 1;

question: Tell me the top three most frequent procedures that patients received in the same hospital encounter after being diagnosed with other forms of acute ischemic heart disease.
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'other forms of acute ischemic heart disease' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3 )
generated_sql: SELECT p.patient_id, p.patient_name, p.gender, d.disease_name, COUNT(*) AS procedure_count, rank() OVER (PARTITION BY p.patient_id ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC) AS procedure_rank FROM patient p JOIN disease d ON p.patient_id = d.patient_id JOIN procedure pr ON d.disease_id = pr.disease_id WHERE d.disease_name ilike '%acute%ischemic%heart%disease%' AND pr.procedure_id IN (SELECT procedure_id FROM procedure WHERE procedure_name ilike '%procedure%') GROUP BY p.patient_id, p.patient_name, p.gender, d.disease_name HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT pr.procedure_id) > 1 ORDER BY procedure_rank <= 3;

question: What was the medicine that was prescribed to patient 10025463 in the same hospital encounter after undergoing catheter based invasive electrophysiologic testing during the last month?
true_query: SELECT T2.drug FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.charttime, procedures_icd.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'catheter based invasive electrophysiologic testing' ) AND procedures_icd.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10025463 ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(current_time,'start of month','-1 month') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10025463 ) AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of month') = datetime(current_time,'start of month','-1 month') ) AS T2 ON T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime
generated_sql: SELECT m.medication FROM patient p JOIN catheter c ON p.patient_id = c.patient_id JOIN electrophysiology e ON c.catheter_id = e.catheter_id JOIN medication m ON e.medication_id = m.medication_id WHERE p.patient_id = 10025463 AND e.procedure_date >= (CURRENT_DATE - interval '1 month') GROUP BY m.medication;

question: How much is the difference of SaO2 of patient 10019777 last measured on the first ICU visit compared to the first value measured on the first ICU visit?

question: How many patients were diagnosed with other postoperative infection since 2100 after already being diagnosed with injury to thoracic aorta during the same hospital encounter?
true_query: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT T1.subject_id ) FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'injury to thoracic aorta' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'other postoperative infection' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p.id) AS patient_count FROM patient p JOIN procedure pr ON p.id = pr.patient_id WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM pr.procedure_date) >= 2021 AND pr.procedure_name = 'Thoracic Aorta Injury' AND p.id IN (SELECT p.id FROM patient p JOIN procedure pr ON p.id = pr.patient_id WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM pr.procedure_date) >= 2021 AND pr.procedure_name = 'Postoperative Infection');

question: What are the top three most common specimens tested after receiving arteriography of other intra-abdominal arteries in the same month since 1 year ago?
true_query: SELECT T3.spec_type_desc FROM ( SELECT T2.spec_type_desc, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'arteriography of other intra-abdominal arteries' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc, microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(microbiologyevents.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.spec_type_desc ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3
generated_sql: SELECT s.specimen, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM Specimens s JOIN Arteriography a ON s.specimen = a.specimen WHERE a.artery IN (SELECT artery FROM Arteriography WHERE date_trunc('month', age(CURRENT_DATE, date)) = date_trunc('month', age(CURRENT_DATE, date) - interval '1 year')) GROUP BY s.specimen ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 3;

question: How many patients were diagnosed with type 2 diabetes mellitus without complications during the same month after they were first diagnosed with altered mental status, unspecified?
true_query: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT T1.subject_id ) FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'altered mental status, unspecified' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'type 2 diabetes mellitus without complications' ) ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month')
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM patient p JOIN diagnosis d ON p.id = d.patient_id JOIN patient_status ps ON p.id = ps.patient_id AND d.date_diagnosed = ps.date_admitted WHERE d.diagnosis_type = 'type 2 diabetes mellitus' AND d.complications IS NULL AND EXTRACT(MONTH FROM d.date_diagnosed) = EXTRACT(MONTH FROM ps.date_admitted) AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM d.date_diagnosed) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM ps.date_admitted) AND ps.status_code = 'altered mental status, unspecified';

question: Tell me the three most common microbiology tests for patients who were previously diagnosed with adverse effect of penicillins, initial encounter within 2 months.

question: How many patients received extirpation of matter from left lower lobe bronchus, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic treatment in the same month after having been diagnosed with other diseases of bronchus, not elsewhere classified since 2100?

generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM bronchus b JOIN bronchial_treatments t ON b.patient_id = t.patient_id WHERE b.bronchus_type = 'lower' AND b.bronchus_side = 'left' AND b.date_of_treatment BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31' AND t.treatment_name ILIKE '%extirpation%' AND (t.treatment_type_id = 1 OR t.treatment_type_id = 2) AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM bronchial_treatments sub_t WHERE sub_t.patient_id = t.patient_id AND sub_t.treatment_date < t.treatment_date AND sub_t.treatment_name NOT ILIKE '%other%disease%of%bronchus%not%elsewhere%classified%since%2021%');
